INSERT INTO `characters` VALUES (1,'Naruto Uzumaki','Some random description','2020-10-14 15:06:48','2020-10-14 15:06:48','https://giantbomb1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_small/3/33873/1700999-naruto.png','Main Character'),(2,'Naruto Uzumaki','Some random description','2020-10-14 15:06:58','2020-10-14 15:06:58','https://giantbomb1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_small/3/33873/1700999-naruto.png','Main Character'),(3,'Naruto Uzumaki','Some random description','2020-10-14 15:08:17','2020-10-14 15:08:17','https://giantbomb1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_small/3/33873/1700999-naruto.png','Main Character'),(5,'Naruto Uzumaki','Some random description','2020-10-14 15:12:34','2020-10-14 15:12:34','https://giantbomb1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_small/3/33873/1700999-naruto.png','Main Character'),(6,'Sasuke Uchiha','Some random description','2020-10-14 15:49:07','2020-10-14 15:49:07','https://static.zerochan.net/Uchiha.Sasuke.full.2873171.jpg','Main Character'),(7,'Sakura','Some random description','2020-10-14 15:53:52','2020-10-14 15:53:52','https://i.pinimg.com/originals/38/28/3b/38283b3aacde00cd444be725c490cb26.jpg','Main Character'),(8,'Kakashi','Some random description','2020-10-14 15:55:08','2020-10-14 15:55:08','https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/naruto/images/2/27/Kakashi_Hatake.png/revision/latest?cb=20170628120149','Main Character'),(9,'Hinata','Some random description','2020-10-14 15:56:18','2020-10-14 15:56:18','https://www.anime-planet.com/images/characters/hinata-hyuuga-626.jpg','Main Character'),(10,'Detective Conan','Some random description','2020-10-14 16:11:28','2020-10-14 16:11:28','https://i.redd.it/zmbggxja2df41.jpg','Main Character'),(11,'Akame','__Height:__ 164cm (5\'4)\n\nAkame is one of the members of the Assassin\'s group, Night raid. She is the first member to attack Tatsumi, and comes very close to killing him. She initially appears very serious and cold-hearted, but she is actually caring and worries about the safety of her comrades. She has a younger sister named Kurome, who is a member of the Jaegers, and loyal to the Empire.   ~!When she was a child, her parents had sold both her and Kurome to the Empire. There, they were placed and raised as Assassins from childhood. Akame in particular became infamous enough to earned the top rank in the Imperial Assassin Division. At some point, many of her comrades had died and she become dissatisfied and resentful towards the government. It was not until she was sent to kill former General Najenda that Akame finally deflected to the Rebels after being swayed by her.!~ (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:31','2020-10-19 11:23:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b63351-0WmsDENpiscp.png','SC'),(12,'Tatsumi','Tatsumi is a swordsman from a small village. He set out to the capital with two of his companions in hope of raising money for the village. He got separated from his friends and reaches the capital. Tatsumi was not aware of the type of place the capital really was. After a series of events centered around his naivety of the true nature of the capital he found himself being saved be Night Raid(Assassination Group) and later join them to rid the capital of its corrupt inhabitants. His Teigu is Incursio.','2020-10-19 11:23:31','2020-10-19 11:23:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/64749-a2ZdRWW1D5TR.jpg','MC'),(13,'Lubbock','Lubbock is a member of the assassin group, Night Raid. He is often shown being a pervert, including trying to peep on Leone while bathing, usually these attempts end in failure. In the city, his cover is an owner of a bookstore.   ~!Rabac was 4th son born into a wealth merchant family in a region in the Empire. During his childhood as a boy he met Najenda who just moved into the region for the first time. Falling in love at first sight he left the privileged life he no longer desired to follow her into the army. Using his talent, Rabac rose through the ranks to the point where he could serve and be by her side. He would also join Najenda in her deflection to the rebellion, even going as far risk his life to change the military records of both him and her to K.I.A. Because of this he shares a somewhat antagonistic relationship Susanoo who he views as a rival for Najenda\'s affections.!~','2020-10-19 11:23:31','2020-10-19 11:23:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65231-2QpM2yw2X86k.png','MC'),(14,'Bulat','Bulat was once a high-ranking Imperial Officer known as \"100 Man-Slayer Bulat\". He later decided to betray the Empire when his superior was framed for not giving in to the Prime Minister\'s agenda. Bulat became disgusted with the Empire that cared more for bribes, than merit regardless of how hard he worked. After leaving the Empire, he joined the Revolutionaries, and eventually Night Raid.   ~! He died in battle, before his death at the hands of his former boss he entrusted the Incursio to Tatsumi.!~ (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:31','2020-10-19 11:23:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65235-KbSvHjKWY3z4.png','MC'),(15,'Leone','__Age:__ 20\'s\n__Height:__ 170cm (5\'7)\n\nLeone is one of the older members of the assassination group, Night Raid. She has a very relaxed and a cheerful personality, which tends to display a lack of ladylike manners, such as shoving Tatsumi into her breasts, putting her feet on the table, or consuming large amounts of Sake. She serves as a sort of big sister figure to Tatsumi and the younger members in Night Raid, often referring to herself as \"Onee-San\". Despite the morally dodgy nature, she can sometimes display, Leone is not one to tolerate injustice and can be especially vicious to those who commit the vilest acts. She excels at gathering information and exercising calm judgement when necessary.  \n\n(Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:31','2020-10-19 11:23:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65227-Qpsr77thRIie.png','SC'),(16,'Chelsea','A seasoned assassin working for the Revolutionary Army, having successfully carried out countless missions. While she is somewhat aloof and carefree when not on the job, she is also extremely objective and is often quite blunt when voicing her opinions.  Her Teigu, \'Gaea Foundation\', is a cosmetics box that allows her to instantly change her appearance and build at will.','2020-10-19 11:23:31','2020-10-19 11:23:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65237-6r8wMUJ6pCOF.png','MC'),(17,'Sheele','__Age:__ Mid 20\'s\n__Height:__ 160cm (5\'3)\n\nSheele is one of the members of the Assassin\'s group, Night Raid. While she seems to be clumsy and ditzy on the surface, she\'s a very caring and sweet person. She bears the Teigu \"Ecstasy\", a huge pair of scissors that can cut through anything.   ~!Growing up in the low districts of the Capital, her clumsy nature caused many people throughout her life often consider her useless, isolating her from nearly everyone. At one point in her past, she had a friend who didn\'t mind her personality but was attacked by her ex-boyfriend. Sheele killed the boyfriend in order to protect her, revealing that she had a strange talent for killing. However, in the end, this broke their friendship. Soon after, a gang-related to the man she killed earlier sought revenge against her and had already murdered her parents. Sheele defeated the group and was later scouted by the Revolutionary Army who learned of her ability.  By joining, she wanted to use her talent in a way that would make her useful to others by helping fix society. She is one of the first members to warm up to Tatsumi, comforting him while he mourned his deceased friends from his home village. Later, she is attacked by Seryuu, and killed while saving Mine from harm.!~  (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:31','2020-10-19 11:23:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65233-f8RXB4LQiNh0.png','SC'),(18,'Esdeath','__Age:__ Early 20\'s\n__Height:__ 170cm (5\'7)\n\nEsdeath is a high-ranking general of the Empire, and leader of the Jaegers. She enjoys torturing her enemies slowly, seen when she used her Teigu to put large blocks of ice in a cauldron so that the people inside would die slower and suffer more. Despite her sadistic actions, she is actually shown to have a compassionate heart when it comes to the lives of her men and others close to her.   ~!She is looking for love and although her expectations were high, when she saw Tatsumi\'s skill, she smiled and fell in love with him instantly !~  (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:32','2020-10-19 11:23:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b65239-bBwWet3ejZhu.png','MC'),(19,'Susanoo','Susanoo is one of the new members of Night Raid that Boss brought back with her from the Revolutionary Army HQ. He is a tall man with distinctive bull horns coming out of the sides of his head. He saves the members of Night Raid(except Tatsumi), who were all under the effects of a powerful poison created by Dr. Stylish. He is then caught in an explosion created by Stylish\'s exploding minions, and it is revealed that he is a Human Teigu, regenerating his lost limbs immediately.','2020-10-19 11:23:32','2020-10-19 11:23:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65559-dpDCunKgdlTL.png','SC'),(20,'Wave','Wave is a member of the Jaegers who is very similar to Tatsumi. He is from a small town on the coast where he served in the Imperial Navy, and brought a massive bag full of seafood with him when he joined the Jaegers. Also similar to Tatsumi, he is often used for Comic Relief. When he first arrived at the meeting room for his new group, he first encountered Bors, who ignored him shyly until the rest of the crew showed up.  Like Tatsumi, Wave uses a sword in combat and has formidable skills. He Wields the Armor type Teigu, \" Grand Chariot \", which is a newer version of Incursio.  (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:32','2020-10-19 11:23:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n65555-3JyIFJNbFrZn.png','SC'),(21,'Kurome','Kurome is a member of the Jaegers, and the younger sister of Akame. Like her sister, she has a big appetite and is often seen eating, usually candy. She stubbornly refuses to share her candy with even her comrades. Kurome wields an offensive Teigu like her sister, in the form of a sword named \"March of the Dead: Yatsuhusa\", which allows her to enslave up to 8 enemies killed with the Teigu. Also like her sister, she is extremely skilled in the art of the sword and assassination.  (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:32','2020-10-19 11:23:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b65297-R3DmHXnUXYIZ.png','SC'),(22,'Seryuu Ubiquitous','Age: early 20\nBlood type: A\n\nSeryuu is a member of the Jaegers, formerly of the Imperial Guard. She has a strong fixation upon \"Justice\", originating from her father\'s service in the Emperial Army and subsequent death. She also highly respected Ogre the Demon, her superior and teacher, and was heavily anguished by his death as well.\n\nHer opinion of justice is blunt, she believes the Night Raid are evil for their actions as assassins, but believes killing in service to justice is always right, which ultimately makes her opinion of murder similar to theirs if not the complete same thing. However, Seryuu has a twisted sense of right and wrong, bordering on a completely black and white view of the world. All people who serve the empire, despite the deeds they do both publicly and not, are considered good by her, while those who oppose it, even those forced to against their will, are pure evil. Her twisted view of justice has caused a level of distrust towards her by her own teammates, as well as generally the entire emperial forces, on occasion, as she brutally murdered a group of prisoners long before they could interrogate the group.\n\n (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:32','2020-10-19 11:23:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/83405-JEbhNkj3bZkA.png','MC'),(23,'Bors','A member of Jaegars, he was formerly a member of the Incineration Squad. His Teigu is Rubicante, a flamethrower type Teigu. Despite his looks he is married to an attractive woman and has a child. He always wears a mask and tries to hide his face; yet  Esdese forcefully removes his mask at one point and claims there is nothing wrong with his face.   ~!He is killed by Chelsea while trying to retreat.!~','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b65793-xRWzkHVOKqd7.png','MC'),(24,'Najenda','Najenda, also known as The Hunk of the Rebellion is the head of the assassin group Night Raid. Taciturn, sharp-minded and level-headed, she leads the group with a surprisingly gentle but firm air. Her years of experience serving in the Empire as a general have made her a highly capable leader. Najenda is sometimes mistaken as a man due to her boyish appearance, even sometimes being nicknamed \'The Hunk of the Rebellion\" by her cohorts. She tends to have a habit of telling \"cold jokes\" and making bad puns.  (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b72267-heLonNDtobAG.png','SC'),(25,'Spear','Spear was the daughter of the former Prime Minister Chouri, and a disciple of the \"Temple of the Imperial Fist\".\n\n(Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b124797-jn55Dxdykonx.png','SC'),(26,'Trooma','He is a member of Team Stylish.\n\nTrooma is one of Dr. Stylish\'s stronger henchmen. It is unknown whether he had Dr. Stylish perform experiments on him or not.','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b163230-tYYxSeRGUw9a.jpg','SC'),(27,'Mez','Mez is the daughter of Gozuki as well as a member of the Four Rakshasa Demons, who served as the Prime Minister\'s squad of executioners.\n\n(Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126276-M0j7uCQFk8mR.jpg','SC'),(28,'Mine','__Height:__ 155cm (5\'1)\n__Favourite Color:__ Pink\n\nMine is a self-proclaimed \"Genius Sniper\", as well as being a sharp-tongued and quick-witted member of the assassin\'s group, Night Raid. She is often quick to anger, and easily irritated with those she does not know well. Despite this cold exterior, she has shown to be warm and kind to those she has opened up to.  Mine wields a powerful Teigu in the form of a rifle called the \"Roman Artillery: Pumpkin\" that fires highly concentrated piercing shots of spirit energy. Her proficiency in its use allows her to strike any target with extreme precision. When Pumpkin\'s user is in a dangerous situation, the power of its shots is magnified.\n\n~!Tatsumi and Mine retired from service and settled down away from civilization where they married and had a child.!~ (Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65229-tDLiig1xOx92.png','MC'),(29,'Mei Misaki',' __Age__: Looks 14 - 15 years old\n__Occupation__: Middle School Student\n__Grade__: 3rd year, 3rd class\n__Height__: 152 cm (5\'0\'\')\n\nA mysterious, cute and isolated girl in Yomiyama North Middle School\'s third year\'s third class. Her left eye is covered by an eye patch. The girl with a mysterious presence and is always sketching alone. She is labelled as the one that \"does not exist\".   ~!Her left eye is a doll\'s eye. It can see things that should remain unseen, that\'s why she keeps it covered.  It can see people close to death or that are dead.!~','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n41402-OS8FBE4EDVZD.jpg','SC'),(30,'Misaki Fujioka','Mei\'s cousin.   ~!Mei and her are twins at birth, but due to circumstances, one was adopted.!~','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b58923-hCPBRJtv5WGL.png','MC'),(31,'Gozuki','Gozuki is the leader of the newly formed assassination squad of the Empire, the Elite Seven.\n\n(Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:33','2020-10-19 11:23:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126274-xagFDpAXo681.jpg','MC'),(32,'Daidara','Daidara is a member of Esdeath\'s former bodyguards, known as \"The Three Beasts\". He\'s a battle fanatic who will fight anyone who seems strong, and constantly takes every opportunity to improve himself when he can. He is first introduced attacking and assassinating the former Prime Minister, along with Liver and Nyau. Later, they are ordered by Esdeath to assassinate another political rival on a cruise ship. There they encountered Tatsumi and Bulat.','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127424-BF8tuLsSTRMq.jpg','SC'),(33,'Shura ','Shura is a mysterious individual who has recently begun to make his move. He seems to share his father\'s lust for power as well as his corruption but wishes to surpass him in terms of being rotten. He created and is leading the majorly corrupt and twisted Secret Police \"Wild Hunt\" to aid the Jgers and to compensate for their losses; however, he regards the empire as a toy. The incident in the theater implies he solely enjoys causing carnage.\n\nAlso much like Cosmina, Champ, and Enshin, Shura took part in the mass rape during the Umatora Theater incident where the producer denies the accusation of it\'s plays criticizing the Empire and tries to bribe Shura, but he declines the money in a heartbeat declaring the death sentence on them leading to the entire team being raped and killed by Wild Hunt in which Shura shows his twisted side by calling this action an investigation. He then mentions that this is all because Esdeath was not present in the Capital.\n\nAfter his devilish act, Shura joyfully tells his father how much of a kick he gets from leading Wild Hunt telling he made preparations to take out Night Raid. Along with his father, he watches the Great General Budo arrive.\n\n~!In Chapter 52, he tortures what he thinks is an unarmed Lubbock; however, Lubbock manages to trick Shura into removing his shackles. He then pulls some string out of his mouth and immediately kills Shura.\n!~','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b163233-8ARWDCFjWwh4.jpg','SC'),(34,'Kubikiri Zank','Zank was once an imperial executioner. Possess the Imperial Arm Spectator, that has the form of a headpiece with a large eye attached to it. He was known for severing the heads of his victims. Night Raid was contracted to track him down and kill him.','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b163223-kkhBpoiR1DPg.jpg','SC'),(35,'Run','Run is a member of the Jgers. He\'s a lover of literature. His teigu Banri Hishou Mastema is a wing type.\n\nRun is the kind of Esdeath\'s adviser, because he\'s probably the smartest person of Jgers.','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b88578-regG6GCwGmSA.png','MC'),(36,'Suzuka','Suzuka is a member of the Four Rakshasa Demons, who served as the Prime Minister\'s squad of executioners.\n\n(Source: Akame ga Kill! Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126273-91w8aUFMwwmH.jpg','SC'),(37,'Kyouko Kaneki','','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b58837-mU5U6hJ47jOk.png','SC'),(38,'Aki Matsui','A quiet student, who is a good friend of Anzu Kanaki.   ~!She is killed during the class trip, when Kazami throws a blade through her throat, just after meeting with Kouichi.!~','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/58835.jpg','SC'),(39,'Kouichi Sakakibara',' __Age__: 15 years old\n__Occupation__: Middle School Student\n__Grade__: 3rd year, 3rd class\n__Height__: 167 cm (5\'6\")\n__Weight__: 55 kg  \n\nThe new transfer student into Yomiyama North Middle School\'s third year\'s third class (in May, 1998). He is 15 years old and the only son in the Sakakibara family. His mother supposedly passed away 15 years ago after giving birth to him. He becomes very interested and curious about Mei Misaki and attempts to pursue a friendship with her, but little does he know of the trouble this is going to cause...   ~!He has pneumothorax (collapsed lung), which is the reason why he is absent from the school for a month at the start of the story. This is also the reason why he doesn\'t know Misaki was treated as \'one who does not exist\' that year.!~','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b41400-v3WD2Tz5cXo8.png','SC'),(40,'Sten','Sten is one of the Four Rakshasa Temple Demons who serve as the Prime Minister\'s squad of executioners. He seems to think of murdering as \"releasing one\'s soul.\"\n\nSten is a large man with a heavily muscled build similar to Ibara. He has a long braided hairstyle with hair sticking far out at the sides and bald at the top of his head. He has long bushy beard and mustache, bushy eyebrows, and dark prominent circles around his eyes. Similar to his fellow Rakshasa Demons, he wears armor plating on his forearms. He also wears a large Iron pauldron on his left shoulder.\n\n~!In Chapter 36, Lubbock hits him with a spear made of threads. Sten is able to withstand the attack, but Lubbock uses the threads that pierced Sten\'s body to cut his heart into pieces.!~','2020-10-19 11:23:34','2020-10-19 11:23:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b163242-SmXjdRNRLn1w.jpg','MC'),(41,'Nagisa Shiota','He is one of students in Class 3-E. Nagisa is seen as one of the weakest students in the class due to his small stature and mediocre physical abilities that are comparable to a girl. However, he is actually the most talented to become an assassin out of all the students, something that acknowledged by Korosensei and Karasuma. He is able to draw closer while hiding his bloodlust to make a surprise attack and able to make his opponents falter through his bloodlust alone.  Nagisa usually writes Korosensei\'s weaknesses that at first seen minor (since it doesn\'t look like major weaknesses), but eventually revealed to be useful since once they\'re able to almost kill Korosensei because of one of his weaknesses that is the same as the one that Nagisa has written down in his note.  Outwardly friendly and polite to his friends and everyone, he hides a somewhat darker side of him as an assassin that won\'t be able to be found out during daily classes and will only shown during training and assassination time. According to Karasuma, whenever Nagisa unleashes his killing intent, he isn\'t training and truly goes for a kill.','2020-10-19 11:23:37','2020-10-19 11:23:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65645-o6Rjx8ud8gmM.png','SC'),(42,'Karma Akabane','Karma Akabane is a student in Korosensei\'s class 3-E of Kunugigaoka Junior High School who had been suspended from school due to his violent behavior.  He excels at using weaponry and foul play and is the only student thus far to have successfully injured Korosensei. Despite this, he is actually rather smart and manages a perfect score on one of Korosensei\'s tests. He and Nagisa were in the same class during their 1st and 2nd years at Kunugigaoka.  (Source: Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:23:37','2020-10-19 11:23:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b71933-IrwW73MpAh9j.jpg','SC'),(43,'Tadaomi Karasuma','He is a government worker associated with the Ministry of Defense. He first appeared announcing Korosensei\'s deal with the government and their mission to assassinate him before the end of the year. He later became the assistant teacher and P.E. instructor of class 3-E, using his lessons to train the students in assassination techniques. He is well known among militaries for his outstanding reputation and is a powerful individual, which he has proven when he easily overpowered Irina\'s master, who is a retired professional hitman, and even Korosensei himself is afraid upon seeing his capability for the first time. He is strict, but kind man, though he keeps a distance between himself and the students due to his status as an agent and his own professionalism. He is one of a few who is very perceptive enough to see Nagisa\'s talent as an assassin. He seems to know Korosensei\'s past, though he has no intention to indulge into it further.\n<br>\n(Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:23:37','2020-10-19 11:23:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/73881-Ukr6cBzK8dsi.png','MC'),(44,'Koro-sensei','Koro-sensei () is a teacher for class 3-E of Kunugigaoka Junior High School and the main antihero of Ansatsu Kyoushitsu. He claims responsibility for blowing up the moon into a permanent crescent shape and plans to destroy the Earth in a year after teaching the students of class 3-E the art of assassination. His name comes from korosenai (), meaning \"cannot be killed\", and sensei (), meaning teacher. In this way, he is literally called the unkillable teacher.','2020-10-19 11:23:37','2020-10-19 11:23:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/65643-536fzzXqiIYD.jpg','MC'),(45,'Kaede Kayano','She is one of Nagisa\'s classmates and close friends, being the one who is mostly seen with him. She hasn\'t shown any capabilities during her training to become an assassin, and so far has only been shown to discuss Korosensei\'s weaknesses along with Nagisa. She experiences a slight inferiority complex when it comes to sex appeal, resulting her to get angry whenever there\'s a woman with big breasts and readily protest.','2020-10-19 11:23:37','2020-10-19 11:23:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85291-io7X60xBW1LK.jpg','SC'),(46,'Megu Kataoka','She is a student of Kunugigaoka Junior High School. She is assigned to Class 3-E, where she trains to become a professional assassin, with her teacher as the target. She is one of the two class representatives of Class 3-E, with the other being Yma Isogai.  (Source: Ansatsu Kyoushitsu Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:23:37','2020-10-19 11:23:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85799-z6SKUG1Zf1lo.png','MC'),(47,'Yuma Isogai','He is a student and class rep in class 3-E of Kunugigaoka Junior High School, taught by Korosensei. ','2020-10-19 11:23:38','2020-10-19 11:23:38','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b85801-g9riqQUgVilK.jpg','SC'),(48,'Irina Jelavic','Age: 20 years \nHeight: 170cm \nWeight: 50 kg \nOccupation: Professional Hitman, Part-time Foreign Language Teacher \nThree sizes: B97 W60 H91 \n\nShe is a professional hitwoman who is hired to kill Korosensei by becoming a part-time foreign language teacher in class 3-E. She uses her charms to seduce Korosensei, making him at first obeys to whatever she asks. However, her first assassination attempt was foiled when Korosensei able to suppressed her 3-men\'s attacks, ending in her humiliation and swore revenge. She teaches the students how to seduce people from other countries, so that with this method, they can learn foreign languages, and usually would punish male students who failed answering her questions during her lesson by kissing them.    \n\nPersonality: Irina is a deceitful, wily and beguiling individual; she frequently uses her charm to influence and manipulate her targets. She can easily befriend people, if she so chooses, and entice them to let down their defenses and become vulnerable to her.Seduction is primarily the technique she employs, and it is her area of expertise. Irina is a professional assassin who excels at handling infiltration and approaching targets. She possesses strong conversational skills in ten languages, and a proven track record of eleven jobs in countries all over the world.She boasts of her own capability and greatnessshe has passionately stated that others in the same room as her should be grateful.Irina looks down on others, especially kids, who she believes are not commensurate to her excellence in performance.Her haughtiness is often considered detestable, and she particularly clashes with the students of Class 3-E. However, when enlightened of the necessity to work together with the students and the significance of them, she corrects her condescension, and learns to be more humble.  She\'s nicknamed Bitch-nee-san by her students since she\'s prohibited them to call her by her first name and later became Bitch-sensei after her students has acknowledged her as their teacher. \n\nShe got her nickname \"-bitch\" from the end of her last name \"Jela-vic.\" Since Japanese often pronounce \"V\" as \"B\", hence -vic become -bic/-bitch.','2020-10-19 11:23:38','2020-10-19 11:23:38','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/73883-wMRHLvqOVKqJ.jpg','MC'),(49,'Yuzuki Fuwa','She is a student in class 3-E of Kunugigaoka Junior High School, taught by Korosensei.   Fuwa has an imaginative personality, as evidenced with her like of reading the Weekly Shnen Jump magazine. ','2020-10-19 11:23:38','2020-10-19 11:23:38','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85815-DmGWlh9hKrYZ.png','SC'),(50,'Taiga Okajima','He is a student in Korosensei\'s class 3-E of Kunugigaoka Junior High School.   Okajima is the class pervert and is rather open about it. As with Rio Nakamura, Okajima is known to like peeping. He likes to read erotica magazines and even claimed to be a brother of Korosensei and Itona Horibe for doing so. At the start of July, he enjoys looking at the girls\' more exposed skin. ','2020-10-19 11:23:38','2020-10-19 11:23:38','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85813-L0gtF4nfiN1t.png','SC'),(51,'Taisei Yoshida','He is a student of Kunugigaoka Junior High School. He is assigned to Class 3-E, where he trains to become a professional assassin, with his teacher as the target. His partners are Ryma Terasaka and Takuya Muramatsu.   Yoshida is an inconsiderate individual, unmindful to the consequences of his actions. He is willing to resort to any means in order to escape contemptible circumstances. He collaborates with Ryma Terasaka and Takuya Muramatsu, and together they pressure others to act according to their bidding. ','2020-10-19 11:23:39','2020-10-19 11:23:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85811-wV4VTP3IT1Ep.png','SC'),(52,'Ryouma Terasaka','He is a student of Kunugigaoka Junior High School. He is assigned to Class 3-E, where he trains to become a professional assassin, with his teacher as the target. His partners are Takuya Muramatsu and Taiji Yoshida.   Terasaka is a rash, selfish and impatient individual. Desperate to escape from the miserable circumstances of being part of the dropout class, he is willing to resort to any means, even if the methods may be immoral.He holds no regards for the injuries of his comrades who provide assistance.  However, Terasaka possesses relative leadership skills, as he is usually accompanied by his peers, Takuya Muramatsu and Taiji Yoshida.He persuades others to do his bidding by being direct and intrusively forward, as indicated when he pressures Nagisa Shiota to carry out an assassination of Korosensei by reminding him of the harsh conditions they live in.','2020-10-19 11:23:39','2020-10-19 11:23:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85809-nsZ8abs93o9r.png','MC'),(53,'Koutarou Takebayashi','','2020-10-19 11:23:39','2020-10-19 11:23:39','https://s4.anilist.co/f