n\'s attacks, ending in her humiliation and swore revenge. She teaches the students how to seduce people from other countries, so that with this method, they can learn foreign languages, and usually would punish male students who failed answering her questions during her lesson by kissing them.    \n\nPersonality: Irina is a deceitful, wily and beguiling individual; she frequently uses her charm to influence and manipulate her targets. She can easily befriend people, if she so chooses, and entice them to let down their defenses and become vulnerable to her.Seduction is primarily the technique she employs, and it is her area of expertise. Irina is a professional assassin who excels at handling infiltration and approaching targets. She possesses strong conversational skills in ten languages, and a proven track record of eleven jobs in countries all over the world.She boasts of her own capability and greatnessshe has passionately stated that others in the same room as her should be grateful.Irina looks down on others, especially kids, who she believes are not commensurate to her excellence in performance.Her haughtiness is often considered detestable, and she particularly clashes with the students of Class 3-E. However, when enlightened of the necessity to work together with the students and the significance of them, she corrects her condescension, and learns to be more humble.  She\'s nicknamed Bitch-nee-san by her students since she\'s prohibited them to call her by her first name and later became Bitch-sensei after her students has acknowledged her as their teacher. \n\nShe got her nickname \"-bitch\" from the end of her last name \"Jela-vic.\" Since Japanese often pronounce \"V\" as \"B\", hence -vic become -bic/-bitch.','2020-10-19 11:23:45','2020-10-19 11:23:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/73883-wMRHLvqOVKqJ.jpg','SC'),(91,'Yukio Okumura',' __Age:__ 15 \n __Date of Birth:__ December 27  \n__Height:__ 180 cm (5\' 11\") \n __Weight:__ 154 lbs (70 kg)  \n__Blood:__ Type O \n __Pastimes and talents:__ Formulating plans, mixing in with a crowd, reading Jump Square every month  \n__Average hours of sleep per night:__ 4  \n__Favorite foods:__ Seafood (especially sashimi)  \n__Favorite manga genres:__ Gags/comedy, horror, suspense/mystery  \n__Favorite type of girl:__ ...  \n__Details:__ Popular with girls. Extremely poor eyesight. Ambidextrous Embarrassed by how many moles he has.  \n\nYukio is Rin Okumura\'s twin and younger brother and Shiro Fujimoto\'s adopted son. He is a Middle First Class Exorcist who has started his training to become an Exorcist at seven by his father suggestion and, since then, gained the titles of Dragoon and Doctor at only fourteen, becoming the youngest Exorcist in the True Cross Order history. Yukio is also the youngest teacher of the True Cross\' Exorcist Cram School, at which he teaches pharmacology. Before he was born, he has had a weak body that couldn\'t bear the power of the blue flames, causing the power of Satan to be fully inherited by Rin. He is seen as an example and prodigy by the ones who live together with him and is friends with Shiemi Moriyama, who calls him Yuki-chan.\n\n(Source: viz and Blue Exorcist volume one manga extras)','2020-10-19 11:23:46','2020-10-19 11:23:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b24734-GgVZoNAPnxoc.png','MC'),(92,'Yuri Frederick Egin','Yuri Egin is the daughter of the Candial and Yukio and Rin&#039;s Mother.   (Rin and Yukio&#039;s mother has so far only been shown and named in the anime.)    ~!Yuri let herself voluntarily be possessed by Satan and give birth to his children to prove that humans and demons could live and love together. She died after she gave birth to Rin and Yukio. !~','2020-10-19 11:23:47','2020-10-19 11:23:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b48511-FfvuZ6i6Czep.png','SC'),(93,'Shura Kirigakure','She reveals herself in chapter 9, before that she had her face hidden beneath a hooded sweater and was known as Yamada.   The only information received in the manga so far is that she is an upper first class exorcist and a senior inspector. She was dispatched by the True Cross Vatican Headquarters to investigate the Japanese Branch\'s \"risk factor\".  2 years before Rin was born, she was Fujimoto Shirou\'s student.  She claims to be 18, but in chapter 11 Yukio said that she already turned 26, and she seems sensitive about her age, as she threw a beer can at him claiming \'her hand slipped\' shortly after','2020-10-19 11:23:47','2020-10-19 11:23:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b32110-pGZbTcYfIy4l.png','MC'),(94,'Amaimon',' __Race:__ Demons  __Height:__ 172 cm (5\'7\")  __Weight:__ 58 kg  Also known as the \"Earth King.\" Amaimon is supposedly the second son of Satan and another Demon Prince of Gehenna. Unlike his father and elder brother Mephisto, Amaimon had little interest in Rin after their first encounter.   He is a human-like demon. He has a spike of hair which is lightly colored compared to the rest of his dark green hair. He wears a jacket that has cross bones as buttons. He also wears a long sleeved green shirt under his jacket, which is ripped at the ends.   He appears to be calm and collected, but very confident in his powers. However he shows great anger and annoyance when someone gets in the way of his fun. He is very playful and doesn\'t take things seriously when it comes to fighting strong combatants which hints that he is very skilled in combat.  (Source: Ao No Exorcist Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:23:47','2020-10-19 11:23:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b30433-BksZVnkRVy07.png','MC'),(95,'Rin Okumura','Age: 15\nDate of Birth: December 27 1995 \nHair: Navy Blue \nEyes: Blue \nHeight: 173 cm (5\' 8\")  \nWeight: 63 kg (138 lb)  \nBlood: Type A \nPastimes and talents: Cooking, sleeping, eating, spacing out \nAverage hours of sleep per night: 12\nFavorite foods: Sukiyaki (with any kind of ingredients) \nFavorite manga genres: Battle/action, comedy, emotional drama \nFavorite type of girl: Cute, shy girls  \nDetails: Surprisingly good with his hands. Cooking repertoire includes all kinds of Japanese and Western foods (home cuisine) \nQuote:  \"Yukio!! I swear to god I\'ll surpass you!!, just you watch!\"  - \"I\'ll become an exorcist and kick Satan\'s ass!\"\n\nThe fifteen-year-old protagonist of the story, Rin is the son of Satan born from a human woman and is the inheritor of Satan\'s powers. His powers were sealed at birth into the demon-slaying blade Kurikara, or Koumaken, by Mephisto Pheles, allowing him to live a normal human life for about 15 years. Rin became aware of his true identity after Kurikara could no longer seal the blue flames he inherited from Satan, setting a chain of events that led to the death of his guardian, Father and Exorcist Fujimoto Shiro, at the hands of Satan who attempted to drag Rin back to the demon realm. Exorcist Mephisto Pheles confronted Rin after Shiro\'s funeral with several exorcists, giving Rin the option to kill them all or die. Rin instead demanded to become an exorcist, an idea that amused Mephisto. Rin was then enrolled personally by Mephisto into the True Cross Academy Exorcist School, and since been pursuing his goal to become a Paladin and to defeat Satan. He is currently an Exwire and attempting to gain the title of Meister as a \"Knight\". Rin can tap into the power he has inherited from Satan through the use of a demon-slaying katana, called Kurikara or Koumaken. The sheath acts as a portal to Gehenna (the demon world) which when drawn returns Rin to his demon form. While in his human form, Rin exhibits a number of physical traits that are signs of his demonic nature, such as sharper-looking teeth, slightly pointed ears, and a black, fur tufted tail (which he keeps hidden in his shirt). As a demon, Rin gains two blue flames that float above his head, long, elf-like ears, and his eyes turn bright blue. In both forms Rin can almost control his destructive bright blue flames, the trademark sign of Satan. However, when he draws Kurikara, the magnitude of the flames dramatically increase and often leads to Rin being \"consumed\" by his own flames and losing his mind. Rin also has a demon Familiar Cat Sith, Kuro, who was initially Father Fujimoto\'s.  \n(Sources: Viz, Blue Exorcist volume one manga extras)','2020-10-19 11:23:47','2020-10-19 11:23:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n24482-lvOeN02vmDQI.jpg','MC'),(96,'Satan','Satan is the king of Gehenna. It has been said that he is the creator of every demon in existence. There is no body in Assiah powerful enough to host him because of his incredible powers.    Source: Wiki','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b48449-LZibifWzcpoo.png','SC'),(97,'Ryuuji Suguro',' __Date of Birth:__ August 20  __Age:__ 16  __Height:__ 181 cm  __Weight:__ 76 kg  __Blood:__ B  __Pastimes and talents:__ Memorization, cleaning, Zen meditation  __Average bath time:__ 20 minutes  __Favorite words:__ Karma  __Favorite music genres:__ Rock, American/European, Japanese  __How he spends days off:__ Cleaning, meditating, about two hours weight lifting or jogging  __Details:__ A bit of a neat freak Gets migraines Worries about his tendency to glare  Suguro Ryuji (nicknamed \"Bon\") is Rin\'s rival and the prodigy in the class. He was the child of the Cursed Temple which was destroyed by Satan 16 years ago. Bon takes everything seriously and is trying his hardest in order to become an Exorcist powerful enough so he could one day defeat Satan ( a goal he claims Rin stole from him) and rebuild his Temple. Currently Bon is trying to acquire the title of Meister in both Aria (a person who recites holy texts to kill certain demons) and Dragoon (a person who fights with heavy artillery). He is currently an Exwire.   (Sources: Wikipedia and the Blue Exorcist volume two manga extras)','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b30429-Wm58gjdzncFj.png','MC'),(98,'Shirou Fujimoto',' __Date of Birth:__ May 10th  __Height:__ 177 cm (5\' 8\")  __Weight:__ 137 lbs (62 kg)  __Blood:__ Type AB  __Pastimes and talents:__ Collecting dirty books, taking care of his glasses, falling asleep anywhere and anytime  __Average hours of sleep per night:__ 6  __Favorite foods:__ Oden (especially Japanese radish)  __Favorite manga genres:__ Romance, emotional drama, social drama  __Favorite type of girl:__ Ones with big boobs  __Details:__ Has known Mephisto for a long time Hasn\'t smoked for 15 years  Father Fujimoto was Rin and Yukio\'s guardian and was also considered to be one of the most powerful Exorcists in the world. He was thought to be the only man in the world that was able to sustain possession by Satan himself and thus Satan was constantly after his body. Fujimoto was able to fought off Satan\'s attempts at possessing his body through sheer willpower. However after receiving a mental shock from what Rin had said, Satan was finally able to take over his body and later killed him. Fujimoto had a familiar sith cat demon, which he called Kuro, that Rin has inherited. He was a confirmed Aria, Dragoon and tamer and could possibly have been a Knight and a Docter as two of those who have studied under him have become these. He was said to be the strongest exorcist on the planet and was the only one to gain the rank of Paladin, the highest rank of the exorcists.   Source: viz, Blue Exorcist volume one manga extras','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b30431-l5NMqfM82w4q.png','SC'),(99,'Igor Neuhaus','Birthday: November 13 Nationality: Polish  An Upper First Class Exorcist as well as lecturer in the Academy, who obtained the titles of Tamer, Doctor and Aria. He wears an eyepatch over his left eye, while he has Aria incantations tattooed on both arms.   He had a run-in with Satan when he was younger, which robbed him of his family and his left eye\'s sight, which is why he holds immense hatred for Satan and demons that are related to Satan. Yet ironically, he is extremely loyal to Mephisto, willing to listen to any command of his, which is why he stopped his attacks on Rin prior to the latter becoming an Exorcist.','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b38985-pW70uJHQONhK.png','MC'),(100,'Renzou Shima',' __Date of Birth:__ July 4  __Age:__ 15  __Height:__ 176 cm  __Weight:__ 63 kg  __Blood:__ O  __Pastimes and talents:__ Smiling, lying, fake politeness, buying dirty books even when a girl is working the cash register  __Average bath time:__ 30 minutes  __Favorite words:__ They\'re not fit for print  __Favorite music genres:__ Rock, pop, R&amp;amp;B, hip-hop, American/European, Japanese  __How he spends days off:__ Dating girls  __Details:__ His hair is brown tinged with pink His nickname in elementary school was the erotic demon Trying to be more refined in high school  Renzou is a very carefree character, yet he has a fear of many things, mainly bugs. He\'s very loyal to Bon, his childhood friend. They grew up together along with Konekomaru in Kyoto. He is also has a big obsession with women. Plans to become a Meister in Aria He is the 5th and youngest son of his family, and tells Konekomaru he\'s glad of this because it means he has less responsibilities. His older brother Juuzou says he\'s the pervert out of the brothers. He has pink (dyed) hair. It is naturally black. In the manga, Renzou wears a man-tailored (flannel sort of) shirt over a t-shirt with a symbol, sort of like a bulls-eye. Renzou also carries around K\'rik (Khakkhara) staff, which he and his two brothers also have. Renzou is a carefree character and was the first person to actually befriend Rin since the revealing of the blue flames, which shows Renzou is the friendly-type. He is also afraid of bugs, yet he is known as the pervert out of the Shima brothers. Renzou was born into the temple that Bon and Konekumaru was in as well, making him the childhood friend of the two.  Source: http://aonoexorcist.wikia.com Source: Blue Exorcist volume two manga extras','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b38983-NrEXYWsAzm68.jpg','SC'),(101,'Shiemi Moriyama',' __Age:__ 15  \n__Date of Birth:__ March 6  \n__Eyes:__ Green  \n__Height:__ 165 cm (5\' 4\")  \n__Weight:__ 49 kg (108 lbs)  \n__Blood:__ Type B  \n__Favorite food:__ Herb cookies from her grandmother.  \n__Pastimes and Talents:__ Gardening, making herbal teas, naming plants and flowers, baking cookies, lying in the sun  \n\nSlightly allergic to pollen.  Shiemi is Rin\'s classmate and friend. Before she met Rin, Shiemi tended her grandmother\'s garden while her mother ran an Exorcist only shop inside True Cross Academy. During her encounter with Rin and Yukio, they were able to discover that Shiemi was having her life force leached out by a Demon. After Yukio exorcised the demon, Shiemi finally decided to become an Exorcist and started to attend class. It was later revealed that Shiemi had talent in becoming a Tamer, as she was able to summon a Greenman Spirit during class. It is apparently a rare talent to possess amongst the Exorcists, where there are only a few who can control demons and fight. \n\n(Source: Blue Exorcist manga volume one extras)','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b30430-5Z6ZTgU0AqRo.png','SC'),(102,'Reiji Shiratori','He\'s a boy of Rin\'s age who\'s about to go to True Cross Academy, but since he\'s a bit of a delinquent in his free time he finds that he must pay Rin to keep his mouth shut about it since Rin saw him when he was about to kill some birds with a crossbow.    ~!He\'s later possessed by a demon named Astaroth. When he finds out that Rin\'s also a demon, he tries to get him so he can bring Rin to Gehenna.!~','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b42208-m2qTsuHUCnpi.png','SC'),(103,'Arthur Auguste Angel','The newly appointed Paladin. He was ordered by the Grigori to to interrogate Mephisto and captured Rin as evidence. According to Shura he\'s a saint on the outside and a devil inside. Uses the demon sword Caliburn.   __Appearance__ Angel has long blonde hair in a pony tail, with a communicator in his ear, though it is unclear whether or not he wears it all the time. He wears a fancy white suit that is custom made. Rin makes fun of it.    __Personality__ Not much is known about Arthur so far, except that he is extremely loyal to the True Cross Order. He follows the orders of his superiors without questioning them at all, even attempting to kill people when they interfere with his work. He believes that anything related to Satan must be destroyed, as it could only cause harm to let them live. Arthur also seems to be slightly sadistic, as he stabbed Rin completely through the leg to immobilize him during Rin\'s trial, while remarking that the wound would heal soon enough. According to Shura, he is a saint on the outside and a devil on the inside, hinting that he may have a malicious personality.    __Powers &amp; Abilities__ Despite not being seen in combat, it can be assumed that Arthur is extremely powerful, as he was given the rank of Paladin, which only the strongest exorcist in the world can hold. He wields a demon sword, called Caliburn, indicating that he obtained a Meister as a Knight.   His power is hinted at when he was quickly able to overcome Kirigakure Shura, one of the most powerful exorcists seen in the series.  Caliburn his demon blade, seems to be able to talk, and has the personality of a little girl who adores Arthur. He\'s willing to cut some of his hair, using Caliburn, in exchange for power.   (Source: Ao no Exorcist Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b34758-XzvetamkXXVQ.png','MC'),(104,'Noriko Paku','Noriko is Izumo\'s best friend but quits the cram school because she did not understand the classes and she was failing.','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b43239-jnFBSkQSQ2FE.png','SC'),(105,'Kuro','A two-tailed cat demon (nekomata).  Formerly Fujimoto\'s familiar but is now Rin\'s familiar.  Kuro is a Cat Sith who was once worshipped as a protective deity for silkworms.  He usually takes the appearance of a kitten, but he can reach an enormous size at will.\n','2020-10-19 11:23:48','2020-10-19 11:23:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b43187-uJySWMkmaWmZ.png','MC'),(106,'Youhei','He appeared in the 11th episode of the anime.     ','2020-10-19 11:23:49','2020-10-19 11:23:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b45969-1HovUV9Q5Diz.png','SC'),(107,'Michelle Neuhaus','The wife of Igor Neuhaus, she was killed on the Blue Night.   ~!But was brought back to life by someone. She was also the masked man who hunt Rin and kept the True Cross Academy students hostage.   She only appears in the anime.!~ (Source: Blue Exorcist Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:23:49','2020-10-19 11:23:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b49367-V2yxyWzgePa7.png','MC'),(108,'Kaoru Tsubaki','The Physical Education (P.E.) teacher in the cram school. Called by some students as &quot;Ol&#039; Sideburns&quot;, he is well known to abruptly cancel and/or leave class upon recieving a call from a woman currently identified only as &#039;Kitten&#039;, which is the name he calls her.     (Source: BlueExorcist.wikia)','2020-10-19 11:23:49','2020-10-19 11:23:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b49369-ZIHUMtyF9SiK.png','MC'),(109,'Ernst Frederick Egin','Yuri\'s father and Rin and Yukio\'s grandfather. 