rasuno High \nAge: 15 \nHeight: 188.3 cm \nWeight: 68.4 kg \nBirthday: September 27 \nYear: 1st year, class 4 \nNumber: 11 \nPosition: Middle Blocker  \n\nA member of the Karasuno High volleyball club. He often looks down on Hinata stating that he should not only rely on his jump. He also teases Kageyama calling him \"The king\" which angers him to the core. He is best friends with fellow Karasuno member Yamaguchi Tadashi, often reserving his kindness and love for him. He is standoffish and has an arrogant and condescending personality, while also struggling with the inner conflicts with his own personal demons. Although he is only outwardly close with Yamaguchi, he can be seen occasionally caring about his other club members.','2020-10-19 11:26:27','2020-10-19 11:26:27','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b67329-BaxY9PNMEWjL.jpg','SC'),(756,'Tadashi Yamaguchi','Team: Karasuno High \nAge: 15 \nHeight: 179.5 cm \nWeight: 63 kg \nBirthday: November 10 \nYear: 1st year, class 4 \nNumber: 12 \nPosition: Middle Blocker  \n\nYamaguchi always hangs out with Tsukishima and is very protective of him. He has trained himself hard to use a jump float serve. He is also a substitute ace server of the Karasuno Volleyball team.','2020-10-19 11:26:27','2020-10-19 11:26:27','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b71609-5Ht0aqB34eEa.png','SC'),(757,'Tobio Kageyama','Team: Karasuno High, Kitagawa Daiichi Junior High (former) \nAge: 15 \nHeight: 180.6 cm \nWeight: 66.3 kg \nBirthday: December 22 \nYear: 1st Year, class 3 \nNumber: 9 \nPosition: Setter \nFavorite Food: Pork curry with a soft-boiled egg on top \nCurrent Concerns: He\'s worried that animals seem to dislike him \nAbility Parameters (out of 5): Power = 4; jump = 4; stamina = 5; intellect = 5; technique = 5; speed = 4  \n\nA famous setter in his middle school who joins the Karusuno High Volleyball team. He was known as the \"King of the Court\" in his middle school because of his arrogant demeanor and the way he would order around his teammates. Although he still carries an overbearing attitude, he begins to change when he starts to play with Hinata Shouyou who views him as a rival.','2020-10-19 11:26:27','2020-10-19 11:26:27','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b64771-cS4Bbbs8Yvpz.png','SC'),(758,'Chikara Ennoshita','Team: Karasuno High \nAge: 16 \nHeight: 175.4 cm \nWeight: 66.4 kg \nBirthday: December 26 \nYear: 2nd year, class 4 \nPosition: Wing Spiker','2020-10-19 11:26:28','2020-10-19 11:26:28','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n67331-skTD3AJ7jrWr.png','SC'),(759,'Asahi Azumane','Team: Karasuno High \nAge: 17 \nHeight: 184.7 cm \nWeight: 75.2 kg \nBirthday: January 1 \nYear: 3rd year, class 3 \nNumber: 3 \nPosition: Wing Spiker','2020-10-19 11:26:28','2020-10-19 11:26:28','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/67333-2WDTI5mL8k9Y.jpg','SC'),(760,'Kiyoko Shimizu','Team: Karasuno High\nAge: 17\nHeight: 166.2 cm\nWeight: 51.4 kg\nBirthday: January 6\nYear: 3rd Year, class 2 \n\nThe manager of the Karasuno High volleyball club.','2020-10-19 11:26:28','2020-10-19 11:26:28','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b67689-5ZgvIYEVvBd6.png','MC'),(761,'Keishin Ukai','Team: Karasuno High \nAge: 26 \nHeight: 178.2 cm \nWeight: 72.2 kg \nBirthday: April 5  \n\nKarasuno High School volleyball club\'s alumnus, currently coaching volleyball club and helping out his mother at the shop.','2020-10-19 11:26:28','2020-10-19 11:26:28','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n70861-ML1y9YWWrdlB.png','MC'),(762,'Koushi Sugawara','__Team:__ Karasuno High \n__Age:__ 17 \n__Height:__ 174.3 cm \n__Weight:__ 63.5 kg \n__Birthday:__ June 13 \n__Year:__ 3rd year, class 4 \n__Number:__ 2 \n__Position:__ Setter \n__Favorite Food:__ Super spicy mapo tofu \n__Current Concerns:__ That there are a lot of kouhai taller than him \n__Ability Parameters (out of 5):__ Power = 2; jump = 2; stamina = 2; intellect = 4; technique = 4; speed = 2  \n\nBeing the vice captain, Sugawara has a soothing personality for his teammates and acts as a pillar of support for them. Even though he isn\'t Karasuno\'s official setter anymore, he doesn\'t dream of giving up on playing in general. As such, he encourages himself and all of his teammates not to give up, no matter how rough the situation might be.\n\nSugawara\'s dedication to volleyball is clear when he decides to continue club activities even when most third years choose to retire to focus on their futures. In a meeting, his teacher asked Sugawara why he\'s so determined to continue playing even though he\'s not a starting member, and Sugawara replied that he doesn\'t want to have regrets in the future.\n\nHe is also quite perceptive as he noticed how Tanaka asked for the key to the gym (back during the first years\'s 3-on-3 match) even though he always comes in late, so Sugawara knew that something was up. He is also intelligent as he can come up with helpful tactics during the game. An example of this is when he came up with the idea of saying \"bring it\" and \"send it to me\" for Kageyama and Hinata\'s combo.\n\n(Source: Haikyuu!! Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:26:28','2020-10-19 11:26:28','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b67321-mvoj64wNIoKo.jpg','SC'),(763,'Ittetsu Takeda','Team: Karasuno High \nAge: 29 \nHeight: 166.5 cm \nWeight: 59.4 kg \nBirthday: January 10  \n\nVolleyball club faculty advisor of the Karasuno High School.  Takeda is inexperienced in volleyball, but still became an advisor for Karasuno. He often doesn\'t understand rules and that\'s why takes notes about every new thing he learns. Takeda has enthusiastic and brave personality.','2020-10-19 11:26:29','2020-10-19 11:26:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n73679-OS9fOsMjSJua.png','MC'),(764,'Hitoka Yachi','Age: 15\nTeam: Karasuno High \nPosition: Manager\nOccupation: High School Student (1st Year, Class 5)','2020-10-19 11:26:29','2020-10-19 11:26:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89124-pVCtbWX1TWr6.jpg','SC'),(765,'Satori Tendo','Age:	18\nDate of birth:	May 20\nHeight:	187.7cm (6\' 1.9\")\nWeight:	71.1kg (156.7 lbs)\nHome town:	Miyagi Prefecture\nHome country:	Japan\nLikes:\nShounen Jump\nChocolate Ice Cream\nCute Actresses\nJumping Reach: 327 cm\n\nSatori Tend is a third year middle blocker in Shiratorizawa Academy. He is often referred to as Guess Monster by other teams. He is cheerful and loud, though a bit sardonic. Tend enjoys teasing both his teammates and opponents, usually annoying the latter. However, when he gets into the game, he becomes a different, more intimidating person, relishing the look of defeat on people\'s faces when they are denied. He has a high success rate with this blocking style due to his analytical skills and predictions, thus he is confident in his abilities . He also greatly values the fun aspect of volleyball.\n\n~!As an elementary student, he was called a monster for his looks also probably due to the meaning of his name (Satori refers to a Yokai) and was told he couldn\'t join the volleyball team by other students because of that. Using his guess block, he was able to block the spike of one of his bullies. This event made him feel happy and he continued to use his unique blocking technique to feel that way again despite much opposition until high school. Since his guess block got a lot of points, the Shiratorizawa coach let him join the team without resistance.!~','2020-10-19 11:26:29','2020-10-19 11:26:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b126073-MVwax8GNur2c.jpg','MC'),(766,'Wakatoshi Ushijima','Team: Shiratorizawa Academy\nAge: 18\nBirthday: August 13\nHeight: 189.5 cm (6\' 2.6\")\nWeight: 84.8 kg (187 lbs)\nYear: 3rd Year, Class 3\nNumber: 1\nPosition: Wing Spiker\nFavorite Food: Hayashi rice\nCurrent Concern: None.\nAbility Parameters (out of 5): Power = 5; Jump = 5; Stamina = 5; Intellect = 3; Technique = 3; Speed = 3\n\nWakatoshi Ushijima is a third year at Shiratorizawa Academy and the captain and ace of the school\'s boys\' volleyball team. Currently, he is the number one ace in Miyagi Prefecture and one of the country\'s top three aces, along with Sakusa and Kiryu. Left handed.','2020-10-19 11:26:29','2020-10-19 11:26:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/76816-g4krhMj8CUpF.png','SC'),(767,'Taichi Kawanishi','__Date of Birth:__ April 15, 1995\n__Height:__ 188.3 cm (6\' 2.1\")\n__Weight:__ 74.0 kg (163.1 lbs)\n__Likes:__ Sukiyaki\n__Hometown:__ Miyagi Prefecture\n\n__Introduction:__\nTaichi Kawanishi is a second year middle blocker at Shiratorizawa Academy.\n\n__Personality:__\nHe doesn\'t talk to his teammates very often, and appears mostly emotionless, only looking annoyed on occasion. He has been seen crying once. He doesn\'t seem to put much effort into his playing and sometimes accidentally lets a ball in; however, since he\'s a starting member in Shiratorizawa, his abilities shouldn\'t be too low. Tend has noted that Kawanishi has an eclectic and more analytical blocking style, which the third year\'s a little annoyed by; Kawanishi would use guess blocking on occasions and switch back to read blocking when needed. He also won\'t fight any uncertain battles.\n\n(Source: [Haikyuu!! Fandom Wikia](https://haikyuu.fandom.com/wiki/Taichi_Kawanishi))','2020-10-19 11:26:29','2020-10-19 11:26:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137538-rd1nDDPYjcs6.jpg','SC'),(768,'Eita Semi','__Date of Birth:__ November 11, 1994\n__Height:__ 179.5 cm (5\' 10.7\")\n__Weight:__ 70.5 kg (155.4 lbs)\n__Likes:__ Tekka Maki\n__Hometown:__ Miyagi Prefecture\n\n__Introduction:__\nEita Semi is a third year setter in Shiratorizawa Academy. Like most members of the Shiratorizawa Boys\' Volleyball Team, Semi got into the school through a sports scholarship. He was a famous setter during his time at middle school and the main setter for Shiratorizawa before being replaced by Shirabu.\n\n__Personality:__\nHe appears serious and stoic, but is actually hot-headed and competitive, partially also towards Shirabu, who had taken his spot as the team\'s starting setter. Despite that, Semi acknowledges Shirabu\'s and his opponents\' strengths and abilities. He also cares about his teammates and is occasionally sincere and nice.\n\n(Source: [Haikyuu!! Fandom Wikia](https://haikyuu.fandom.com/wiki/Eita_Semi))','2020-10-19 11:26:29','2020-10-19 11:26:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137535-BmEmUBbBKRjQ.png','MC'),(769,'Tooru Oikawa','__Team:__ Aoba Josai High, Kitagawa Daiichi (former) \n__Age:__ 18 \n__Height:__ 184.3 cm \n__Weight:__ 72.2 kg \n__Birthday:__ July 20 \n__Year:__ 3rd Year \n__Number:__ 1 \n__Position:__ Setter  \n\nThe setter and captain of the Aoba Josai High School volleyball club. Also, Oikawa was Kageyama\'s senpai when they were attending Kitagawa Daiichi. According to Kageyama, he is a very talented setter and volleyball player with a bad personality.','2020-10-19 11:26:29','2020-10-19 11:26:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n71611-pSEwFxLqJ0XG.jpg','MC'),(770,'Kenjirou Shirabu','__Date of Birth:__ May 4, 1995\n__Height:__ 174.8 cm (5\' 8.8\")\n__Weight:__64.4 kg (142 lbs)\n__Likes:__Shirasu (whitebait)\n__Hometown:__ Miyagi Prefecture\n\n__Introduction:__\nKenjirou Shirabu is a second year setter at Shiratorizawa Academy. He is the only player on Shiratorizawa\'s Boys\' Volleyball Team who didn\'t get into the school with a sports scholarship. He took the exam to get into Shiratorizawa in hopes of being able to play with tall and strong players after watching Ushijima play in junior high. \n\n__Personality:__\nHe is respectful towards his upperclassmen but tends to bicker with Goshiki, a first year. Though he appears serious and composed, Shirabu is extremely hot-headed and gets annoyed at nearly every move his opponents pull. However, he is capable of recomposing himself quickly. He is also very studious and hardworking, spending all of his free time studying in order to pass the difficult entrance exam for Shiratorizawa. During junior high, he had good grades.\n\n(Source: [Haikyuu!! Fandom Wikia](https://haikyuu.fandom.com/wiki/Kenjir%C5%8D_Shirabu))','2020-10-19 11:26:29','2020-10-19 11:26:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137537-lTq63OBoxrmF.jpg','MC'),(771,'Tsutomu Goshiki','__Date of Birth:__ August 22, 1996\n__Height:__ 181.5 cm (5\' 11.5\")\n__Weight:__ 69.5 kg (153.2lbs)\n__Likes:__ Boiled flounder\n__Hometown:__ Miyagi Prefecture\n\n__Introduction:__\nTsutomu Goshiki is a first year wing spiker in Shiratorizawa Academy. Goshiki appears to have been a capable volleyball player even before entering Shiratorizawa Academy. In one of his recollections, he is seen being praised by an elderly lady while showing off a volleyball related trophy. He is also frequently acknowledged for his height and reliability as an ace.\n\n__Personality:__\nHe is hardworking, ambitious, and enjoys showing off. Every time he pulls off a good move, he looks around in excitement, wondering if anyone saw him (and occasionally being told off by Shirabu). Goshiki responds to things his teammates say enthusiastically even if he doesn\'t understand what\'s being said to him (as seen with his coach, who speaks in the Miyagi dialect). He greatly admires Ushijima and dreams of becoming a better ace player than him, which is sometimes made the subject of jokes by his teammates (much to his chagrin).\n\n(Source: [Haikyuu!! Fandom Wikia](https://haikyuu.fandom.com/wiki/Tsutomu_Goshiki))','2020-10-19 11:26:30','2020-10-19 11:26:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137534-xgaYo1w8UrhZ.png','SC'),(772,'Hajime Iwaizumi','Team: Aobajousai High School \nAge: 17 \nHeight: 179.3 cm \nWeight: 70.2 kg \nBirthday: June 10 \nYear: 3rd Year, class 5 \nNumber: 4 \nPosition: Wing Spiker \nAbility Parameters (out of 5): Power = 5; jump = 4; stamina = 4; intellect = 3; technique = 3; speed = 4  \n\nIwaizumi often gets irritated by Oikawa\'s behavior and tells him that guys who have girls going kyaa kyaa over them irritates him the most.','2020-10-19 11:26:30','2020-10-19 11:26:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n75636-oQeROudFKrpg.png','SC'),(773,'Reon Ouhira','__Date of Birth:__ October 30, 1994\n__Height:__ 182.7 cm (5\' 11.9\") \n__Weight:__ 82.4 kg (181.7 lbs)\n__Likes:__ Mackerel cooked in miso\n__Hometown:__ Miyagi Prefecture\n\n__Introduction:__\nReon is a third year wing spiker at Shiratorizawa Academy. It\'s implied that he was accepted due to a sports scholarship for volleyball.\n\n__Personality:__\nOuhira has a soothing personality and tends to be responsible for calming his teammates down when they\'re hyped up. He doesn\'t get riled up easily and is similar to Ushijima when it comes to his temperament; along with Ushijima, he wasn\'t upset about the hundred serves they had to do upon losing. He is confident in his own abilities, going up against three blockers and performing well despite being aware of the audience\'s disappointment that it wasn\'t Ushijima attacking.\n\n(Source [Haikyuu!! Fandom Wikia](https://haikyuu.fandom.com/wiki/Reon_%C5%8Chira))','2020-10-19 11:26:30','2020-10-19 11:26:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137536-f2SehLCy8VdW.png','SC'),(774,'Tanji Washijou','Tanji is the head coach of Shiratorizawa Academy Boys\' Volleyball team.','2020-10-19 11:26:31','2020-10-19 11:26:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137539-UYztRwNfKB26.png','MC'),(775,'Daichi Sawamura','Team: Karasuno High \nAge: 17 \nHeight: 176.8 cm \nWeight: 70.1 kg \nBirthday: December 31 \nYear: 3rd year, class 4 \nNumber: 1 \nPosition: Wing Spiker \nFavorite Food: Shoyu ramen \nCurrent Concerns: The frequency of his dream about the vice-principal\'s wig flying around \nAbility Parameters (out of 5): Power = 4 ; Jump = 3 ; Stamina = 3 ; Intellect = 4 ; Technique = 4 ; Speed = 3  \n\nThe captain of the Karasuno High volleyball club.','2020-10-19 11:26:31','2020-10-19 11:26:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b67323-yFbLDAfJ5ysG.png','MC'),(776,'Akiteru Tsukishima','','2020-10-19 11:26:31','2020-10-19 11:26:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/121624-jCbW1ystnD1E.jpg','SC'),(777,'Tobio Kageyama','Team: Karasuno High, Kitagawa Daiichi Junior High (former) \nAge: 15 \nHeight: 180.6 cm \nWeight: 66.3 kg \nBirthday: December 22 \nYear: 1st Year, class 3 \nNumber: 9 \nPosition: Setter \nFavorite Food: Pork curry with a soft-boiled egg on top \nCurrent Concerns: He\'s worried that animals seem to dislike him \nAbility Parameters (out of 5): Power = 4; jump = 4; stamina = 5; intellect = 5; technique = 5; speed = 4  \n\nA famous setter in his middle school who joins the Karusuno High Volleyball team. He was known as the \"King of the Court\" in his middle school because of his arrogant demeanor and the way he would order around his teammates. Although he still carries an overbearing attitude, he begins to change when he starts to play with Hinata Shouyou who views him as a rival.','2020-10-19 11:26:32','2020-10-19 11:26:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b64771-cS4Bbbs8Yvpz.png','MC'),(778,'Kourai Hoshiumi','__Height:__ 169 cm\n\nA second year at Kamomedai High and a wing spiker. He wishes to be like the Small Giant.','2020-10-19 11:26:32','2020-10-19 11:26:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b139509-7uph3TF8AsXV.jpg','MC'),(779,'Tadashi Yamaguchi','Team: Karasuno High \nAge: 15 \nHeight: 179.5 cm \nWeight: 63 kg \nBirthday: November 10 \nYear: 1st year, class 4 \nNumber: 12 \nPosition: Middle Blocker  \n\nYamaguchi always hangs out with Tsukishima and is very protective of him. He has trained himself hard to use a jump float serve. He is also a substitute ace serv