r in NewWorld Online.','2020-10-19 11:27:16','2020-10-19 11:27:16','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158414-wxE8Akzz3bqM.png','SC'),(937,'Marx','Markus or Marx is a member of the guild Flame Emperors along side Mii, Misery, and Shin.\nMarx is a trap specialist and tends to uses different traps and spells to his advantage but tends to doubt himself.','2020-10-19 11:27:16','2020-10-19 11:27:16','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158416-zeNcJmCQ8leO.png','MC'),(938,'Christmas Rose','Christmas Rose is a side character usually seen getting defeated.','2020-10-19 11:27:16','2020-10-19 11:27:16','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158421-LzTjGgIRw1Ze.png','SC'),(939,'Misery','Misery is a member of the guild Flame Emperors along side Mii, Marx, and Shin. She is the guilds main healer.','2020-10-19 11:27:16','2020-10-19 11:27:16','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158418-z4HArKzpvD41.png','SC'),(940,'Shin','Shin is a member of the guild Flame Emperors along side Mii, Marx, and Misery. He earned the title of Destructor.','2020-10-19 11:27:16','2020-10-19 11:27:16','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158417-Fk9fFmabyp9M.png','SC'),(941,'Oboro','Sallys pet fox in the game.','2020-10-19 11:27:16','2020-10-19 11:27:16','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b162411-IdnSGn3f97bK.png','MC'),(942,'Payne','Payne or Pain, is the top player in NewWorld Online considered to be the strongest. He is the guild master of the Congregation of the Holy Swords along side Frederica,Dread,and Drag. \nAll though polite he sees Maple as a rival he aims to defeat in the future','2020-10-19 11:27:17','2020-10-19 11:27:17','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158419-OiDYa7reUOt5.png','SC'),(943,'Syrup','Maple\'s pet turtle in New World Order.','2020-10-19 11:27:17','2020-10-19 11:27:17','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b162410-ZfLsawPAIZFN.png','SC'),(944,'Dread','Dred or Dread, is a member of Payne\'s Guild, the Congregation of the Holy Swords along side Frederica and Drag.\n\nHe has a sharp intuition. His style puts focus on high speed and moderate attack power but his instincts tell him thats hes not an opponent for Payne or Maple.','2020-10-19 11:27:17','2020-10-19 11:27:17','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158411-k8Uw7GlwZhHP.jpg','MC'),(945,'Mii','Mii is a player in NewWorld Online. She is the guild master of the Flame Emperors guild along side Markus,Misery,and Shin.\n\nMii acquired a skill and unknowingly built up a character with her great charisma that others willingly follow. After realizing this, she became embarrassed to show her true self; a quiet girl who wants to enjoy cute things. She regrets her actions but decided to up appearances for those who chose to follow her.\n','2020-10-19 11:27:18','2020-10-19 11:27:18','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158420-Ob9jiuvO5Ui3.jpg','MC'),(946,'Midari Ikishima','A third-year student and head of the Student Council Beautification Committee. She gets pleasure from taking risks such as starting games of Russian roulette by herself.','2020-10-19 11:27:19','2020-10-19 11:27:19','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/122691-Z4TwnAbSTl3s.jpg','SC'),(947,'Mary Saotome','The central figure in Yumekos class. She tricks her classmates into becoming her slaves, and challenges Yumeko to a match. She is very prideful, and quick to snap.','2020-10-19 11:27:20','2020-10-19 11:27:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b122687-BDnMESgA4uae.jpg','MC'),(948,'Yumeko Jabami','A girl who transfers into Hyakkaou Private Academy. She might look like an attractive young lady, but she is actually a \"Kakegurui,\" someone who finds pleasure in taking risks.\n\nAttractive, smooth as silk, and silver-tongued, Yumeko is a natural-born gambler. Gathering the attention of her peers and the entire student council, there\'s no denying she enjoys the attention she receives. Despite all odds in a gambling match, she somehow manages to turn the tables in the most daring ways, often times using her perceptiveness to decipher her opponent\'s tricks.\n\n(Source: Honey\'s Anime)','2020-10-19 11:27:20','2020-10-19 11:27:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b121889-GOJZ1dzJhLhe.png','MC'),(949,'Kirari Momobami','__Birth Date:__ August 24\n__Zodiac:__ Virgo\n\nKirari Momobami is the 105th student council president at Hyakkaou Private Academy, and as well as the one responsible for the current hierarchy on the academy.','2020-10-19 11:27:20','2020-10-19 11:27:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b122693-qg2NIaq5h1VD.png','MC'),(950,'Ryouta Suzui','Yumekos classmate. Cowardly and poor, he quickly ends up being treated as Maeris livestock, and is called Pochi (a common name for a dog). However, he is saved from this predicament by Yumeko.','2020-10-19 11:27:20','2020-10-19 11:27:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b122688-DdMMQtWRdchY.png','SC'),(951,'Jun Kiwatari','Jun is portrayed as a typical bully. He is aggressive, arrogant and sadistic person, who loves dominating others. \n~!Rank: Housepet\nDebt: 310 Million Yen\n\nHe made use of Tsubomi Nanami\'s housepet status and cut her long hair, probably only because she really valued them and threatened Yumeko Jabami when she didn\'t strip in front of him and his friends. He battle\'s Nanami, Yumeko and Mary. In that battle, he was cheating with Nanami. That\'s the reason why Yumeko and Mary were allies. In the end, he lost and end up being a Housepet.!~','2020-10-19 11:27:20','2020-10-19 11:27:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/123179-7LhyoD26QS6M.jpg','MC'),(952,'Sayaka Igarashi','Secretary of the Student Council and the right hand of Student council president. She is determined to become Kirari\'s \'Number 1,\' and thinks of Yumeko as a plague. Sayaka is intelligent, serious and deeply cares about school and Student Council. She\'s endlessly loyal to the Student Council President, Kirari Momobami and will do anything for her. It seems that she has a crush on Kirari, as she expressed concern and sadness when she drove off without telling her where she went and what she was doing. While she seems to be reserved and calm, her subduing of a violent student, Jun Kiwatari and telling him what he now owes in the debt recollection game shows that she\'s every bit as terrifying as the rest of the Student Council. ','2020-10-19 11:27:20','2020-10-19 11:27:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b122690-BgoAty3EQ2GW.png','SC'),(953,'Itsuki Sumeragi','She\'s a first-year student belonging to the \"flower\" class at Hyakkaou Private Academy and a member of the Student Council. Her father is the president of a prominent toy company in Japan. Her hobby is collecting other peoples nails.\n~!Since Kaede betted his lifeplan Yumeko received it, but gave it to Itsuki. Its apparent, that she actually has feelings for him. She watches over him, as he lays in bed, still under shock. She goes on to collect quite a few votes during the election. And she is also present during Yumemis battle against Kawaru!~','2020-10-19 11:27:20','2020-10-19 11:27:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b122696-Ap3xm4l14BPQ.jpg','MC'),(954,'Yuriko Nishinotouin','A third-year student, member of the student council, and president of the Tradition Culture Research Society. She ends up challenging Yumeko to an original gambling match.','2020-10-19 11:27:20','2020-10-19 11:27:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/122694-3jxZQhslUVLK.jpg','SC'),(955,'Nanami Tsubomi',' She\'s a house pet, who gambled against Yumeko Jabami, Mary Saotome, and Jun Kiwatari in order to lower her debt.','2020-10-19 11:27:21','2020-10-19 11:27:21','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/123178-W