istcdn/character/large/b122693-qg2NIaq5h1VD.png','MC'),(973,'Sumika   Warakubami','Sumika is a member of The Hundred Devouring Families. She arrived to the Hyakkaou Private Academy to gamble against Kirari Momobami in order to dethrone her from student council president position and thus choosing a new leader of their clan. Secretly, she\'s also a famous Hollywood actress who goes by the name of Kawaru Natari, who Yumemi Yumemite looks up to.','2020-10-19 11:27:28','2020-10-19 11:27:28','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136599-CTYFtP8YLpEg.jpg','MC'),(974,'Runa Yomozuki',' She is a member of the Student Council and also a leader of the Election Committee, serving as a referee during election gambling matches.\n~!Runa is a sadistic and two-faced person, who seems to be very cute and nice at first but in reality she enjoys watching other people fail and loves to mock them.!~','2020-10-19 11:27:28','2020-10-19 11:27:28','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/122698-8UvXcLs1LGYY.jpg','MC'),(975,'Ririka Momobami','She is the vice president of the student council and is seen almost entirely throughout the whole time wearing a mask that covers her whole face. Ririka is a very quiet and stoic person. She often acts as an observer. \n','2020-10-19 11:27:29','2020-10-19 11:27:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b122777-pdh3z3WbnvlL.png','MC'),(976,'Rei Batsubami','A girl wearing the male students uniform, who was transferred to the school to take care of the Momobamis. She is part of the Momobami clan but not a representative.','2020-10-19 11:27:29','2020-10-19 11:27:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b134776-StIxRG7npCgu.jpg','SC'),(977,'Miri   Yobami','Miri is a member of The Hundred Devouring Families. She arrived to the Hyakkaou Private Academy to gamble against Kirari Momobami in order to dethrone her from student council president position and thus choosing a new leader of their clan. Miri\'s and Miyo Inbami\'s families are specialized in medicine business (including poisons), being responsible for a conflict between other branches.','2020-10-19 11:27:29','2020-10-19 11:27:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136608-YC0FWwZqgrTk.jpg','MC'),(978,'Miroslava Honebami','','2020-10-19 11:27:29','2020-10-19 11:27:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136598-IgLINsrYFJ4t.jpg','MC'),(979,'Horo  Jomaru','He gambled against Kirari Momobami and lose to her, causing him to lost all his votes.','2020-10-19 11:27:30','2020-10-19 11:27:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136602-HUDHSH3ckT96.jpg','MC'),(980,'Nozomi Komabami','','2020-10-19 11:27:30','2020-10-19 11:27:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136617-fW9OeoVXAnBa.jpg','MC'),(981,'Rin   Obami','Rin is a member of The Hundred Devouring Families. He arrived to the Hyakkaou Private Academy to gamble against Kirari Momobami in order to dethrone her from student council president position and thus choosing a new leader of their clan. His branch is widely known for being good swindlers.','2020-10-19 11:27:30','2020-10-19 11:27:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136597-n7Va2VSCJvee.jpg','SC'),(982,'Saori','She is the manager of the Student Council\'s Head of Public Relations, Yumemi Yumemite. She is the daughter of a big time producer','2020-10-19 11:27:30','2020-10-19 11:27:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136613-2Du0Maq9LEnI.jpg','MC'),(983,'Rumia Uru','Rumia is a part of the Election Committee, serving as a referee during election gambling matches.','2020-10-19 11:27:30','2020-10-19 11:27:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136605-OqxZv64Ez2P2.jpg','SC'),(984,'Erimi  Mushibami','A young girl who likes dressing in gothic lolita clothing and acting like a little girl to hide her twisted nature. Her family is known for being torturers, and she\'s