 before he died.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:20','2020-10-19 11:30:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89303-rkmnCfQ11QMS.jpg','SC'),(1539,'Ebisu','__Race:__ God\n__Gender:__ Male\n__Age:__ Ancient\n__Occupation:__ God of Fishing and Commerce\n\n__Ebisu__ is one of the Seven Gods of Fortune. He is the humorless God of Fishing and Commerce. He first appears in the manga trying to buy Yukine off Yato\'s hands for an incredible amount of money.\n\n~!Ebisu is later revealed to be attempting to gain control over phantoms - a severe taboo if not sin in the eyes of the heavens - going as far as descending to the underworld to achieve his goal. After Yato, under Father\'s command, reaches him and ensures his safe exit from Izanami\'s realm, Ebisu is eliminated by Pacification Ring, causing his reincarnation as a young boy with no memory of his past life.!~\n\nInitially, Ebisu appears very stoic, always bearing a near-emotionless facial expression and speaking in a reserved, polite, yet aloof tone. He is also highly pragmatic and resourceful, constantly progressing towards his goals and willing to go to great lengths to achieve what he is after. Despite his aloof appearance and personality, he can actually be a silly person, making him appear rather comically serious at times.\nHe is also a truly kind God ~!as his desire to control and name Ayakashi and go to the underworld to retrieve the location brush is because he believed if he did so he could relieve some of the strife and pain that Ayakashi cause and make the world a truly better place.!~\n\n~!After reincarnating Ebisu becomes very curious, and also jolly and friendly, yet is also well-mannered like his past adult form.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:20','2020-10-19 11:30:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89120-HVqIYwQAQ8Ih.png','MC'),(1540,'Tsuguha','Tsuguha is one of Bishamon\'s Ten Shinki. She transforms into Bishamon\'s bikini battle attire. Her vessel name is Shouki.\n~!She becomes an ayakashi and is killed by Kazuma after finding out her birth name.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:20','2020-10-19 11:30:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89304-Em5i0pTwlRCU.png','MC'),(1541,'Kuraha','Kuraha is a current Regalia to Bishamon. His regalia form is a male lion with a scar on his right eye.','2020-10-19 11:30:20','2020-10-19 11:30:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89301-1kEosHwb6M5T.png','MC'),(1542,'Yukine','__Age:__ 14\n__Race:__ Shinki\n__Height:__147.4cm (4\'10\")\n__Birthday:__ November 29\n\nWhile wandering about as a spirit, Yukine was picked up by Yato and made into a Shinki. When called \"Sekki\" he transforms into a katana.\n\n~!He died at a young age, making him miss his normal life as a middle schooler. He acts like his age, and was once stealing money from people with the excuse that it\'s okay since he\'s dead. After being \"saved\" by Hiyori, he becomes more obedient and respects Yato and Hiyori. When he was alive he had trouble with his father as seen by Yato when he first obtains Yukine.!~\n\nIn a katana form, he finds Yato\'s sweaty hands so disgusting that he calls him \"Drippy.\"\n\n~!In Noragami Aragoto, he evolves into a Hafuri while trying to save Yato from Bishamon\'s attack. Since then he turns into a dual wield katana when called.!~\n\n(Source: Fallen Syndicate)','2020-10-19 11:30:20','2020-10-19 11:30:20','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n84681-EdJOIvRlIhRW.png','MC'),(1543,'Genos','<b>Race:</b> Cyborg\n<b>Alias:</b> Demon Cyborg\n<b>Age:</b> 19\n<b>Height:</b> 178 cm (5\'10\")\n<b>Weight:</b> Undisclosed\n<b>Gender:</b> Male\n<b>Location:</b> Z-City\n<b>Abilities:</b> Enhancements Physical feats, Full Cyborg Weaponry, Highly Skilled and Strategist Combatant\n<b>Weapons:</b> Cyborg Body\n<b>Occupation:</b> Superhero\n<b>Level:</b> S-Class; Rank: 16\n<b>Affiliation:</b> The Heroes Association\n<b>Partner(s):</b> Saitama (Master)\n<b>Debut:</b> Chapter 6 / Episode 1\n\nGenos ( Jienosu) is a 19 years old cyborg and a self claimed disciple of Saitama. He is always aiming to become stronger and fights for justice. As a registered Superhero, he is in the S-Class ranking at 16.\n\nAppearance: Genos has a mechanical body of a teenage model, a pale looking face, yellow eyebrows, black sclera and yellow piercing eyes and has blond spiky hair. Over his mechanical limbs, he wears black pants and black shoes. Genos sometimes sports new black mechanical arms, during the time when he sparred with Saitama, and during the time on preparing to stop a giant meteor, he equipped more block-shaped, black mechanical arms along with a small headgear.\n\nPersonality: Genos is an extremelly serious character. He has a strong drive to get stronger than he is, and pesters Saitama to train him frequently.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:22','2020-10-19 11:30:22','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b73979-tVi9maPID881.jpg','MC'),(1544,'Mumen Rider','Race: Human<br>Age: Unknown<br>Gender: Male<br>Location: Z-City<br>Abilities: Weapons; Gauntlets<br>Occupation: Superhero<br>Level: C-Class; Rank: 1<br>Affiliation: Heroes Association<br>Debut: Chapter 12 <br><br>License-less Rider ( Mumen Raida) is a C-Class Hero from Z-City. He has the #1 rank of the C-Class.   __Appearance:__ The License-less Rider is a young man of average height and weight. He wears an armored suit, with light colored armor covering his torso and shoulders. He has a black leather suit under the armor and black gauntlets and kneepads. He also has a yellow bicycle helmet and dark shades.   __Abilities:__ Not much of License-less Rider\'s abilities have been seen, since he was defeated before showing any kind of action whatsoever. However, before being smashed to the ground and judging by his outfit, it seems that License-less Rider prefers hand-to-hand-combat and relies on his speed.  (Source: onepunchman.wikia.com)','2020-10-19 11:30:22','2020-10-19 11:30:22','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81935-NGDgB9J4MMlF.png','SC'),(1545,'King','__Race:__ Human  \n__Age:__ 29 \n__Gender: __Male\n__Occupation:__ Superhero \n__Level:__ S-Class; Rank 7\n__Affiliation:__ The Heroes Association\n\nDespite not being the highest ranked hero of the Heroes Association, he is considered to be the most powerful man on Earth, and it is due to this strength that he receives praise and respect from fellow heroes. His strength is so feared that criminals and mysterious beings will surrender before having to fight him. Appearance: King has slightly long, blonde, brushed back hair along with three long scars on the left side of his face. He wears a turtleneck sweater, has sunken cheeks, a defined jawline and a squarish chin. Notably, a loud drumming sound may be heard in his proximity. The King Engine is a rumbling sound that others claim occurs when King readies for battle or when he is generally serious having an intimidating effect on his opponents. ~! In actuality, it is simply the sound of King\'s heartbeat which, when he is frightened, is so loud that it can be heard outside his body, but because of King\'s intimidating reputation people mistake it for bloodlust. King is able to appear to remain calm in threatening situations as well as put out an extremely threatening aura. Despite the intimidating personality King projects, he is actually a coward and an otaku. He has been shown to get very excited about buying a dating game. Saitama saved his life many times, but always end up getting all the credits that was supposed to be for the latter. With this misunderstanding, he came to be known as \"the strongest man on earth\". He got his scars from the Octopus Claw man. !~','2020-10-19 11:30:23','2020-10-19 11:30:23','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n88907-M7QLjYvp2LEp.png','MC'),(1546,'Sonic','__Race:__ Human\n__Alias:__ Sonic\n__Age:__ 25\n__Gender:__ Male\n__Location:__ Z-City\n__Abilities:__ Superhuman Speed and Agility\n__Weapons:__ Ninja equipment\n__Occupation:__ Bodyguard (former, now a villain)\n__Affiliation:__ Mr. Monier (former)\n__Debut:__ Chapter 12 - Speed of Sound\n\nSonic ( Onkun no Soniku) is a villain in the series, first appearing as a bodyguard hired by Mr. Monier. He views Saitama as his eternal rival.\n\n__Appearance:__ Sonic is a thin, slightly effeminate man, who despite his slender build is extremely strong and fast. He has black medium length hair that is tied up in a topknot. One noticeable feature is that he has two black marks under his eyes, one under each. He first appears wearing a tight black outfit highlighted by metal plating on the shins, forearms, shoulders, and chest, as well as a long red scarf. He is shown later in black street clothes. He always carries a ninjato and other ninja equipment such as kunai and ninja stars.\n__Personality:__ Sonic is a villain who, despite his normally calm appearance, loves fighting strong opponents as shown by when he gets a \"child-like smile\" on his face when he first meets Saitama and has two of his attacks blocked, earlier calling this his \"bad habit.\" He seems to be very quick to act as he attacks Saitama on their first meeting without letting him explain the situation.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:23','2020-10-19 11:30:23','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n74167-mCuAQmAZK4xZ.png','SC'),(1547,'Tatsumaki','__Race:__ Human\n__Age:__ 28\n__Gender:__ Female\n__Abilities:__ Unknown\n__Occupation:__ Superhero\n__Level:__ S-Class; Rank: 2\n__Affiliation:__ Heroes Association\n__Family:__ Fubuki (sister)\n__Debut:__ OPM Special Chapter\n\n__Appearance:__ Tornado appears to be a rather small thin woman with short, curly, green hair. She wears a long dress that separates into 6 sections a little below the waist. She usually has an expressionless face, with partially closed eyes.\n\n__Abilities:__ Tornado has an unknown psychic ability, but she has shown to easily crush a wall, to protect herself from Demonic Fan\'s wind generations and to slice the Demon Fan in several pieces in an instant.\n\n(Source: One Punch Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:23','2020-10-19 11:30:23','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81929-odIgMdeRZDp2.jpg','SC'),(1548,'Bang ','__Race:__ Human \n__Gender:__ Male \n__Occupation:__ Superhero \n__Level:__ S-Class \n__Rank:__ 3 \n__Affiliation:__ Heroes Association\n__Appearance:__ Bang is an old man with white-spiky hair, thick eyebrows, and a thick mustache. He has distinct wrinkles on his face, a squarish chin and has slightly tan skin. He wears a dark shirt, light colored pants, and kung fu shoes.   \n__Personality:__ Bang has a serious personality, he acts calm and does not seem to be afraid at the prospect of stopping a Dragon-level disaster meteor. He also prefers to be called by his name.   \n__Abilities:__ Bang being in the top 3 of the S-Class ranking, he is acknowledged by the public and heroes to be a strong fighter. Not much is known about Bang\'s abilities other than that he uses a martial art called \"Rock-Smashing Water Stream Fist\".  \n\n Bang is an S-Class, rank 3, superhero for the Heroes Association, settled in Z-City. Bang owns a dojo passed down from generations, and uses the fighting style the Rock-Smashing Water Stream Fist.   \n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:23','2020-10-19 11:30:23','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n81141-1ml7Q6X2B508.png','SC'),(1549,'Handsome Kamen Amai Mask','_Race:_ Human~!?!~ _Age:_ 24 _Occupation:_ Superhero _Level:_ A-Class; Rank 1.  \n\n Sweet Mask is a tall and lean-built young man with messy, shoulder-length light blue hair and yellow eyes. He is considered to be very handsome by the public. Aside from being a hero he is also a famous model, actor and singer, being the most popular one in the world.Sweet Mask has stated that he believes that heroes are to protect the citizens, and if they can\'t do that, they must become strong enough to be able to do so. He also genuinely cares for the well-being of the citizens around him and actually wishes happiness upon every living thing in the universe. However, befitting the darker side of Sweet Mask\'s name is his hidden merciless nature. He is shown to have a burning hatred for anything that he sees as evil. Anything that he declares as evil must be swiftly and thoroughly exterminated. \n\nSweet Mask is shown to adhere to any method that makes heroes popular. He notes that only promotions to S-Class or A-Class are fit for his attention, as they are the heroes who draw the most attention from the public, and hence, any heroes in those ranks who earn themselves negative reputations would drag his reputation down as well. Because of this, Sweet Mask stays in the A-Class Rank 1 position to prevent unworthy heroes from promoting to S-Class. \n\nSweet Mask is very narcissistic about \"beauty overwhelming the power\", as he said about his philosophy that \"heroes have to be beautiful as well\". This became obvious when he showed interest in a worthy S-Class Hero like Genos, who has both a beautiful appeal and having done more heroic deeds as the main priority, fitting Sweet Mask\'s philosophy. ~! However, after witnessing the defeat of Garou by Saitama, his viewpoint changes and becomes more focused on the overwhelming power of the individual than beauty alone. !~','2020-10-19 11:30:23','2020-10-19 11:30:23','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b86031-vvn9Y5aoriox.jpg','MC'),(1550,'Saitama','<b>Race:</b> Human\n<b>Alias:</b> Bald Cape\n<b>Age:</b> 25\n<b>Height:</b> 175 cm (5\'9\")\n<b>Weight:</b> 70 kg (154 lbs.)\n<b>Gender:</b> Male\n<b>Location:</b> Z-City\n<b>Abilities:</b> Invaluable Physical Prowess, Supernatural Reflexes and Senses, Invulnerability, Indomitable Will\n<b>Occupation:</b> Superhero\n<b>Level:</b> A-Class; Rank 39\n<b>Affiliation:</b> The Heroes Association\n<b>Partner(s):</b> Genos (Disciple)\n<b>Debut:</b> Chapter 1\n\nSaitama is the main protagonist of One Punch Man, and the most powerful hero alive. Having apparently trained himself to superhuman condition, Saitama faces an existential crisis as he is now too powerful to gain any thrill from his heroic deeds.  He is registered with the Heroes Association as a C-Class Superhero and is tasked to defend Z-City against Mysterious Beings. \n\nAppearance: Saitama is a bald man of thin, but well-built physique and average height and weight. He claims to have lost all of his hair suddenly and prematurely as a result of the toll taken on his body by intense hero training. Three years before the story line, Saitama had spiky, black hair and brown eyes.  Saitama is usually deliberately drawn in a simpler style than other characters, with a very rounded head and only a simple mouth and eyes. When drawn in a more \'action-oriented\' style with more detail, Saitama is revealed to have sharp features, dangerous looking eyes, and chiseled musculature. His costume is a plain yellow jumpsuit with a short zipper at the collar and a belt. The costume is finished out by a red ensemble of boots, gloves and a cape.\n\nPersonality: For a superhero, Saitama is rather laid-back. Because even the mightiest foes pose no challenge to him, he doesn\'t take his hero work very seriously. In spite of this, he is constantly searching for an opponent that can challenge him, since his superhero work is beginning to bore him because it\'s too easy. The combination of his attitude, unstoppable strength, and distinctively simple and \'unimpressive\' appearance often cause his battles to become anticlimactic. Saitama will usually allow his opponents to rant about their motives and power up into their strongest forms before suddenly and nonchalantly obliterating them with one punch.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:23','2020-10-19 11:30:23','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/73935-WX4ViYPuZhs5.jpg','SC'),(1551,'Puri-Puri Prisoner','__Occupation:__ Superhero \n__Level:__ S-Class; Rank 17\n\nPuri-Puri Prisoner is a flamboyant, openly homosexual superhero. He takes an interest in other, up-and-coming heroes and criminals; an interest which led to his titular jail sentence, as he kept attacking them. Criminals that he apprehends are then added to his harem. ','2020-10-19 11:30:23','2020-10-19 11:30:23','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n86029-iomUtQtGfJOU.png','MC'),(1552,'Watchdog Man','Watchdog Man ( Banken-man) is a S-Class Rank 12 professional hero who is in charge of Q-City. Watchdog Man has been shown to be very blunt and nonchalant. He acts like a dog at all times, speaking sparingly, sitting on his haunches while alert or loitering, and curling up in a dog bed while asleep. He takes a stance on all fours while fighting, rather than standing upright to confront enemies.','2020-10-19 11:30:24','2020-10-19 11:30:24','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b86027-g3kRrv9jewmz.png','SC'),(1553,'Fubuki','Race: Human\nAge: 23\nGender: Female\nOccupation: Superhero\nLevel: B-Class\nRank: Unknown\nAffiliation: Heroes Association\nFamily: Tornado (sister)\nDebut: OPM Special Chapter\n\nMiss Blizzard is the leader of the B-Class superhero group \"The Blizzard Group\". Her rank is unknown.\n__Appearance:__ Miss Blizzard is a tall, pretty woman, with shoulder length black hair. She wears a long black dress, black boots and several necklaces all under a long fur coat. Her eyes are bright green.\n__Abilities:__ Miss Blizzard is shown to be able to levitate and launch items such as stones  Hell Storm: Miss Blizzard levitates the rocks in the surrounding area and then launches them at high speed towards an opponent.\n\n(Source: One Punch Man Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:24','2020-10-19 11:30:24','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81931-LndoxTgfpqx4.png','SC'),(1554,'Sneck','Race: Human Alias: Biting Snake Fist Age 	Unknown Gender: Male Occupation: Superhero Level: A-Class; Rank: 38 Affiliation: Heroes Association Debut: Chapter 16  Sneck is an A-Class Superhero, rank 38. He was tasked with welcoming the new heroes for the National Superhero Registry Test that Saitama and Genos were a part of.   __Appearance:__ Sneck is a tall and very serious looking man with a rather angular face and sharp eyes, and has spikey black hair. He wears a snakeskin suit with a black shirt and a white tie.  (Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:24','2020-10-19 11:30:24','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b75460-ytg6vTtJNGOw.png','SC'),(1555,'Metal Bat','Bad (, Baddo), also known by his hero alias Metal Bat (, Kinzoku Batto), is the S-Class Rank 15 professional hero for the Hero Association. Metal Bat is a young man with black hair styled in a pompadour, and dark eyes that emphasize his hot temper. Metal Bat has a great deal of confidence in himself, stating that he did not care whether a threat is a Demon or Dragon level. Like Saitama, he doesn\'t care about his rank, and accidentally kills his enemies faster than he intended.','2020-10-19 11:30:24','2020-10-19 11:30:24','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89156-s3wSDAyC6KTe.png','MC'),(1556,'Deep Sea King','The Deep Sea King (, Shinkai) ruled over the Seafolk as their king, and claimed the deep sea as his own. The Deep Sea King is a rather sadistic individual, who enjoys causing pain to others and starting fights. He is determined to take the surface world for himself to rule. He regards people as little more than food and has no qualms about treating them as such. He is also very arrogant and prideful, considering himself to be better than everyone and stating that he stands at the very top of the pyramid of all living organisms on the planet.','2020-10-19 11:30:24','2020-10-19 11:30:24','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n86057-gl3cN3YOJ60N.png','SC'),(1557,'Tanktop Tiger','Race: Human Gender: Male Occupation: Superhero Level: C-Class; Rank: 6 Affiliation: The Heroes Association Debut: Chapter 19  Tanktop Tiger ( Tankutopu Taiga) is a C-Class superhero, rank 6, and the younger brother of Tanktop Black Hole.   __Appearance:__ Tanktop Tiger is a large, muscular man who has tiger stripes running through his hair and eyebrows. He wears a tiger stripped tanktop.   __Personality:__ Tanktop Tiger is especially loud and obnoxious. He is confident in his own power and looks down upon superhero newbies, making him quite arrogant and hostile.  (Source: onepunchman.wikia.com)','2020-10-19 11:30:24','2020-10-19 11:30:24','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81939-O5EORVRLJKne.jpg','MC'),(1558,'Lord Boros','The leader of the Dark Matter Thieves who comes from outer space and wants to battle warriors.<br><br>\n\n(Source: ANN)','2020-10-19 11:30:24','2020-10-19 11:30:24','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n89263-GPItRQ64F27D.png','MC'),(1559,'Kombu Infinity','Mysterious Being that dwell in Z-City. It heard a rumor that a strong being was present in the outskirts of the town that drew strong Heroes opponents to it.','2020-10-19 11:30:24','2020-10-19 11:30:24','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b86055-8rbEBIa1nhwM.png','SC'),(1560,'Armored Gorilla','Race: cyborg Debut: chapter 7 Affiliation: House of Evolution Place in organization: Number 3 in terms of power Nickname: The Crystal of Wisdom (, Eichi no Kesshou)','2020-10-19 11:30:25','2020-10-19 11:30:25','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85983.jpg','MC'),(1561,'Flashy Flash ','\nHe is the S-class,rank 13 hero of one punch man.Shining Flash has feminine features, sharp looking eyes, shoulder-lengthed silver hair, and a white cape with a black pin that\'s the shape of the stars. He has two hairpins which are also the same shape.','2020-10-19 11:30:25','2020-10-19 11:30:25','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b138981-74nPW2rXVews.png','SC'),(1562,'All Back-Man','Class C superhero.','2020-10-19 11:30:26','2020-10-19 11:30:26','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/86049.jpg','SC'),(1563,'Golden Ball','Race: Human Gender: Male Abilities: Weapons; Slingshot, Shape Memory Gold Occupation: Superhero Level: A-Class; Rank: 29 Affiliation: Heroes Association Debut: Chapter 20  Golden Ball is an A-Class Superhero, rank 29. He was partnered with Spring Mustache to investigate the Kombu Infinity rumor in Z-City.   __Appearance:__ Golden Ball is a tall man who carries a lolipop in his mouth. Golden Ball wears baggy bants, a hoddie underneath a lettermans jacket and a hat. His jacket has \"Golden Ball\" written on his back and on the left breast, and \"It\'s not Kintama, it\'s Golden Ball,\" which is a joke about testicles.   __Personality:__ Golden Ball is a rather confident man, who believes he does not need to prepare for a fight.  (Source: One Punch-Man wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:26','2020-10-19 11:30:26','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81943-Zbjr1W8O0lkl.jpg','SC'),(1564,'Spring Mustachio','Class A Superhero. Rank 33.  First Appearance: Chapter 20.\n\nSpring Mustachio is an intelligent, serious man who doesn\'t back down, as shown by his persistence in fighting Kombu Infinity, even after being beaten up rather badly. He also shares a bond with fellow A-Class hero Golden Ball, as they regularly pair up to hunt monsters and share drinks in their spare time. ','2020-10-19 11:30:26','2020-10-19 11:30:26','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/86039.jpg','MC'),(1565,'Ground Dragon','Affiliation: House of Evolution Debut: Chapter 8','2020-10-19 11:30:26','2020-10-19 11:30:26','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85981.jpg','SC'),(1566,'Child Emperor','Race: Human\nGender: Male\nOccupation: Superhero\nLevel: S-Class; Rank: 5\nAffiliation: Heroes Association\nDebut: Chapter 29\n\nChild Emperor is a young boy with large eyes. He wears a plain T-shirt with two buttons both of which are buttoned, along with a black school bag on his back.\n\nAs a genius, the Child Emperor values education, which can be seen when he mentions about going to cram school even after hearing about the Earth being in danger. He easily becomes infuriated when being labeled as childish by others. He is very analytical, observing the situation and formulating plans in a calm and collected manner.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:26','2020-10-19 11:30:26','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137661-LkXiwarihX16.png','SC'),(1567,'Asura Kabuto','Carnage Kabuto (, Ashura Kabuto) was an artificial mutant created by Dr. Genus of the House of Evolution and is by far their strongest creation.','2020-10-19 11:30:27','2020-10-19 11:30:27','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85991.jpg','SC'),(1568,'Garou','Garou is a former disciple of Bang, but was kicked out from his dojo for going on a rampage. He\'s one of the strongest characters in the series and plays a major role as the main villain in the Hero Hunt arc.\n\nGarou is introduced as an evil character with a hatred for heroes and a confident, vindictive personality. He hates being insulted and will attack or kill any who offend him. He thinks highly of himself and uses that assertion to threaten high ranking personal such as heroes and Shicchi. He does not consider other human villains to be allies, wiping out a large group of them along with the heroes present. He will also attack low ranked hero and hero staff members if he encounters them. A large aspect of his personality seems to be some sort of disdain for his former master, Bang, enough to avoid using the Water Stream Rock Smashing Fist he was taught unless seriously cornered.\n\nHe has no remorse even for people who aid him, as he smashed Licenseless Rider\'s face soon after the latter defended him.\n\nAlthough Garou is an evil character, he possesses some kind of morality: he lets heroes live so that they can grow stronger and fight him again.\n\nIn some ways, Garou can be considered the opposite to Saitama. Where Saitama wanted to be a hero who fought villains from his childhood, Garou wanted to be a monster who defeated heroes. While Garou is a genius fighter, Saitama had to work extremely hard to get his strength. (Source: One Punch Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:29','2020-10-19 11:30:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89277-nVBmHdNGZTPE.png','SC'),(1569,'Metal Bat','Bad (, Baddo), also known by his hero alias Metal Bat (, Kinzoku Batto), is the S-Class Rank 15 professional hero for the Hero Association. Metal Bat is a young man with black hair styled in a pompadour, and dark eyes that emphasize his hot temper. Metal Bat has a great deal of confidence in himself, stating that he did not care whether a threat is a Demon or Dragon level. Like Saitama, he doesn\'t care about his rank, and accidentally kills his enemies faster than he intended.','2020-10-19 11:30:29','2020-10-19 11:30:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89156-s3wSDAyC6KTe.png','SC'),(1570,'Genos','<b>Race:</b> Cyborg\n<b>Alias:</b> Demon Cyborg\n<b>Age:</b> 19\n<b>Height:</b> 178 cm (5\'10\")\n<b>Weight:</b> Undisclosed\n<b>Gender:</b> Male\n<b>Location:</b> Z-City\n<b>Abilities:</b> Enhancements Physical feats, Full Cyborg Weaponry, Highly Skilled and Strategist Combatant\n<b>Weapons:</b> Cyborg Body\n<b>Occupation:</b> Superhero\n<b>Level:</b> S-Class; Rank: 16\n<b>Affiliation:</b> The Heroes Association\n<b>Partner(s):</b> Saitama (Master)\n<b>Debut:</b> Chapter 6 / Episode 1\n\nGenos ( Jienosu) is a 19 years old cyborg and a self claimed disciple of Saitama. He is always aiming to become stronger and fights for justice. As a registered Superhero, he is in the S-Class ranking at 16.\n\nAppearance: Genos has a mechanical body of a teenage model, a pale looking face, yellow eyebrows, black sclera and yellow piercing eyes and has blond spiky hair. Over his mechanical limbs, he wears black pants and black shoes. Genos sometimes sports new black mechanical arms, during the time when he sparred with Saitama, and during the time on preparing to stop a giant meteor, he equipped more block-shaped, black mechanical arms along with a small headgear.\n\nPersonality: Genos is an extremelly serious character. He has a strong drive to get stronger than he is, and pesters Saitama to train him frequently.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:29','2020-10-19 11:30:29','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b73979-tVi9maPID881.jpg','MC'),(1571,'Saitama','<b>Race:</b> Human\n<b>Alias:</b> Bald Cape\n<b>Age:</b> 25\n<b>Height:</b> 175 cm (5\'9\")\n<b>Weight:</b> 70 kg (154 lbs.)\n<b>Gender:</b> Male\n<b>Location:</b> Z-City\n<b>Abilities:</b> Invaluable Physical Prowess, Supernatural Reflexes and Senses, Invulnerability, Indomitable Will\n<b>Occupation:</b> Superhero\n<b>Level:</b> A-Class; Rank 39\n<b>Affiliation:</b> The Heroes Association\n<b>Partner(s):</b> Genos (Disciple)\n<b>Debut:</b> Chapter 1\n\nSaitama is the main protagonist of One Punch Man, and the most powerful hero alive. Having apparently trained himself to superhuman condition, Saitama faces an existential crisis as he is now too powerful to gain any thrill from his heroic deeds.  He is registered with the Heroes Association as a C-Class Superhero and is tasked to defend Z-City against Mysterious Beings. \n\nAppearance: Saitama is a bald man of thin, but well-built physique and average height and weight. He claims to have lost all of his hair suddenly and prematurely as a result of the toll taken on his body by intense hero training. Three years before the story line, Saitama had spiky, black hair and brown eyes.  Saitama is usually deliberately drawn in a simpler style than other characters, with a very rounded head and only a simple mouth and eyes. When drawn in a more \'action-oriented\' style with more detail, Saitama is revealed to have sharp features, dangerous looking eyes, and chiseled musculature. His costume is a plain yellow jumpsuit with a short zipper at the collar and a belt. The costume is finished out by a red ensemble of boots, gloves and a cape.\n\nPersonality: For a superhero, Saitama is rather laid-back. Because even the mightiest foes pose no challenge to him, he doesn\'t take his hero work very seriously. In spite of this, he is constantly searching for an opponent that can challenge him, since his superhero work is beginning to bore him because it\'s too easy. The combination of his attitude, unstoppable strength, and distinctively simple and \'unimpressive\' appearance often cause his battles to become anticlimactic. Saitama will usually allow his opponents to rant about their motives and power up into their strongest forms before suddenly and nonchalantly obliterating them with one punch.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:30','2020-10-19 11:30:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/73935-WX4ViYPuZhs5.jpg','MC'),(1572,'Handsome Kamen Amai Mask','_Race:_ Human~!?!~ _Age:_ 24 _Occupation:_ Superhero _Level:_ A-Class; Rank 1.  \n\n Sweet Mask is a tall and lean-built young man with messy, shoulder-length light blue hair and yellow eyes. He is considered to be very handsome by the public. Aside from being a hero he is also a famous model, actor and singer, being the most popular one in the world.Sweet Mask has stated that he believes that heroes are to protect the citizens, and if they can\'t do that, they must become strong enough to be able to do so. He also genuinely cares for the well-being of the citizens around him and actually wishes happiness upon every living thing in the universe. However, befitting the darker side of Sweet Mask\'s name is his hidden merciless nature. He is shown to have a burning hatred for anything that he sees as evil. Anything that he declares as evil must be swiftly and thoroughly exterminated. \n\nSweet Mask is shown to adhere to any method that makes heroes popular. He notes that only promotions to S-Class or A-Class are fit for his attention, as they are the heroes who draw the most attention from the public, and hence, any heroes in those ranks who earn themselves negative reputations would drag his reputation down as well. Because of this, Sweet Mask stays in the A-Class Rank 1 position to prevent unworthy heroes from promoting to S-Class. \n\nSweet Mask is very narcissistic about \"beauty overwhelming the power\", as he said about his philosophy that \"heroes have to be beautiful as well\". This became obvious when he showed interest in a worthy S-Class Hero like Genos, who has both a beautiful appeal and having done more heroic deeds as the main priority, fitting Sweet Mask\'s philosophy. ~! However, after witnessing the defeat of Garou by Saitama, his viewpoint changes and becomes more focused on the overwhelming power of the individual than beauty alone. !~','2020-10-19 11:30:30','2020-10-19 11:30:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b86031-vvn9Y5aoriox.jpg','SC'),(1573,'Puri-Puri Prisoner','__Occupation:__ Superhero \n__Level:__ S-Class; Rank 17\n\nPuri-Puri Prisoner is a flamboyant, openly homosexual superhero. He takes an interest in other, up-and-coming heroes and criminals; an interest which led to his titular jail sentence, as he kept attacking them. Criminals that he apprehends are then added to his harem. ','2020-10-19 11:30:30','2020-10-19 11:30:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n86029-iomUtQtGfJOU.png','MC'),(1574,'Tatsumaki','__Race:__ Human\n__Age:__ 28\n__Gender:__ Female\n__Abilities:__ Unknown\n__Occupation:__ Superhero\n__Level:__ S-Class; Rank: 2\n__Affiliation:__ Heroes Association\n__Family:__ Fubuki (sister)\n__Debut:__ OPM Special Chapter\n\n__Appearance:__ Tornado appears to be a rather small thin woman with short, curly, green hair. She wears a long dress that separates into 6 sections a little below the waist. She usually has an expressionless face, with partially closed eyes.\n\n__Abilities:__ Tornado has an unknown psychic ability, but she has shown to easily crush a wall, to protect herself from Demonic Fan\'s wind generations and to slice the Demon Fan in several pieces in an instant.\n\n(Source: One Punch Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:30','2020-10-19 11:30:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81929-odIgMdeRZDp2.jpg','SC'),(1575,'Eyelashes','','2020-10-19 11:30:30','2020-10-19 11:30:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137879-xev8ntBC4Jqm.jpg','MC'),(1576,'Sonic','__Race:__ Human\n__Alias:__ Sonic\n__Age:__ 25\n__Gender:__ Male\n__Location:__ Z-City\n__Abilities:__ Superhuman Speed and Agility\n__Weapons:__ Ninja equipment\n__Occupation:__ Bodyguard (former, now a villain)\n__Affiliation:__ Mr. Monier (former)\n__Debut:__ Chapter 12 - Speed of Sound\n\nSonic ( Onkun no Soniku) is a villain in the series, first appearing as a bodyguard hired by Mr. Monier. He views Saitama as his eternal rival.\n\n__Appearance:__ Sonic is a thin, slightly effeminate man, who despite his slender build is extremely strong and fast. He has black medium length hair that is tied up in a topknot. One noticeable feature is that he has two black marks under his eyes, one under each. He first appears wearing a tight black outfit highlighted by metal plating on the shins, forearms, shoulders, and chest, as well as a long red scarf. He is shown later in black street clothes. He always carries a ninjato and other ninja equipment such as kunai and ninja stars.\n__Personality:__ Sonic is a villain who, despite his normally calm appearance, loves fighting strong opponents as shown by when he gets a \"child-like smile\" on his face when he first meets Saitama and has two of his attacks blocked, earlier calling this his \"bad habit.\" He seems to be very quick to act as he attacks Saitama on their first meeting without letting him explain the situation.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:30','2020-10-19 11:30:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n74167-mCuAQmAZK4xZ.png','SC'),(1577,'Fubuki','Race: Human\nAge: 23\nGender: Female\nOccupation: Superhero\nLevel: B-Class\nRank: Unknown\nAffiliation: Heroes Association\nFamily: Tornado (sister)\nDebut: OPM Special Chapter\n\nMiss Blizzard is the leader of the B-Class superhero group \"The Blizzard Group\". Her rank is unknown.\n__Appearance:__ Miss Blizzard is a tall, pretty woman, with shoulder length black hair. She wears a long black dress, black boots and several necklaces all under a long fur coat. Her eyes are bright green.\n__Abilities:__ Miss Blizzard is shown to be able to levitate and launch items such as stones  Hell Storm: Miss Blizzard levitates the rocks in the surrounding area and then launches them at high speed towards an opponent.\n\n(Source: One Punch Man Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:30','2020-10-19 11:30:30','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81931-LndoxTgfpqx4.png','SC'),(1578,'King','__Race:__ Human  \n__Age:__ 29 \n__Gender: __Male\n__Occupation:__ Superhero \n__Level:__ S-Class; Rank 7\n__Affiliation:__ The Heroes Association\n\nDespite not being the highest ranked hero of the Heroes Association, he is considered to be the most powerful man on Earth, and it is due to this strength that he receives praise and respect from fellow heroes. His strength is so feared that criminals and mysterious beings will surrender before having to fight him. Appearance: King has slightly long, blonde, brushed back hair along with three long scars on the left side of his face. He wears a turtleneck sweater, has sunken cheeks, a defined jawline and a squarish chin. Notably, a loud drumming sound may be heard in his proximity. The King Engine is a rumbling sound that others claim occurs when King readies for battle or when he is generally serious having an intimidating effect on his opponents. ~! In actuality, it is simply the sound of King\'s heartbeat which, when he is frightened, is so loud that it can be heard outside his body, but because of King\'s intimidating reputation people mistake it for bloodlust. King is able to appear to remain calm in threatening situations as well as put out an extremely threatening aura. Despite the intimidating personality King projects, he is actually a coward and an otaku. He has been shown to get very excited about buying a dating game. Saitama saved his life many times, but always end up getting all the credits that was supposed to be for the latter. With this misunderstanding, he came to be known as \"the strongest man on earth\". He got his scars from the Octopus Claw man. !~','2020-10-19 11:30:31','2020-10-19 11:30:31','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n88907-M7QLjYvp2LEp.png','SC'),(1579,'Sitch','Sitch (, Shicchi) is the Minister Officer of Justice for the Hero Association. ','2020-10-19 11:30:32','2020-10-19 11:30:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137876-e7AuIB3Ny5Bs.png','SC'),(1580,'Bang ','__Race:__ Human \n__Gender:__ Male \n__Occupation:__ Superhero \n__Level:__ S-Class \n__Rank:__ 3 \n__Affiliation:__ Heroes Association\n__Appearance:__ Bang is an old man with white-spiky hair, thick eyebrows, and a thick mustache. He has distinct wrinkles on his face, a squarish chin and has slightly tan skin. He wears a dark shirt, light colored pants, and kung fu shoes.   \n__Personality:__ Bang has a serious personality, he acts calm and does not seem to be afraid at the prospect of stopping a Dragon-level disaster meteor. He also prefers to be called by his name.   \n__Abilities:__ Bang being in the top 3 of the S-Class ranking, he is acknowledged by the public and heroes to be a strong fighter. Not much is known about Bang\'s abilities other than that he uses a martial art called \"Rock-Smashing Water Stream Fist\".  \n\n Bang is an S-Class, rank 3, superhero for the Heroes Association, settled in Z-City. Bang owns a dojo passed down from generations, and uses the fighting style the Rock-Smashing Water Stream Fist.   \n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:32','2020-10-19 11:30:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n81141-1ml7Q6X2B508.png','MC'),(1581,'Mumen Rider','Race: Human<br>Age: Unknown<br>Gender: Male<br>Location: Z-City<br>Abilities: Weapons; Gauntlets<br>Occupation: Superhero<br>Level: C-Class; Rank: 1<br>Affiliation: Heroes Association<br>Debut: Chapter 12 <br><br>License-less Rider ( Mumen Raida) is a C-Class Hero from Z-City. He has the #1 rank of the C-Class.   __Appearance:__ The License-less Rider is a young man of average height and weight. He wears an armored suit, with light colored armor covering his torso and shoulders. He has a black leather suit under the armor and black gauntlets and kneepads. He also has a yellow bicycle helmet and dark shades.   __Abilities:__ Not much of License-less Rider\'s abilities have been seen, since he was defeated before showing any kind of action whatsoever. However, before being smashed to the ground and judging by his outfit, it seems that License-less Rider prefers hand-to-hand-combat and relies on his speed.  (Source: onepunchman.wikia.com)','2020-10-19 11:30:32','2020-10-19 11:30:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81935-NGDgB9J4MMlF.png','MC'),(1582,'Suiryu','Suiryu is a Martial Artist and user of the Void Fist. He is said to be a top contender in the Super Fight tournament. Suiryu is an easygoing and carefree man usually seen smiling and is a notorious playboy, who would rather spend time with women than training. He is also very eager to fight strong opponents and believes the reason for fighting is to live an easy life without worry. During fights, Suiryu holds back in an effort to make any fight more interesting, only using his legs during his fights and later defeating his opponents with one kick. While fighting he tries to make small talk and after he defeats his opponents, he sarcastically apologizes to them for being too strong. Suiryu is a martial arts prodigy. Despite having spent most of his time goofing off or not taking his lessons seriously, he still ultimately became one of the most revered martial artists in the world, considered a legend for winning four Super Fight tournaments in a row.\n\n(Source: One-Punch Man Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:32','2020-10-19 11:30:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b132939-DLMpET3S5YG6.png','MC'),(1583,'Charanko','Charanko (, Charanko) is a Martial Artist and Bang\'s last and only disciple before he was expelled during Garou\'s hero hunt.','2020-10-19 11:30:32','2020-10-19 11:30:32','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b138979-0DWXgUOmruFL.jpg','MC'),(1584,'Watchdog Man','Watchdog Man ( Banken-man) is a S-Class Rank 12 professional hero who is in charge of Q-City. Watchdog Man has been shown to be very blunt and nonchalant. He acts like a dog at all times, speaking sparingly, sitting on his haunches while alert or loitering, and curling up in a dog bed while asleep. He takes a stance on all fours while fighting, rather than standing upright to confront enemies.','2020-10-19 11:30:33','2020-10-19 11:30:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b86027-g3kRrv9jewmz.png','SC'),(1585,'Tanktop Tiger','Race: Human Gender: Male Occupation: Superhero Level: C-Class; Rank: 6 Affiliation: The Heroes Association Debut: Chapter 19  Tanktop Tiger ( Tankutopu Taiga) is a C-Class superhero, rank 6, and the younger brother of Tanktop Black Hole.   __Appearance:__ Tanktop Tiger is a large, muscular man who has tiger stripes running through his hair and eyebrows. He wears a tiger stripped tanktop.   __Personality:__ Tanktop Tiger is especially loud and obnoxious. He is confident in his own power and looks down upon superhero newbies, making him quite arrogant and hostile.  (Source: onepunchman.wikia.com)','2020-10-19 11:30:33','2020-10-19 11:30:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b81939-O5EORVRLJKne.jpg','SC'),(1586,'Bomb','Bomb  is Bang\'s older brother as well as a dojo master. He and Bang are the two greatest masters of the Martial Arts world.[2] He\'s one of the few people who are aware of Saitama\'s true strength and is part of the Saitama Group.','2020-10-19 11:30:33','2020-10-19 11:30:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b138982-5QRetWxLmQYo.png','MC'),(1587,'Bofoy','Race: Human Alias: Metal Knight Gender: Male Location: Z-City Abilities: Weapons; Large remotely controlled robot, with lots of firepower Occupation: Superhero Level: S-Class; Rank: 6 Affiliation: The Heroes Association  Bofoy is an S-Class, rank 6, superhero for the Heroes Association and is settled in Z-City.   __Appearance:__ Not much is known about Bofoy\'s real appearance as his full face has never been fully shown. From what has been seen has white hair.   __Personality:__ Bofoy seems to be a rather confident person, believing himself to be capable of taking care of a meteor with ease. Bofoy shows little to no compassion for anyone in the city during the meteor attack.  (Source: One Punch Man Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:33','2020-10-19 11:30:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/81933.jpg','SC'),(1588,'Zombieman','Zombieman (, Zonbiman) is the S-Class Rank 8 professional hero for the Hero Association. Zombieman is stated to be nihilistic, possibly due to the fact that he has \"died\" several times, therefore he is always calm. In addition, he prefers to work as a lone wolf and dislikes gathering, although he still respects common courtesy. Despite his bleak view of the world, he is a fairly forgiving individual who does not hold onto a grudge when there isn\'t a point in pursuing it. Described as \"a man that even in death cannot die\", Zombieman possesses one of the best regeneration capabilities in the series. He is able to regenerate any part of his body no matter how severe the injury is, and he was able to heal his broken arms in an instant.','2020-10-19 11:30:33','2020-10-19 11:30:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n133835-7dbqvi4YzpRC.png','SC'),(1589,'Tank-top  Master','Race: Human\nOccupation: Superhero\nLevel: S-Class; Rank: 14\nAffiliation: The Heroes Association\nDebut: Chapter 29\n\nMuch like the other heroes with the Tanktop motif, Tanktop Tiger and Tanktop Black Hole, Tanktop Master is a muscular man with a tanktop and short hair. However, unlike the other Tanktop heroes, no known color is associated with Tanktop Master\'s name. In the first anniversary color spread of the manga, he is shown with blonde hair and a blue tank top.\n\nTanktop Master has a chivalrous nature, which can be seen when he noted that even if Tornado is ranked 2nd, he should not let a \"little girl\" handle dangerous enemies on her own, despite the fact that Tornado is actually an adult. He is also unafraid to admit defeat, for example, when he was outclassed by Tornado during the encounter of Dark Matter Thieves\' aircraft.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:33','2020-10-19 11:30:33','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b156125-y0ww6bnKD357.jpg','MC'),(1590,'Drive Knight ','Drive Knight (, Kud Kishi) is the S-Class Rank 9 professional hero for the Hero Association.Drive Knight has long black hair and wears a white mask. His mask has a single horizontal slit for the eyes, and a single red shining eye in the center of the slit. The mask has three small vertical slits where his mouth should be. His armor is rather simplistic, being similar to a medieval black knights\' armor.','2020-10-19 11:30:34','2020-10-19 11:30:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b138980-hp9fsJnwCF1M.png','MC'),(1591,'Child Emperor','Race: Human\nGender: Male\nOccupation: Superhero\nLevel: S-Class; Rank: 5\nAffiliation: Heroes Association\nDebut: Chapter 29\n\nChild Emperor is a young boy with large eyes. He wears a plain T-shirt with two buttons both of which are buttoned, along with a black school bag on his back.\n\nAs a genius, the Child Emperor values education, which can be seen when he mentions about going to cram school even after hearing about the Earth being in danger. He easily becomes infuriated when being labeled as childish by others. He is very analytical, observing the situation and formulating plans in a calm and collected manner.\n\n(Source: One Punch-Man Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:34','2020-10-19 11:30:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137661-LkXiwarihX16.png','MC'),(1592,'Flashy Flash ','\nHe is the S-class,rank 13 hero of one punch man.Shining Flash has feminine features, sharp looking eyes, shoulder-lengthed silver hair, and a white cape with a black pin that\'s the shape of the stars. He has two hairpins which are also the same shape.','2020-10-19 11:30:34','2020-10-19 11:30:34','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b138981-74nPW2rXVews.png','MC'),(1593,'Shalltear Bloodfallen','The Guardian of the First, Second, and Third floors of Nazarick, she has the form of a beautiful vampire girl. She\'s also in love with Momonga. She and Albedo constantly clash for his attention. While the two don\'t mind sharing Momonga, they still fight for superiority and who would ultimately appeal to Momonga. Shalltear is one of the most powerful guardians, allegedly capable of going toe-to-toe with Albedo. ~!Due to an incident where she is subjected to mind control by a member of the Black Scripture, she ends up unintentionally rebelling against Nazarick.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:36','2020-10-19 11:30:36','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89121-zE0gzCp5sj0A.jpg','SC'),(1594,'Momonga','He is the guild master of Ainz Ooal Gown and regarded as the highest of the Almighty 41 Supreme Beings by the NPCs of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. He is also the creator of Pandora\'s Actor.\n\nA cautious and stingy person, Momonga always tries to plan and control details, avoiding any haphazard actions. Because he doesn\'t underestimate his opponents, he will usually overkill them. Since being transferred to a new world and becoming an actual Undead being, Momonga could feel himself becoming very cold and calculating, his emotions repressed.\n\nLoyal to his friends and creations, since becoming Lord ruler of Nazarick in the new world he acts with a certain degree of nobility for his devoted followers. Momonga only does things that will benefit Nazarick or himself, whether its information or prestige. Although he does have a sense of justice and doesn\'t hate humans as much as his followers, he holds no attachment to them, and he feels nothing toward their deaths.\n\n~!His real name is Satoru Suzuki.!~\n\n(Source: Overlord Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:37','2020-10-19 11:30:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89103-jNcqIFsGWfNp.jpg','MC'),(1595,'Albedo','The overseer of the Floor Guardians and one of the most powerful NPC in Nazarick. She takes the form of a beautiful woman with fallen angel wings and horns. Because Ainz modified her settings on a whim, she ends up madly in love with him. Albedo\'s romantic obsessions are so strong that if Ainz were to even glance at her body, she would immediately become excited. Albedo\'s obsession with Ainz has led him to greatly regret his actions. While she tries to act calm, as befitting of her role, any perceived insult against Ainz or Nazarick, real or imagined, sends her into a rage. Like most inhabitants of Nazarick, she despises humans which she refers to as \"lower life-forms.\" ~!Though the reason is not yet known, Albedo holds a strong hatred towards all of the 41 Supreme Beings except for Ainz. It is hinted that she is scheming to annihilate all the other guild members if they are found.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:37','2020-10-19 11:30:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89122-AX3GMHvqa0Ye.png','SC'),(1596,'Cocytus','The Guardian of the Fifth floor of Nazarick, he has the form of a huge, four-armed, insect-like humanoid with the power to control ice. He has a warrior personality and respects anyone with a fighting spirit. He\'s in charge of the security of Nazarick, and later becomes responsible for a tribe of lizardmen that Ainz has him conquer.','2020-10-19 11:30:37','2020-10-19 11:30:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89138-tVwPzfMsh3qg.jpg','MC'),(1597,'Solution Epsilon','One of the Pleiades. She\'s a slime and one of the most dangerous Pleiades to humans, since she enjoys devouring humans alive. An assassin and poisoner who can decide to protect or dissolve things she absorbs, she can also control the speed of her digestion. She gets along with Shalltear because of their similar tastes','2020-10-19 11:30:37','2020-10-19 11:30:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89123-LgUt6CMg22eB.jpg','SC'),(1598,'Mare Bello Fiore','One of the Guardians of the Sixth floor of Nazarick alongside his twin sister Aura. He\'s rather shy and calm in comparison to his sister, although he can fight and be ruthless when necessary. Like his sister, Mare is a Dark Elf. Mare specializes in Druid magic, capable of twisting the earth to his whims.','2020-10-19 11:30:37','2020-10-19 11:30:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89126-0L0VoRL1LVgc.jpg','MC'),(1599,'Demiurge','The Guardian of the Seventh floor of Nazarick, with the form of a demon wearing glasses. Demiurge is very intelligent, but is also considered the most evil NPC on Nazarick. He greatly enjoys the suffering of others, made clear by his vicious experiments on prisoners. He\'s in charge of tactics and defenses of Nazarick. Among the Guardians, he gets along the best with Mare, since he understands the more cunning side of the Dark Elf.','2020-10-19 11:30:37','2020-10-19 11:30:37','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89125-7bQqj1LgvGgS.jpg','MC'),(1600,'Pandora\'s Actor','The Area Guardian in charge of the Treasury and finances of Nazarick, who was created by Ains himself. He\'s a Doppelgnger whose face is a simple egghead with three holes dressed in a Neo-Nazi-esque uniform. In Momonga\'s original design, he\'s the combination of everything that he though was cool, with exaggerated gestures and body language. His existence embarrasses Ains, but at the same time knows he\'s the NPC he can trust the most and the only one who can perform all his master\'s tasks without misunderstanding his intentions. He\'s on the same level as the Floor Guardians, and can copy the appearance and skills of anyone he has seen.','2020-10-19 11:30:38','2020-10-19 11:30:38','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89154-jbsFsEsjL3aS.jpg','SC'),(1601,'Touch Me','Touch Me is one of the original founding members of the Ainz Ooal Gown guild and one of the strongest warriors in YGGDRASIL. He is regarded as one of the Forty-One Supreme Beings by the NPCs of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. He is the creator of Sebas Tian. At some point in YGGDRASIL, Touch Me participated in an official martial tournament and defeated all of his adversaries. By winning the tournament, he was awarded a special prize that comes in two. Firstly, he was given a special job class known as the \"World Champion\" of lfheimr, and in addition he was awarded with the pure white armor set called \"Compliance with Law.\"\n\nTouch Me\'s outfit consists of shining white armor and a helm. His chest piece contains a huge sapphire embedded in the middle, which radiates with pure and divine light.\nHe is also adorned with a reddish cape attached around his right shoulder. Additionally, he is armed with both sword and shield. Touch Me\'s actual facial appearance in real life is said to look exactly like Sebas Tian. \n\nAs Touch Me played YGGDRASIL, he decided to assist the heteromorphic players during a time when they were being hunted down for fun through PKing. Thus, that was how he met Momonga, by saving him from a PK party; the two started becoming friends since then. There was also a time when Bukubukuchagama could not find a party to adventure with due to her appearance, so he was the one who approached her before anyone else. Afterwards, they formed a party together with other non-human characters and organized the First Nine, also known as Nine\'s Own Goal.\n\nAfter that, the clan grew with members chosen and invited personally by Touch Me, becoming a stable and friendly group. However, he felt that the clan was beginning to slowly fall apart. During one of its meetings, Touch Me was seen looking troubled by Momonga and Peroroncino, but their concerns were brushed aside. Once all the clan members had arrived, Touch Me started the meeting by having Nishikienrai report his latest discovery of a new unexplored dungeon. After the various clan members discussed the pros and cons of the dungeon, it was agreed that the clan would launch a raid.  Touch Me then moved unto the next point in the agenda of the meeting, in which he formally announced his intention to dissolve the Clan. His declaration elicited many protests, however he informed them that he wished to form Nine\'s Own Goal as an official Guild. Hearing the majority of the Clan concur to the idea, Touch Me decided to turn down the suggestion to become the Guildmaster. Just as several members of the groups argued about who should become Guildmaster, Touch Me restored order and nominated Momonga as their new guild leader, a proposal which many accepted. \n\nTouch Me is looked upon as very righteous and fair. He would help people in times of trouble without hesitation, and scolds his friends if one of them did something wrong. Momonga describes Touch Me as someone who is a straightforward person, the kind who was very direct in his words and deeds. However, Touch Me can be self-reflective at times, as evidenced when he was willing to step down as clan leader and proposed for someone else to be the guild master rather than him. If what Ulbert said is true; about him chasing away one of their former clansman leaving the game, then this might be part of the reason why Touch Me decided to step down voluntarily as a candidate for Guildmaster. \n\n(Source: Overlord Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:38','2020-10-19 11:30:38','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127437-HHvKoQEugGhN.jpg','SC'),(1602,'Narberal Gamma','One of the Pleiades, combat maids of the Tenth floor under Sebas Tian. She\'s a Doppelgnger and, because she\'s one of the most human-looking of the maids, she is Momonga\'s companion in his exploration of the new world disguised as adventurers. Narberal takes great pride in this duty, often \"wearing\" it like a badge of honor. However, like most in Nazarick, she holds great disdain towards humans. This proves troublesome, as she becomes incredibly violent when human males make advances on her. \nWhile operating as a member of the adventuring guild, \"Darkness\", Narberal operates under the alias of \"Nabe\", which becomes \"Nabe, the Beautiful Lady\" when Darkness becomes famous. Narberal\'s beauty has been compared to that of the \"Golden Princess of Re-Estize\" by many of the country\'s inhabitants.','2020-10-19 11:30:39','2020-10-19 11:30:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89152-C8VHEJUgMcDK.jpg','SC'),(1603,'Aura Bella Fiora','One of the Guardians of the Sixth floor of Nazarick, alongside her twin brother Mare. She\'s very energetic and extroverted, in contrast with her brother. Aura is a 70-year-old Dark Elf. Despite constantly fighting, she and Shalltear are quite close. Aura specializes in beast-taming and fights with a long, bladed whip.','2020-10-19 11:30:39','2020-10-19 11:30:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n89129-5DrpwF5YEQxB.jpg','SC'),(1604,'Sebas Tian','The butler of the Tenth floor of Nazarick, who specializes in unarmed combat, with power comparable with the other floor Guardians. He has the appearance of an elderly gentleman with a neat beard, but is actually of a species known as Dragonoids. He has a strong sense of justice, like his creator. Thus, he dislikes when the other Guardians kill humans needlessly. Because of their opposite personalities, he and Demiurge don\'t get along.','2020-10-19 11:30:39','2020-10-19 11:30:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89155-Rl0sWa0fAABk.jpg','SC'),(1605,'Entoma Vasilissa Zeta','One of the members of the battle maids () originally created by Genjiro. \n\n~!She has the appearance of a normal girl but her true form is that of an arachanid hybrid. She has bug mask to cover her real face. She uses a leech that recreates human voices after it kills them to disguise her original voice. She has insect focused abilities and uses talismans.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:39','2020-10-19 11:30:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n126281-DqoIZzZrIeBI.jpg','MC'),(1606,'Nemu Emmot','Age: 10\n Gender: Female\n Race: Human \nAffiliation:\n Sorcerer Kingdom \nRe-Estize Kingdom (Formerly)\n Family: \nEnri Emmot (Older Sister) \nNfirea Bareare (Brother-In-Law)\n Occupation: Villager \nResidence: Carne Village\n\n Nemu has a childish and naive personality, but it seems that she may actually know more than her older sister. She used to be more bold and rebel, but after the attack to her village and the death of her parents she try to be more useful and obedient to help Enri. However, it seems that her boldness comes back when she gets emotional, like the time that she visited Nazarick','2020-10-19 11:30:39','2020-10-19 11:30:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128402-6d5Ab9O2ThK8.jpg','SC'),(1607,'Brain Unglaus','Brain is a warrior turned mercenary after he lost to Gazef Stronoff in a grand tournament to determine the strongest fighter in Re-Estize Kingdom. He has brown eyes with blue hair and the appearance of a wild beast. He is equipped with a chainmail and wears a necklace and ring which are infused with protection magic. His whole body is lean and his muscles are tough as steel and tempered through experience.\n\nOriginally a farmer, he was gifted with what could only be described as a God-given talent in the mastery of the sword. He has always believed himself to be the strongest fighter inside the Kingdom, having never lost a fight before he entered the grand tournament to decide the King\'s guard captain. He easily fought his way to the final where he faced off against Gazef Stronoff. A grand and close battle ensued between the two, but eventually, he would taste his first defeat at the hand of Gazef.\n\nHis fame was shattered and his confidence as an unbeatable warrior took a hit. He then decided to do everything he could to become stronger, so he would truly become unbeatable. At the same time, in order to make a living he started working as a mercenary for the Death Spreading Brigade. \n\n\n~!When first introduced he is very arrogant, thinking that he is the most powerful, even though he earlier lost to Gazef. While a mercenary, he suffered a devastating defeat at the hand of Shalltear Bloodfallen when she attacked the hideout of the Death Spreading Brigade. After that, his personality changes drastically. Having his confidence completely crushed and getting a feel of what true terror is like, his attitude changes to one where he is completely depressed, hinting at a suicidal tendency.\n\nHe eventually does a complete overhaul after meeting Climb and Sebas Tian. He changes to a much friendlier person that starts to think that strength is more than simply being skilled with a sword.\n\nIn his second encounter with Shalltear, he managed to chip off Shalltear\'s pinky fingernail using Fourfold Slash of Light.\n\nIn the web novel version, he becomes a vampire under Shalltear.!~\n\n(Source: Overlord Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:39','2020-10-19 11:30:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128263-KwhoIxlYfLET.jpg','MC'),(1608,'Gazef Stronoff','Gazeff Stronoff is the Warrior Captain of the Re-Estize Kingdom and King Ramposa III\'s personal bodyguard, and professes his utmost loyalty to him. Incredibly talented with the sword and well-versed in martial arts, he is famously considered the strongest warrior in the entire kingdom, and commands the respect and admiration of everyone who knows his name. Due to internal power struggles among the nobles in the kingdom, Gazeff is not knighted, so the King granted him the title of \"Warrior Captain\", which allows him to command his own unit comprised of \"Warrior Troops\".\n\nBorn a commoner in a frontier village, he later became a mercenary. During his travels, he encountered a former adamantite-ranked adventurer who taught him his extraordinary swordsmanship. He participated in the grand tournament and defeated Brain Unglaus, becoming the champion and earning the King\'s trust.\n\nA muscular man in his thirties, he has a sunbathed face with noticeable wrinkles and dark-colored eyes. His short-trimmed hair is dark brown in color. He is a strong-willed individual who is willing to sacrifice his life in order to protect the citizens of the kingdom. Usually he is clad in a breastplate ornamented with red bands across his chest and shoulder pads, and considerably less protection on the lower half of his body. As Warrior Captain, he has the right to wield the five treasures of the Kingdom, of which merely four are publicly known. These are the Guardian Armor, made of extremely hard steel, the Amulet of Immortality, which grants regeneration, the Gauntlets of Endurance, said to grant endless stamina, and Razor Edge, a magically enchanted sword which is believed to be capable of cutting through armor like paper.','2020-10-19 11:30:40','2020-10-19 11:30:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126869-HZeyTV5SR1QU.jpg','SC'),(1609,'Lizzie Bareare','Gender: Female\nRace: Human\nAffiliation:\nSorcerer Kingdom\nRe-Estize Kingdom (Formerly)\nFamily:\nNfirea Bareare (Grandson)\nOccupation:\nHerbalist\nPotion Maker\nResidence\nE-Rantel (Formerly)\nCarne Village (Currently)\nis a pharmacist who used to operate in E-Rantel and the grandmother of Nfirea Bareare. When Nfirea was kidnapped by Zurrernorn, she made a deal with Ainz to rescue him in return for her services. Afterwards, she moved to Carne Village.\nThough a seemingly old woman, Lizzie Bareare is still quite sharp for her age. Highly knowledgeable about the make-up, properties and lore of potions. She also has a demanding and fastidious personality. Her intense gaze gives other people the shivers.\nRenown throughout the city of E-Rantel, Lizzie Bareare holds the title as the city\'s best pharmacist.','2020-10-19 11:30:40','2020-10-19 11:30:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128403-gJFHR2J3qMHh.jpg','SC'),(1610,'Lupusregina Beta','A member of the \"Pleiades Six Stars\", the battle maid squad of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. She serves as the role of battle cleric and focuses on healing magic. In terms of combat ability, she possesses the highest physical defense and resistances among the Pleiades, and has balanced stats overall. Being a werewolf, she is weak to silver weapons, but is blessed with resistance against other metals.\n\nHer appearance is that of a brown-skinned beauty with amber-colored eyes, and red hair which she ties in two long braids. She wears a maid uniform with short sleeves and long black gloves, white stockings, and a skirt that has a long slit on its left side. She is usually seen carrying her signature weapon slung across her back, a menacing black and silver scepter which looks like and oversized religious symbol, the Crosier.\n\nLupusregina boasts a very sociable and outgoing personality, and seems very friendly, even towards humans, a race considered unworthy of respect by other beings of Nazarick. For example, she adds \"-chan\" to the other maid\'s names, and often likes teasing Enri with lewd jokes. The Homunculus Maids (the ordinary maids of Nazarick) are convinced she\'s the friendliest of the Pleiades and even believe that being approached by her can be a sign of good fortune. However, her fellow battle-maid Yuri Alpha has commented that Lupusregina\'s friendliness is merely a facade, and that in reality she can be as brutal and sadistic as Solution.\n\nShe likes startling people by using her \"Complete Invisibility\" spell and appearing behind them unnoticed.','2020-10-19 11:30:40','2020-10-19 11:30:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126870-DKc1B7cvoUu7.jpg','MC'),(1611,'Clementine','Age: Mid 20s\n Gender: Female \nRace: Human \nAffiliation: \nSlane Theocracy (Former) \nBlack Scripture (Former)\n Zurrernorn \nFamily: Quaiesse Hazeia Quintia (Brother)\n Occupation: Warrior \n\nClementine was a sadistic psychopath, obsessed with inflicting pain and torture on others. As a former member of the Black Scripture, Clementine was extremely confident in her abilities. She would go so far as to declare herself unbeatable until her unfortunate encounter with Ainz, who proved to be much more powerful than her. Before Clementine went rogue, she once held the position of 9th Seat in the Black Scripture. Besides betraying the Scripture, she also stole the magical Crown of Wisdom from one of the Six Miko Princesses of the Theocracy. Because of that, she has chosen to flee from her homeland and join Zurrernorn for protection.','2020-10-19 11:30:40','2020-10-19 11:30:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128401-ntBGw9BGMacx.jpg','SC'),(1612,'Yuri Alpha','The Vice-Captain, but de facto leader of the Pleiades. She is a Dullahan who uses a choker to keep her head attached to the rest of her body, causing her to appear to be human. She specializes in unarmed combat and uses Gauntlets in battle. She is programmed to behave like a teacher, because her creator was one, and the other Pleiades look up to her like a big sister. Like Sebas, she holds a primarily neutral stance towards outsiders, but unlike him, her sense of justice is not so strong that she\'d help people like him.<br></br>(Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:30:40','2020-10-19 11:30:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128288-rxWuyLQkxYBL.jpg','SC'),(1613,'Shizu Delta','One of the members of the battle maids originally created by someone except for Tabula Smaragdina.\n\nCZ2I28 Delta is an automaton battle maid and member of the \"Pleiades Six Stars,\" the battle maid squad of the Great Tomb of Nazarick.\n\nShe is a short girl with red-gold straight long hair. She wears an eyepatch over her left eye, while her right eye has an emerald color and target-mark on the pupil. She wears accessories with military camouflage patterns. While her face is beautiful, she does not show her emotions and talks in a flat tone.\n\nCZ2128 appears emotionless and has a silent nature. Her Karma is relatively high, which makes her, along with Yuri Alpha, one of the two \"safe\" Pleiades to humans. Though she usually ignores conversations from humans, sometimes there is a possibility to communicate with her. She hates cannibalism and likes cute things, such as Eclair.','2020-10-19 11:30:40','2020-10-19 11:30:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126841-zO8B5EQgj2dj.jpg','MC'),(1614,'Nigun Grid Luin','Nigun Grid Luin () was the captain of the Sunlight Scripture of the Slane Theocracy. He was ordered by the Cardinals to assassinate the Re-Estize Kingdom\'s strongest warrior, Gazef Stronoff.','2020-10-19 11:30:40','2020-10-19 11:30:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b141731-hiOr8aSP2tO3.jpg','MC'),(1615,'Enri Emmot','Age: 16\nGender: Female\nRace: Human Race\nAffiliation\nSorcerer Kingdom\nRe-Estize Kingdom (Formerly)\nis the Chieftain of Carne Village and the older sister of Nemu Emmot.\nRaised by a loving family, Enri has grown up to be a kind person, but has shown to have a strong character. As seen when she is willing to sacrifice herself for the sake of her little sister\'s life. She shows great leadership, being the new village head and defending the town from monsters with the other villagers.\nGrowing up in Carne Village and living there all her life, Enri has always lived the life of a simple farmer\'s daughter. Due to her healthy lifestyle, Enri has grown to be physically fit to the point where she is considered as one of the strongest five in the village.','2020-10-19 11:30:41','2020-10-19 11:30:41','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128405-Dy4SezyQ9OPV.jpg','MC'),(1616,'Hamusuke','Hamsuke resembles a giant Djungarian hamster with a long snake tail. Six sigils dot her silvery fur.\n\nBefore being inducted in the Great Tomb of Nazarick, Hamusuke was very boastful and prideful of her ability and power as the \"Virtuous King of the Forest.\" However, since meeting Momonga and witnessing the power of the denizens of Nazarick, she has seen how vastly inferior she is. She accepts this and swears loyalty to Momonga, willing to do anything to please his master and earn his keep.\n\n(Source: Overlord Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:42','2020-10-19 11:30:42','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128569-vRysqOLW66l0.jpg','SC'),(1617,'Nfirea Bareare','Gender: Male\nRace: Human\nAffiliation:\nSorcerer Kingdom\nRe-Estize Kingdom (Formerly)\nFamily\nLizzie Bareare (Grandmother)\nEnri Emmot (Wife)\nNemu Emmot (Sister-In-Law)\nOccupation:\nHerbalist\nPotion Maker\nResidence:\nE-Rantel (Formerly)\nCarne Village (Currently)\nBirthday: Middle Wind Month 18th Day\nHobby: Alchemical Experiments.\nNfirea is described as a nice, calm and timid person. He works hard at making potions with his grandmother every day.\nHe also has a minor inferiority complex, due to comparing himself to Ainz.\nAt a young age, Nfirea Bareare was raised by his grandmother Lizzie Bareare after his parents died; he only has murky impressions of them. His grandmother made him her apprentice and taught him everything she knew about herbs, alchemy, and potion-making. He met Enri Emmot while delivering potions to Carne Village and developed feelings for her.','2020-10-19 11:30:42','2020-10-19 11:30:42','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128404-5ncnTSZPNoKV.jpg','MC'),(1618,'Momonga','He is the guild master of Ainz Ooal Gown and regarded as the highest of the Almighty 41 Supreme Beings by the NPCs of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. He is also the creator of Pandora\'s Actor.\n\nA cautious and stingy person, Momonga always tries to plan and control details, avoiding any haphazard actions. Because he doesn\'t underestimate his opponents, he will usually overkill them. Since being transferred to a new world and becoming an actual Undead being, Momonga could feel himself becoming very cold and calculating, his emotions repressed.\n\nLoyal to his friends and creations, since becoming Lord ruler of Nazarick in the new world he acts with a certain degree of nobility for his devoted followers. Momonga only does things that will benefit Nazarick or himself, whether its information or prestige. Although he does have a sense of justice and doesn\'t hate humans as much as his followers, he holds no attachment to them, and he feels nothing toward their deaths.\n\n~!His real name is Satoru Suzuki.!~\n\n(Source: Overlord Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:43','2020-10-19 11:30:43','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89103-jNcqIFsGWfNp.jpg','SC'),(1619,'Aura Bella Fiora','One of the Guardians of the Sixth floor of Nazarick, alongside her twin brother Mare. She\'s very energetic and extroverted, in contrast with her brother. Aura is a 70-year-old Dark Elf. Despite constantly fighting, she and Shalltear are quite close. Aura specializes in beast-taming and fights with a long, bladed whip.','2020-10-19 11:30:44','2020-10-19 11:30:44','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n89129-5DrpwF5YEQxB.jpg','MC'),(1620,'Narberal Gamma','One of the Pleiades, combat maids of the Tenth floor under Sebas Tian. She\'s a Doppelgnger and, because she\'s one of the most human-looking of the maids, she is Momonga\'s companion in his exploration of the new world disguised as adventurers. Narberal takes great pride in this duty, often \"wearing\" it like a badge of honor. However, like most in Nazarick, she holds great disdain towards humans. This proves troublesome, as she becomes incredibly violent when human males make advances on her. \nWhile operating as a member of the adventuring guild, \"Darkness\", Narberal operates under the alias of \"Nabe\", which becomes \"Nabe, the Beautiful Lady\" when Darkness becomes famous. Narberal\'s beauty has been compared to that of the \"Golden Princess of Re-Estize\" by many of the country\'s inhabitants.','2020-10-19 11:30:44','2020-10-19 11:30:44','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89152-C8VHEJUgMcDK.jpg','MC'),(1621,'Mare Bello Fiore','One of the Guardians of the Sixth floor of Nazarick alongside his twin sister Aura. He\'s rather shy and calm in comparison to his sister, although he can fight and be ruthless when necessary. Like his sister, Mare is a Dark Elf. Mare specializes in Druid magic, capable of twisting the earth to his whims.','2020-10-19 11:30:44','2020-10-19 11:30:44','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89126-0L0VoRL1LVgc.jpg','SC'),(1622,'Shalltear Bloodfallen','The Guardian of the First, Second, and Third floors of Nazarick, she has the form of a beautiful vampire girl. She\'s also in love with Momonga. She and Albedo constantly clash for his attention. While the two don\'t mind sharing Momonga, they still fight for superiority and who would ultimately appeal to Momonga. Shalltear is one of the most powerful guardians, allegedly capable of going toe-to-toe with Albedo. ~!Due to an incident where she is subjected to mind control by a member of the Black Scripture, she ends up unintentionally rebelling against Nazarick.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:45','2020-10-19 11:30:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89121-zE0gzCp5sj0A.jpg','MC'),(1623,'Pandora\'s Actor','The Area Guardian in charge of the Treasury and finances of Nazarick, who was created by Ains himself. He\'s a Doppelgnger whose face is a simple egghead with three holes dressed in a Neo-Nazi-esque uniform. In Momonga\'s original design, he\'s the combination of everything that he though was cool, with exaggerated gestures and body language. His existence embarrasses Ains, but at the same time knows he\'s the NPC he can trust the most and the only one who can perform all his master\'s tasks without misunderstanding his intentions. He\'s on the same level as the Floor Guardians, and can copy the appearance and skills of anyone he has seen.','2020-10-19 11:30:45','2020-10-19 11:30:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89154-jbsFsEsjL3aS.jpg','SC'),(1624,'Demiurge','The Guardian of the Seventh floor of Nazarick, with the form of a demon wearing glasses. Demiurge is very intelligent, but is also considered the most evil NPC on Nazarick. He greatly enjoys the suffering of others, made clear by his vicious experiments on prisoners. He\'s in charge of tactics and defenses of Nazarick. Among the Guardians, he gets along the best with Mare, since he understands the more cunning side of the Dark Elf.','2020-10-19 11:30:45','2020-10-19 11:30:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89125-7bQqj1LgvGgS.jpg','MC'),(1625,'Albedo','The overseer of the Floor Guardians and one of the most powerful NPC in Nazarick. She takes the form of a beautiful woman with fallen angel wings and horns. Because Ainz modified her settings on a whim, she ends up madly in love with him. Albedo\'s romantic obsessions are so strong that if Ainz were to even glance at her body, she would immediately become excited. Albedo\'s obsession with Ainz has led him to greatly regret his actions. While she tries to act calm, as befitting of her role, any perceived insult against Ainz or Nazarick, real or imagined, sends her into a rage. Like most inhabitants of Nazarick, she despises humans which she refers to as \"lower life-forms.\" ~!Though the reason is not yet known, Albedo holds a strong hatred towards all of the 41 Supreme Beings except for Ainz. It is hinted that she is scheming to annihilate all the other guild members if they are found.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:45','2020-10-19 11:30:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89122-AX3GMHvqa0Ye.png','MC'),(1626,'Solution Epsilon','One of the Pleiades. She\'s a slime and one of the most dangerous Pleiades to humans, since she enjoys devouring humans alive. An assassin and poisoner who can decide to protect or dissolve things she absorbs, she can also control the speed of her digestion. She gets along with Shalltear because of their similar tastes','2020-10-19 11:30:45','2020-10-19 11:30:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89123-LgUt6CMg22eB.jpg','SC'),(1627,'Cocytus','The Guardian of the Fifth floor of Nazarick, he has the form of a huge, four-armed, insect-like humanoid with the power to control ice. He has a warrior personality and respects anyone with a fighting spirit. He\'s in charge of the security of Nazarick, and later becomes responsible for a tribe of lizardmen that Ainz has him conquer.','2020-10-19 11:30:45','2020-10-19 11:30:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89138-tVwPzfMsh3qg.jpg','MC'),(1628,'Sebas Tian','The butler of the Tenth floor of Nazarick, who specializes in unarmed combat, with power comparable with the other floor Guardians. He has the appearance of an elderly gentleman with a neat beard, but is actually of a species known as Dragonoids. He has a strong sense of justice, like his creator. Thus, he dislikes when the other Guardians kill humans needlessly. Because of their opposite personalities, he and Demiurge don\'t get along.','2020-10-19 11:30:46','2020-10-19 11:30:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89155-Rl0sWa0fAABk.jpg','SC'),(1629,'Shizu Delta','One of the members of the battle maids originally created by someone except for Tabula Smaragdina.\n\nCZ2I28 Delta is an automaton battle maid and member of the \"Pleiades Six Stars,\" the battle maid squad of the Great Tomb of Nazarick.\n\nShe is a short girl with red-gold straight long hair. She wears an eyepatch over her left eye, while her right eye has an emerald color and target-mark on the pupil. She wears accessories with military camouflage patterns. While her face is beautiful, she does not show her emotions and talks in a flat tone.\n\nCZ2128 appears emotionless and has a silent nature. Her Karma is relatively high, which makes her, along with Yuri Alpha, one of the two \"safe\" Pleiades to humans. Though she usually ignores conversations from humans, sometimes there is a possibility to communicate with her. She hates cannibalism and likes cute things, such as Eclair.','2020-10-19 11:30:46','2020-10-19 11:30:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126841-zO8B5EQgj2dj.jpg','MC'),(1630,'Zaryusu Shasha','Zaryusu Shasha is a lizardman of the Green Claw Tribe, and he\'s the younger brother of its chieftain, Shasuryu Shasha. His scales are dark green and black charcoal in color. A very wise individual, he is also regarded as the strongest lizardman and he is the wielder of the magical blade Frost Pain, one of the few precious treasures the lizardmen possess.\n\nZaryusu is a traveler, which is the name given to a lizardman who left the village in order to explore the outside world, and has a crimson brand/tattoo on his chest which denotes his status as such.  Travelers are very respected individuals among the lizardmen, but conversely they don\'t have a say in any important matters, which heavily implies they might be socially shunned.\n\nHe has a Hydra as a pet named Rororo. Zaryusu stumbled upon it during his travels after finding it had been abandoned by its mother. Rororo is actually a deformed Hydra, because it has only four heads, while normally hydras have six. Rororo regards Zaryusu as his parent and would do practically anything to protect him.\n\n~!Zaryusu falls in love with Crusch Lulu the moment he meets her, and claiming it\'s love at first sight, he immediately proposes in marriage. She eventually reciprocated his feelings and just before the lizardmen\'s final battle, Crusch fearful that he might die asks him to impregnate her with his child.\nAinz proposed that the lizardmen fight for the right to their freedom in a duel against Ainz\'s champion, Cocytus. Due to the massive skill gap, he was among those killed by Cocytus, although it should be noted he was the last one to be slain. He is later resurrected when the lizardmen swear loyalty to Ainz.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:46','2020-10-19 11:30:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127431-Q8tK20xNU9Bb.jpg','MC'),(1631,'Evileye','An adamantite-class adventurer for the Blue Rose.  She is of the same race as Demiurge and is thought to be one of the strongest adventurers in the capital. ','2020-10-19 11:30:46','2020-10-19 11:30:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n125881-G7IbEWaUyCqc.png','MC'),(1632,'Lakyus Alvein Dale Aindra','Lakyus is an adamantite ranked adventurer and the leader of Blue Rose. She is part of the nobility, friend of the Re-Estize Royal Family, and loyal to the people of Re-Estize Kingdom. She acts as a faith based magic caster and warrior priestess of her adventurer group.\n<br><br>\nShe is described as a young women that has long blonde hair with green eyes and pink lips that showed a healthy gleam. Her beauty falls short of Renner but overflows with a different charm.\n<br><br>\nLakyus is a very bright person who enjoys adventuring with her friends. She sometimes acts weird like wearing apparently meaningless rings or fighting against her dark personality, making her other team members worry about her actually becoming evil. When Lakyus was a young girl, she decided to become an adventurer after hearing the adventure stories about Red Drop. She ran away from home to have an adventure, while she was still inexperienced, she was saved by Gagaran and the two became partners.\n<br><br>\nLakyus becomes one of the strongest adventurers of the kingdom at the age of 19 for her near Heroic-level abilities. She is also one of the few users of revival magic.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Overlord Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:46','2020-10-19 11:30:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n127667-TJXgovPZREO6.jpg','MC'),(1633,'Crusch Lulu','Crusch Lulu is an albino white lizardman and the chieftain of the Red Eye tribe. Over the course of time, she proved herself to be a strong practitioner of magic. Currently, she is the strongest of all the magic casters that exist within the lizardmen tribes. Her magic consists of controlling nature and summoning spirits to assist her in different ways.\n\nShe has snow white scales and spotless purity, bright red eyes like rubies and slim limbs. Since she was born an albino, in the lizardmen community that would normally mean that she would be abandoned. In Lulu\'s case however, her parents decided to raise her even with this genetic fault. Due to her this, Crusch burns easily in the sun and is very weak against direct sunlight, which forces her to wear a ridiculous bush outfit during the day. Zenberu teases her about it and refers to her as \'Plant Monster\'.\n\n~!He met Zaryusu when he visited Red Eye tribe in order to propose the formation of an alliance. She revealed that when the famine in the Wetlands occurred, the Red Eye tribe managed to stave off extinction through fratricide. However, unable to bear with the guilt and shame, Crusch led a rebellion against the previous chief. Her rebellion was a success and the mantle of leadership was passed down to her. \nEventually she fell in love with Zaryusu, a feeling had been mutual since the moment he had met her. Before the lizardmen\'s duel with Cocytus, Crusch asked his lover to impregnate her, fearful that he might die. Indeed, after he was slain in battle, Ainz made a deal with Crusch Lulu where he would revive Zaryusu in exchange of her keeping a close watch on whether there are lizardmen thinking of rebelling. Even after the assimilation of her tribe, Crusch is still fearful of Ainz, as when he inquired about her and Zaryusu\'s newly born child, and thinks that Ainz will take their child away. !~','2020-10-19 11:30:46','2020-10-19 11:30:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127434-4niQP00EPWzf.jpg','SC'),(1634,'Jircniv Rune Farlord El Nix','Jircniv Rune Farlord El Nix is the current Emperor of the Baharuth Empire. He is also known as the Bloody Emperor.','2020-10-19 11:30:47','2020-10-19 11:30:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126961-jMnWXTyZVz3K.jpg','MC'),(1635,'Lupusregina Beta','A member of the \"Pleiades Six Stars\", the battle maid squad of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. She serves as the role of battle cleric and focuses on healing magic. In terms of combat ability, she possesses the highest physical defense and resistances among the Pleiades, and has balanced stats overall. Being a werewolf, she is weak to silver weapons, but is blessed with resistance against other metals.\n\nHer appearance is that of a brown-skinned beauty with amber-colored eyes, and red hair which she ties in two long braids. She wears a maid uniform with short sleeves and long black gloves, white stockings, and a skirt that has a long slit on its left side. She is usually seen carrying her signature weapon slung across her back, a menacing black and silver scepter which looks like and oversized religious symbol, the Crosier.\n\nLupusregina boasts a very sociable and outgoing personality, and seems very friendly, even towards humans, a race considered unworthy of respect by other beings of Nazarick. For example, she adds \"-chan\" to the other maid\'s names, and often likes teasing Enri with lewd jokes. The Homunculus Maids (the ordinary maids of Nazarick) are convinced she\'s the friendliest of the Pleiades and even believe that being approached by her can be a sign of good fortune. However, her fellow battle-maid Yuri Alpha has commented that Lupusregina\'s friendliness is merely a facade, and that in reality she can be as brutal and sadistic as Solution.\n\nShe likes startling people by using her \"Complete Invisibility\" spell and appearing behind them unnoticed.','2020-10-19 11:30:47','2020-10-19 11:30:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126870-DKc1B7cvoUu7.jpg','SC'),(1636,'Gagaran','She is an adamantite ranked adventurer and a warrior from Blue Rose','2020-10-19 11:30:48','2020-10-19 11:30:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n127669-8nYP4EnGbCTD.jpg','MC'),(1637,'Touch Me','Touch Me is one of the original founding members of the Ainz Ooal Gown guild and one of the strongest warriors in YGGDRASIL. He is regarded as one of the Forty-One Supreme Beings by the NPCs of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. He is the creator of Sebas Tian. At some point in YGGDRASIL, Touch Me participated in an official martial tournament and defeated all of his adversaries. By winning the tournament, he was awarded a special prize that comes in two. Firstly, he was given a special job class known as the \"World Champion\" of lfheimr, and in addition he was awarded with the pure white armor set called \"Compliance with Law.\"\n\nTouch Me\'s outfit consists of shining white armor and a helm. His chest piece contains a huge sapphire embedded in the middle, which radiates with pure and divine light.\nHe is also adorned with a reddish cape attached around his right shoulder. Additionally, he is armed with both sword and shield. Touch Me\'s actual facial appearance in real life is said to look exactly like Sebas Tian. \n\nAs Touch Me played YGGDRASIL, he decided to assist the heteromorphic players during a time when they were being hunted down for fun through PKing. Thus, that was how he met Momonga, by saving him from a PK party; the two started becoming friends since then. There was also a time when Bukubukuchagama could not find a party to adventure with due to her appearance, so he was the one who approached her before anyone else. Afterwards, they formed a party together with other non-human characters and organized the First Nine, also known as Nine\'s Own Goal.\n\nAfter that, the clan grew with members chosen and invited personally by Touch Me, becoming a stable and friendly group. However, he felt that the clan was beginning to slowly fall apart. During one of its meetings, Touch Me was seen looking troubled by Momonga and Peroroncino, but their concerns were brushed aside. Once all the clan members had arrived, Touch Me started the meeting by having Nishikienrai report his latest discovery of a new unexplored dungeon. After the various clan members discussed the pros and cons of the dungeon, it was agreed that the clan would launch a raid.  Touch Me then moved unto the next point in the agenda of the meeting, in which he formally announced his intention to dissolve the Clan. His declaration elicited many protests, however he informed them that he wished to form Nine\'s Own Goal as an official Guild. Hearing the majority of the Clan concur to the idea, Touch Me decided to turn down the suggestion to become the Guildmaster. Just as several members of the groups argued about who should become Guildmaster, Touch Me restored order and nominated Momonga as their new guild leader, a proposal which many accepted. \n\nTouch Me is looked upon as very righteous and fair. He would help people in times of trouble without hesitation, and scolds his friends if one of them did something wrong. Momonga describes Touch Me as someone who is a straightforward person, the kind who was very direct in his words and deeds. However, Touch Me can be self-reflective at times, as evidenced when he was willing to step down as clan leader and proposed for someone else to be the guild master rather than him. If what Ulbert said is true; about him chasing away one of their former clansman leaving the game, then this might be part of the reason why Touch Me decided to step down voluntarily as a candidate for Guildmaster. \n\n(Source: Overlord Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:48','2020-10-19 11:30:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127437-HHvKoQEugGhN.jpg','MC'),(1638,'Tina','Tina is an adamantite ranked adventurer and a member of Blue Rose. She is the twin sister of Tia.','2020-10-19 11:30:48','2020-10-19 11:30:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n127670-5YG4iz8L8TSS.jpg','SC'),(1639,'Renner Theiere Chardelon Ryle Vaiself','Renner is the third princess of Re-Estize Kingdom and the childhood friend of Climb. She is also known as the Golden Princess for being a reformer who brought major changes within the kingdom such as the ban on slavery. She is the youngest daughter of King Lanposa III and the younger sister of Barbro and Zanac.\n\nRenner is described as a young girl with long golden hair, silky smooth and supple as it drapes over the back of her neck. She has vibrant, dark blue eyes that shine like sapphires filled with warmth. She wears a fashionable white dress which further strengthens her image of purity. Around her neck hangs a golden necklace, appearing to symbolize her noble soul.\n\nRenner is known publicly as the Golden Princess for her benevolence and kindness. While she is believed to be a saint, in reality she has a psychopathic personality and doesn\'t care about the feelings of others. The only exception to this is her childhood friend, Climb. If Climb was wounded, she would declare that anyone involved would be ruthlessly killed.','2020-10-19 11:30:48','2020-10-19 11:30:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n127241-jDj7iccxQGdT.jpg','SC'),(1640,'Zenberu Gugu','Zenberu Gugu is a lizardman and the chieftain of one of the five lizardmen tribes, the Dragon Tusk Tribe. He is a traveler, a lizardman who has explored the outside world. In terms of brute force, he is most likely the strongest of all the lizardmen.  Zenberu is not a warrior by profession, but rather a monk which fights utilizing Ki to enhance his natural physical abilities. He often prefers to fight unarmed, using his claws to rip apart his enemies. In armed combat, he wields a three-meter-long steel halberd, a parting gift he received from an acquaintance of his, a dwarf.\n\nWith a very muscular constitution, he is quite tall for a lizardman, well exceeding two meters in height. His body, covered by several scars, gives the clear impression that he is veteran of battle. His most bizarre feature are his asymmetrical arms. Similar in trait with a fiddler crab, his right arm is especially thicker and muscular when compared to his left. His left arms ring finger and pinky are completely gone. The crimson \"traveler\" brand burned in the form of a two headed snake is displayed on the center of his chest. Overall, his appearance is very crocodile-like, and when he talks, his teeth clash together, making it difficult for others to discern whether he is being casual or threatening.\n\nZenberu is quite blunt when in a conversation, having no need for pointless formalities. Intead of diplomacy, he favors solving disputes with duels, and has somewhat of a cockish attitude, since he likes to challenge any strong individuals he meets. However, while in battle, he can be quite calm and composed, as opposed to brash or reckless.\n\n~!Zenberu is among those slain by Cocytus, and was later resurrected.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:48','2020-10-19 11:30:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127433-P6STh05zrwRb.jpg','SC'),(1641,'Shasuryu Shasha','Shasuryu Shasha is the leader of the lizardmen\'s tribes and chieftain of the Green Claw Tribe. His younger brother is Zaryusu. He is a skilled warrior in addition to a proficient druid, which allows him to complement his weapon attacks with magic. Unlike other lizardmen who have bone weapons, his sword is forged of pure steel.\n\nIncredibly huge in stature, he has dark green and charcoal black scales, a trait which he shares with his younger brother. Numerous scars are present all over his body, the most prominent of which is an old, long white scar, which stands out amongst his dark-colored scales.\n\nShasuryu follows his ancestors traditions, but he is also not blinded by them and is one of the more practical minded lizardmen, as evidenced by the decision to support his brother\'s innovative idea, which led to the creation of the fishery farms near the Green Tribe village.\n\n~!Shasuryu Shasha led the chieftains, save Crusch Lulu, and a band of the strongest warriors of the Lizardmen Alliance in the duel against Cocytus. The majority of the warriors perished in one fell swoop due to Cocytus\'s freezing ability, and only the chieftains remained. Ultimately, Shasuryu and Zaryusu were last lizardmen to be left standing. He sacrificed his life in order to create an opening for his brother to attack Cocytus. Unfortunately, his brother was unable to cause damage, and was also slain shortly. However, their acts and sacrifices in battle were not meaningless, since they earned Cocytus\' respect, which later influenced Ainz\'s decision to resurrect them.\nAfter Zaryusu was resurrected by Ainz\'s magic, the lizardman petitioned his brother and Zenberu be resurrected. Ainz replied he would consider his request, which he later granted.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:48','2020-10-19 11:30:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127432-i76rwiFQWiO5.jpg','SC'),(1642,'Gazef Stronoff','Gazeff Stronoff is the Warrior Captain of the Re-Estize Kingdom and King Ramposa III\'s personal bodyguard, and professes his utmost loyalty to him. Incredibly talented with the sword and well-versed in martial arts, he is famously considered the strongest warrior in the entire kingdom, and commands the respect and admiration of everyone who knows his name. Due to internal power struggles among the nobles in the kingdom, Gazeff is not knighted, so the King granted him the title of \"Warrior Captain\", which allows him to command his own unit comprised of \"Warrior Troops\".\n\nBorn a commoner in a frontier village, he later became a mercenary. During his travels, he encountered a former adamantite-ranked adventurer who taught him his extraordinary swordsmanship. He participated in the grand tournament and defeated Brain Unglaus, becoming the champion and earning the King\'s trust.\n\nA muscular man in his thirties, he has a sunbathed face with noticeable wrinkles and dark-colored eyes. His short-trimmed hair is dark brown in color. He is a strong-willed individual who is willing to sacrifice his life in order to protect the citizens of the kingdom. Usually he is clad in a breastplate ornamented with red bands across his chest and shoulder pads, and considerably less protection on the lower half of his body. As Warrior Captain, he has the right to wield the five treasures of the Kingdom, of which merely four are publicly known. These are the Guardian Armor, made of extremely hard steel, the Amulet of Immortality, which grants regeneration, the Gauntlets of Endurance, said to grant endless stamina, and Razor Edge, a magically enchanted sword which is believed to be capable of cutting through armor like paper.','2020-10-19 11:30:48','2020-10-19 11:30:48','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126869-HZeyTV5SR1QU.jpg','SC'),(1643,'Momonga','He is the guild master of Ainz Ooal Gown and regarded as the highest of the Almighty 41 Supreme Beings by the NPCs of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. He is also the creator of Pandora\'s Actor.\n\nA cautious and stingy person, Momonga always tries to plan and control details, avoiding any haphazard actions. Because he doesn\'t underestimate his opponents, he will usually overkill them. Since being transferred to a new world and becoming an actual Undead being, Momonga could feel himself becoming very cold and calculating, his emotions repressed.\n\nLoyal to his friends and creations, since becoming Lord ruler of Nazarick in the new world he acts with a certain degree of nobility for his devoted followers. Momonga only does things that will benefit Nazarick or himself, whether its information or prestige. Although he does have a sense of justice and doesn\'t hate humans as much as his followers, he holds no attachment to them, and he feels nothing toward their deaths.\n\n~!His real name is Satoru Suzuki.!~\n\n(Source: Overlord Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:49','2020-10-19 11:30:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89103-jNcqIFsGWfNp.jpg','SC'),(1644,'Solution Epsilon','One of the Pleiades. She\'s a slime and one of the most dangerous Pleiades to humans, since she enjoys devouring humans alive. An assassin and poisoner who can decide to protect or dissolve things she absorbs, she can also control the speed of her digestion. She gets along with Shalltear because of their similar tastes','2020-10-19 11:30:49','2020-10-19 11:30:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89123-LgUt6CMg22eB.jpg','MC'),(1645,'Aura Bella Fiora','One of the Guardians of the Sixth floor of Nazarick, alongside her twin brother Mare. She\'s very energetic and extroverted, in contrast with her brother. Aura is a 70-year-old Dark Elf. Despite constantly fighting, she and Shalltear are quite close. Aura specializes in beast-taming and fights with a long, bladed whip.','2020-10-19 11:30:49','2020-10-19 11:30:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n89129-5DrpwF5YEQxB.jpg','SC'),(1646,'Sebas Tian','The butler of the Tenth floor of Nazarick, who specializes in unarmed combat, with power comparable with the other floor Guardians. He has the appearance of an elderly gentleman with a neat beard, but is actually of a species known as Dragonoids. He has a strong sense of justice, like his creator. Thus, he dislikes when the other Guardians kill humans needlessly. Because of their opposite personalities, he and Demiurge don\'t get along.','2020-10-19 11:30:49','2020-10-19 11:30:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89155-Rl0sWa0fAABk.jpg','MC'),(1647,'Narberal Gamma','One of the Pleiades, combat maids of the Tenth floor under Sebas Tian. She\'s a Doppelgnger and, because she\'s one of the most human-looking of the maids, she is Momonga\'s companion in his exploration of the new world disguised as adventurers. Narberal takes great pride in this duty, often \"wearing\" it like a badge of honor. However, like most in Nazarick, she holds great disdain towards humans. This proves troublesome, as she becomes incredibly violent when human males make advances on her. \nWhile operating as a member of the adventuring guild, \"Darkness\", Narberal operates under the alias of \"Nabe\", which becomes \"Nabe, the Beautiful Lady\" when Darkness becomes famous. Narberal\'s beauty has been compared to that of the \"Golden Princess of Re-Estize\" by many of the country\'s inhabitants.','2020-10-19 11:30:49','2020-10-19 11:30:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89152-C8VHEJUgMcDK.jpg','SC'),(1648,'Demiurge','The Guardian of the Seventh floor of Nazarick, with the form of a demon wearing glasses. Demiurge is very intelligent, but is also considered the most evil NPC on Nazarick. He greatly enjoys the suffering of others, made clear by his vicious experiments on prisoners. He\'s in charge of tactics and defenses of Nazarick. Among the Guardians, he gets along the best with Mare, since he understands the more cunning side of the Dark Elf.','2020-10-19 11:30:49','2020-10-19 11:30:49','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89125-7bQqj1LgvGgS.jpg','MC'),(1649,'Shalltear Bloodfallen','The Guardian of the First, Second, and Third floors of Nazarick, she has the form of a beautiful vampire girl. She\'s also in love with Momonga. She and Albedo constantly clash for his attention. While the two don\'t mind sharing Momonga, they still fight for superiority and who would ultimately appeal to Momonga. Shalltear is one of the most powerful guardians, allegedly capable of going toe-to-toe with Albedo. ~!Due to an incident where she is subjected to mind control by a member of the Black Scripture, she ends up unintentionally rebelling against Nazarick.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:50','2020-10-19 11:30:50','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89121-zE0gzCp5sj0A.jpg','MC'),(1650,'Mare Bello Fiore','One of the Guardians of the Sixth floor of Nazarick alongside his twin sister Aura. He\'s rather shy and calm in comparison to his sister, although he can fight and be ruthless when necessary. Like his sister, Mare is a Dark Elf. Mare specializes in Druid magic, capable of twisting the earth to his whims.','2020-10-19 11:30:50','2020-10-19 11:30:50','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89126-0L0VoRL1LVgc.jpg','MC'),(1651,'Albedo','The overseer of the Floor Guardians and one of the most powerful NPC in Nazarick. She takes the form of a beautiful woman with fallen angel wings and horns. Because Ainz modified her settings on a whim, she ends up madly in love with him. Albedo\'s romantic obsessions are so strong that if Ainz were to even glance at her body, she would immediately become excited. Albedo\'s obsession with Ainz has led him to greatly regret his actions. While she tries to act calm, as befitting of her role, any perceived insult against Ainz or Nazarick, real or imagined, sends her into a rage. Like most inhabitants of Nazarick, she despises humans which she refers to as \"lower life-forms.\" ~!Though the reason is not yet known, Albedo holds a strong hatred towards all of the 41 Supreme Beings except for Ainz. It is hinted that she is scheming to annihilate all the other guild members if they are found.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:51','2020-10-19 11:30:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89122-AX3GMHvqa0Ye.png','SC'),(1652,'Gazef Stronoff','Gazeff Stronoff is the Warrior Captain of the Re-Estize Kingdom and King Ramposa III\'s personal bodyguard, and professes his utmost loyalty to him. Incredibly talented with the sword and well-versed in martial arts, he is famously considered the strongest warrior in the entire kingdom, and commands the respect and admiration of everyone who knows his name. Due to internal power struggles among the nobles in the kingdom, Gazeff is not knighted, so the King granted him the title of \"Warrior Captain\", which allows him to command his own unit comprised of \"Warrior Troops\".\n\nBorn a commoner in a frontier village, he later became a mercenary. During his travels, he encountered a former adamantite-ranked adventurer who taught him his extraordinary swordsmanship. He participated in the grand tournament and defeated Brain Unglaus, becoming the champion and earning the King\'s trust.\n\nA muscular man in his thirties, he has a sunbathed face with noticeable wrinkles and dark-colored eyes. His short-trimmed hair is dark brown in color. He is a strong-willed individual who is willing to sacrifice his life in order to protect the citizens of the kingdom. Usually he is clad in a breastplate ornamented with red bands across his chest and shoulder pads, and considerably less protection on the lower half of his body. As Warrior Captain, he has the right to wield the five treasures of the Kingdom, of which merely four are publicly known. These are the Guardian Armor, made of extremely hard steel, the Amulet of Immortality, which grants regeneration, the Gauntlets of Endurance, said to grant endless stamina, and Razor Edge, a magically enchanted sword which is believed to be capable of cutting through armor like paper.','2020-10-19 11:30:51','2020-10-19 11:30:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126869-HZeyTV5SR1QU.jpg','MC'),(1653,'Cocytus','The Guardian of the Fifth floor of Nazarick, he has the form of a huge, four-armed, insect-like humanoid with the power to control ice. He has a warrior personality and respects anyone with a fighting spirit. He\'s in charge of the security of Nazarick, and later becomes responsible for a tribe of lizardmen that Ainz has him conquer.','2020-10-19 11:30:51','2020-10-19 11:30:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/89138-tVwPzfMsh3qg.jpg','SC'),(1654,'Lakyus Alvein Dale Aindra','Lakyus is an adamantite ranked adventurer and the leader of Blue Rose. She is part of the nobility, friend of the Re-Estize Royal Family, and loyal to the people of Re-Estize Kingdom. She acts as a faith based magic caster and warrior priestess of her adventurer group.\n<br><br>\nShe is described as a young women that has long blonde hair with green eyes and pink lips that showed a healthy gleam. Her beauty falls short of Renner but overflows with a different charm.\n<br><br>\nLakyus is a very bright person who enjoys adventuring with her friends. She sometimes acts weird like wearing apparently meaningless rings or fighting against her dark personality, making her other team members worry about her actually becoming evil. When Lakyus was a young girl, she decided to become an adventurer after hearing the adventure stories about Red Drop. She ran away from home to have an adventure, while she was still inexperienced, she was saved by Gagaran and the two became partners.\n<br><br>\nLakyus becomes one of the strongest adventurers of the kingdom at the age of 19 for her near Heroic-level abilities. She is also one of the few users of revival magic.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Overlord Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:30:51','2020-10-19 11:30:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n127667-TJXgovPZREO6.jpg','SC'),(1655,'Jircniv Rune Farlord El Nix','Jircniv Rune Farlord El Nix is the current Emperor of the Baharuth Empire. He is also known as the Bloody Emperor.','2020-10-19 11:30:51','2020-10-19 11:30:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126961-jMnWXTyZVz3K.jpg','SC'),(1656,'Zaryusu Shasha','Zaryusu Shasha is a lizardman of the Green Claw Tribe, and he\'s the younger brother of its chieftain, Shasuryu Shasha. His scales are dark green and black charcoal in color. A very wise individual, he is also regarded as the strongest lizardman and he is the wielder of the magical blade Frost Pain, one of the few precious treasures the lizardmen possess.\n\nZaryusu is a traveler, which is the name given to a lizardman who left the village in order to explore the outside world, and has a crimson brand/tattoo on his chest which denotes his status as such.  Travelers are very respected individuals among the lizardmen, but conversely they don\'t have a say in any important matters, which heavily implies they might be socially shunned.\n\nHe has a Hydra as a pet named Rororo. Zaryusu stumbled upon it during his travels after finding it had been abandoned by its mother. Rororo is actually a deformed Hydra, because it has only four heads, while normally hydras have six. Rororo regards Zaryusu as his parent and would do practically anything to protect him.\n\n~!Zaryusu falls in love with Crusch Lulu the moment he meets her, and claiming it\'s love at first sight, he immediately proposes in marriage. She eventually reciprocated his feelings and just before the lizardmen\'s final battle, Crusch fearful that he might die asks him to impregnate her with his child.\nAinz proposed that the lizardmen fight for the right to their freedom in a duel against Ainz\'s champion, Cocytus. Due to the massive skill gap, he was among those killed by Cocytus, although it should be noted he was the last one to be slain. He is later resurrected when the lizardmen swear loyalty to Ainz.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:51','2020-10-19 11:30:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127431-Q8tK20xNU9Bb.jpg','MC'),(1657,'Lupusregina Beta','A member of the \"Pleiades Six Stars\", the battle maid squad of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. She serves as the role of battle cleric and focuses on healing magic. In terms of combat ability, she possesses the highest physical defense and resistances among the Pleiades, and has balanced stats overall. Being a werewolf, she is weak to silver weapons, but is blessed with resistance against other metals.\n\nHer appearance is that of a brown-skinned beauty with amber-colored eyes, and red hair which she ties in two long braids. She wears a maid uniform with short sleeves and long black gloves, white stockings, and a skirt that has a long slit on its left side. She is usually seen carrying her signature weapon slung across her back, a menacing black and silver scepter which looks like and oversized religious symbol, the Crosier.\n\nLupusregina boasts a very sociable and outgoing personality, and seems very friendly, even towards humans, a race considered unworthy of respect by other beings of Nazarick. For example, she adds \"-chan\" to the other maid\'s names, and often likes teasing Enri with lewd jokes. The Homunculus Maids (the ordinary maids of Nazarick) are convinced she\'s the friendliest of the Pleiades and even believe that being approached by her can be a sign of good fortune. However, her fellow battle-maid Yuri Alpha has commented that Lupusregina\'s friendliness is merely a facade, and that in reality she can be as brutal and sadistic as Solution.\n\nShe likes startling people by using her \"Complete Invisibility\" spell and appearing behind them unnoticed.','2020-10-19 11:30:52','2020-10-19 11:30:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126870-DKc1B7cvoUu7.jpg','MC'),(1658,'Zenberu Gugu','Zenberu Gugu is a lizardman and the chieftain of one of the five lizardmen tribes, the Dragon Tusk Tribe. He is a traveler, a lizardman who has explored the outside world. In terms of brute force, he is most likely the strongest of all the lizardmen.  Zenberu is not a warrior by profession, but rather a monk which fights utilizing Ki to enhance his natural physical abilities. He often prefers to fight unarmed, using his claws to rip apart his enemies. In armed combat, he wields a three-meter-long steel halberd, a parting gift he received from an acquaintance of his, a dwarf.\n\nWith a very muscular constitution, he is quite tall for a lizardman, well exceeding two meters in height. His body, covered by several scars, gives the clear impression that he is veteran of battle. His most bizarre feature are his asymmetrical arms. Similar in trait with a fiddler crab, his right arm is especially thicker and muscular when compared to his left. His left arms ring finger and pinky are completely gone. The crimson \"traveler\" brand burned in the form of a two headed snake is displayed on the center of his chest. Overall, his appearance is very crocodile-like, and when he talks, his teeth clash together, making it difficult for others to discern whether he is being casual or threatening.\n\nZenberu is quite blunt when in a conversation, having no need for pointless formalities. Intead of diplomacy, he favors solving disputes with duels, and has somewhat of a cockish attitude, since he likes to challenge any strong individuals he meets. However, while in battle, he can be quite calm and composed, as opposed to brash or reckless.\n\n~!Zenberu is among those slain by Cocytus, and was later resurrected.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:52','2020-10-19 11:30:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127433-P6STh05zrwRb.jpg','MC'),(1659,'Shizu Delta','One of the members of the battle maids originally created by someone except for Tabula Smaragdina.\n\nCZ2I28 Delta is an automaton battle maid and member of the \"Pleiades Six Stars,\" the battle maid squad of the Great Tomb of Nazarick.\n\nShe is a short girl with red-gold straight long hair. She wears an eyepatch over her left eye, while her right eye has an emerald color and target-mark on the pupil. She wears accessories with military camouflage patterns. While her face is beautiful, she does not show her emotions and talks in a flat tone.\n\nCZ2128 appears emotionless and has a silent nature. Her Karma is relatively high, which makes her, along with Yuri Alpha, one of the two \"safe\" Pleiades to humans. Though she usually ignores conversations from humans, sometimes there is a possibility to communicate with her. She hates cannibalism and likes cute things, such as Eclair.','2020-10-19 11:30:52','2020-10-19 11:30:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126841-zO8B5EQgj2dj.jpg','SC'),(1660,'Crusch Lulu','Crusch Lulu is an albino white lizardman and the chieftain of the Red Eye tribe. Over the course of time, she proved herself to be a strong practitioner of magic. Currently, she is the strongest of all the magic casters that exist within the lizardmen tribes. Her magic consists of controlling nature and summoning spirits to assist her in different ways.\n\nShe has snow white scales and spotless purity, bright red eyes like rubies and slim limbs. Since she was born an albino, in the lizardmen community that would normally mean that she would be abandoned. In Lulu\'s case however, her parents decided to raise her even with this genetic fault. Due to her this, Crusch burns easily in the sun and is very weak against direct sunlight, which forces her to wear a ridiculous bush outfit during the day. Zenberu teases her about it and refers to her as \'Plant Monster\'.\n\n~!He met Zaryusu when he visited Red Eye tribe in order to propose the formation of an alliance. She revealed that when the famine in the Wetlands occurred, the Red Eye tribe managed to stave off extinction through fratricide. However, unable to bear with the guilt and shame, Crusch led a rebellion against the previous chief. Her rebellion was a success and the mantle of leadership was passed down to her. \nEventually she fell in love with Zaryusu, a feeling had been mutual since the moment he had met her. Before the lizardmen\'s duel with Cocytus, Crusch asked his lover to impregnate her, fearful that he might die. Indeed, after he was slain in battle, Ainz made a deal with Crusch Lulu where he would revive Zaryusu in exchange of her keeping a close watch on whether there are lizardmen thinking of rebelling. Even after the assimilation of her tribe, Crusch is still fearful of Ainz, as when he inquired about her and Zaryusu\'s newly born child, and thinks that Ainz will take their child away. !~','2020-10-19 11:30:52','2020-10-19 11:30:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127434-4niQP00EPWzf.jpg','SC'),(1661,'Renner Theiere Chardelon Ryle Vaiself','Renner is the third princess of Re-Estize Kingdom and the childhood friend of Climb. She is also known as the Golden Princess for being a reformer who brought major changes within the kingdom such as the ban on slavery. She is the youngest daughter of King Lanposa III and the younger sister of Barbro and Zanac.\n\nRenner is described as a young girl with long golden hair, silky smooth and supple as it drapes over the back of her neck. She has vibrant, dark blue eyes that shine like sapphires filled with warmth. She wears a fashionable white dress which further strengthens her image of purity. Around her neck hangs a golden necklace, appearing to symbolize her noble soul.\n\nRenner is known publicly as the Golden Princess for her benevolence and kindness. While she is believed to be a saint, in reality she has a psychopathic personality and doesn\'t care about the feelings of others. The only exception to this is her childhood friend, Climb. If Climb was wounded, she would declare that anyone involved would be ruthlessly killed.','2020-10-19 11:30:52','2020-10-19 11:30:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n127241-jDj7iccxQGdT.jpg','MC'),(1662,'Shasuryu Shasha','Shasuryu Shasha is the leader of the lizardmen\'s tribes and chieftain of the Green Claw Tribe. His younger brother is Zaryusu. He is a skilled warrior in addition to a proficient druid, which allows him to complement his weapon attacks with magic. Unlike other lizardmen who have bone weapons, his sword is forged of pure steel.\n\nIncredibly huge in stature, he has dark green and charcoal black scales, a trait which he shares with his younger brother. Numerous scars are present all over his body, the most prominent of which is an old, long white scar, which stands out amongst his dark-colored scales.\n\nShasuryu follows his ancestors traditions, but he is also not blinded by them and is one of the more practical minded lizardmen, as evidenced by the decision to support his brother\'s innovative idea, which led to the creation of the fishery farms near the Green Tribe village.\n\n~!Shasuryu Shasha led the chieftains, save Crusch Lulu, and a band of the strongest warriors of the Lizardmen Alliance in the duel against Cocytus. The majority of the warriors perished in one fell swoop due to Cocytus\'s freezing ability, and only the chieftains remained. Ultimately, Shasuryu and Zaryusu were last lizardmen to be left standing. He sacrificed his life in order to create an opening for his brother to attack Cocytus. Unfortunately, his brother was unable to cause damage, and was also slain shortly. However, their acts and sacrifices in battle were not meaningless, since they earned Cocytus\' respect, which later influenced Ainz\'s decision to resurrect them.\nAfter Zaryusu was resurrected by Ainz\'s magic, the lizardman petitioned his brother and Zenberu be resurrected. Ainz replied he would consider his request, which he later granted.!~','2020-10-19 11:30:52','2020-10-19 11:30:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/127432-i76rwiFQWiO5.jpg','MC'),(1663,'Gagaran','She is an adamantite ranked adventurer and a warrior from Blue Rose','2020-10-19 11:30:53','2020-10-19 11:30:53','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n127669-8nYP4EnGbCTD.jpg','MC'),(1664,'Tina','Tina is an adamantite ranked adventurer and a member of Blue Rose. She is the twin sister of Tia.','2020-10-19 11:30:53','2020-10-19 11:30:53','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n127670-5YG4iz8L8TSS.jpg','MC'),(1665,'Tuareninya Veyron','~!Tuareninya is the Head Maid Candidate of E-Rantel and the older sister of Ninya. She is under the protection of Ainz Ooal Gown after Sebas Tian saved her from the brothel in the Royal Capital.!~\n\n(Source: Overlord Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:54','2020-10-19 11:30:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128267-O0y4t2aXmhO1.jpg','MC'),(1666,'Climb','The Personal Bodyguard of Princess Renner. She saved him when he was just a street urchin about to die from sickness. As such, he views his services to her as a fulfilling of that debt he owes and is even willing to give up his life for her. However, he remains unaware of Renner\'s true nature. He is rather disliked due to him having such a position despite not even being a commoner, but an urchin. Despite this position, he holds no talent at fighting, making up for it with sheer effort. He eventually meets Sebas and, after convincing him to teach him some of his skills, they become friends, though he remains unaware of his loyalty towards Ainz. He also has a close friendship with Gazef and Brain as well as several members of Blue Rose.<br></br>(Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:30:54','2020-10-19 11:30:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128287-MBxEj9BMQKpJ.jpg','MC'),(1667,'Brain Unglaus','Brain is a warrior turned mercenary after he lost to Gazef Stronoff in a grand tournament to determine the strongest fighter in Re-Estize Kingdom. He has brown eyes with blue hair and the appearance of a wild beast. He is equipped with a chainmail and wears a necklace and ring which are infused with protection magic. His whole body is lean and his muscles are tough as steel and tempered through experience.\n\nOriginally a farmer, he was gifted with what could only be described as a God-given talent in the mastery of the sword. He has always believed himself to be the strongest fighter inside the Kingdom, having never lost a fight before he entered the grand tournament to decide the King\'s guard captain. He easily fought his way to the final where he faced off against Gazef Stronoff. A grand and close battle ensued between the two, but eventually, he would taste his first defeat at the hand of Gazef.\n\nHis fame was shattered and his confidence as an unbeatable warrior took a hit. He then decided to do everything he could to become stronger, so he would truly become unbeatable. At the same time, in order to make a living he started working as a mercenary for the Death Spreading Brigade. \n\n\n~!When first introduced he is very arrogant, thinking that he is the most powerful, even though he earlier lost to Gazef. While a mercenary, he suffered a devastating defeat at the hand of Shalltear Bloodfallen when she attacked the hideout of the Death Spreading Brigade. After that, his personality changes drastically. Having his confidence completely crushed and getting a feel of what true terror is like, his attitude changes to one where he is completely depressed, hinting at a suicidal tendency.\n\nHe eventually does a complete overhaul after meeting Climb and Sebas Tian. He changes to a much friendlier person that starts to think that strength is more than simply being skilled with a sword.\n\nIn his second encounter with Shalltear, he managed to chip off Shalltear\'s pinky fingernail using Fourfold Slash of Light.\n\nIn the web novel version, he becomes a vampire under Shalltear.!~\n\n(Source: Overlord Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:30:54','2020-10-19 11:30:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128263-KwhoIxlYfLET.jpg','SC'),(1668,'Luvellia Sanctus','','2020-10-19 11:30:54','2020-10-19 11:30:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b164447-VRYIQ3kTi2UJ.png','MC'),(1669,'Peter Grill','','2020-10-19 11:30:54','2020-10-19 11:30:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b164448-9ykwj2VxZbNt.png','MC'),(1670,'Lisa Alpacas','','2020-10-19 11:30:55','2020-10-19 11:30:55','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b164452-P1A0bR0RiNIE.png','SC'),(1671,'John Goodman','The [Guildmaster\'s](https://anilist.co/character/184904) assistant.','2020-10-19 11:30:55','2020-10-19 11:30:55','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184902-LXn5mjBKDRrq.png','MC'),(1672,'Mimi Alpacas','','2020-10-19 11:30:55','2020-10-19 11:30:55','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b164451-l4upvXktf6dz.png','MC'),(1673,'Albatross Sanctus','[Luvellia\'s](https://anilist.co/character/164447) father and guild master.','2020-10-19 11:30:55','2020-10-19 11:30:55','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184904-qHXZD6Z82J6l.png','SC'),(1674,'Vegan Eldoriel','','2020-10-19 11:30:55','2020-10-19 11:30:55','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b164450-VOdbFDNDMNPg.png','SC'),(1675,'Piglette Pancetta','','2020-10-19 11:30:55','2020-10-19 11:30:55','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b164449-nJvtX30daiKA.png','MC'),(1676,'Worm Goblin','','2020-10-19 11:30:56','2020-10-19 11:30:56','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184908-7BCAFOdwl1Io.png','MC'),(1677,'Tim Robinson','','2020-10-19 11:30:56','2020-10-19 11:30:56','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184903-iPKe9WMN3IyQ.png','M