s critical condition at the start of a tournament, and took upon themselves some of the blame for pressuring Jichir into becoming mentally trapped in the creation of his dishes. Feeling Jichir\'s talent was beyond the tasks of the academy, Senzaemon freed his former student to travel abroad and learn independently, a proposal Jichir happily accepted, as well as Gin whom Senzaemon offered him as the head of resort planner as a mean to atone their sins to ensurr no one wil share a similar fate as what happened to Joichiro before. For a period thereafter, Senzaemon hired Jichir as his private chef.!~\n\n~!Six years ago, Senzaemon exiled his son-in-law, Azami, for abusing Erina with brainwashing, and turns out even worst and dangerous to rule the academy than Joichiro\'s previous ill-fate. Senzaemon became Erina\'s legal guardian and had Azami\'s name struck from the Ttsuki records. However, in the year Erina enrolls in the academy, Azami returns and a majority of the Elite Ten vote to support Azami as headmaster, replacing Senzaemon. In the aftermath, Senzaemon revealed to Sma that he advised Jichir to have him apply to the academy. Senzaemon remains active behind-the-scenes with Jichir, working through tips from informants to wrest control from Azami.!~\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:33:47','2020-10-19 11:33:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/76028-YhCTXMKjPc6I.png','SC'),(2148,'Souma Yukihira','He is the son of Jouichirou Yukihira and, until it closed, worked at his father\'s restaurant, Restaurant Yukihira. As one of the main protagonist in the manga, Soma fight his odds in the elite school to becoming the best chef in the world even with strong background discrimination of his academy. He is currently a student at Tootsuki Culinary Academy and a resident of Polar Star Dormitory.   Souma is a rather energetic child who has the constant drive to move forward with his cooking, mostly due to his rivalry with his father. Due to his drive 