obayashi','She is a 90th Generation student of Tootsuki Culinary Academy and a 2nd seat of the Elite Ten Council.\n\nShe has long flowing scarlet hair that reaches down to her shoulder blades with her bangs covering her left eye. She has a lot of cat-like features, having yellow eyes with vertically slitted pupils and pronounced, cat-like teeth. She is the tallest female Elite Ten Council member.','2020-10-19 11:34:02','2020-10-19 11:34:02','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b89066-zRPZRDvbY9jD.png','SC'),(2194,'Anne','Anne (, An) is a first class bookman for the WGO and was selected to be as an impartial judge for the Rgiment de Cuisine between Central and the rebels.','2020-10-19 11:34:02','2020-10-19 11:34:02','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/126812-CGmdt32WSDsq.jpg','SC'),(2195,'Ryouko Sakaki','Ryko is a tall, mature-looking girl with long purple hair, orange eyes, and a large bust. She is gentle and kind, responding to the eccentrics of the other Polar Star residents in a level-headed manner and comforting the other students when they are troubled. Ryko\'s specialty is fermented foods due to her parents owning a well-known fermented-goods shop, and she maintains a workshop near the dorms to produce her own ingredients. She also keeps a bottle of \"fermented rice drink\" that she would sometimes bring out during parties and celebrations, which Sma suspects is illegally brewed sake.\n\n~!During the Autumn Elections, she presented a \"curry soy-natto rice\" using charcoal-fermented natto and homemade rice-sauce fermented with koji. The dish garnered praise from the judges, who suddenly felt as if they were in a festival due to the quintessentially Japanese and festive taste of the dish. She ultimately took 7th place in her block.!~\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:34:02','2020-10-19 11:34:02','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/85727.jpg','MC'),(2196,'Azami Nakiri','Father of Erina Nakiri and head 