n Lord currently. He is also a partner and best friend of True Dragon Veldora Tempest.!~ ~!Upon becoming a True Demon Lord and evolving his race from Slime to Demon Slime, Rimuru has been depicted wearing a black overcoat. His nails also appear sharper and his overall human form appears slightly older.!~\n\n(Source: Tensura Wiki, Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:34:50','2020-10-19 11:34:50','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b123962-SL05nQDJWB9P.png','MC'),(2336,'Daikenja','Unique Skill Great Sage , Daikenja is one of the first two Unique Skills (the other being Predator) that Rimuru Tempest (Satoru Mikami) had on being born into his new world. It had evolved from Unique Skill Sage during his death, as he thought since he was approaching his forties as a virgin, he must be something much greater than a mere wizard. \n\n~!During Rimuru\'s evolution into Demon Lord this Unique Skill evolved into the Ultimate Skill: Wisdom King Raphael.!~','2020-10-19 11:34:50','2020-10-19 11:34:50','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n129347-CWRPpxlFDh1b.jpg','SC'),(2337,'Shuna','Shuna (, lit. \"Vermilion Vegetable\") is a Fair Oni and one of the greatest admirers of her master, Rimuru Tempest.\nBefore serving under Rimuru, she was the princess of the Ogre Tribe.\n\n(Source: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Fandom)','2020-10-19 11:34:50','2020-10-19 11:34:50','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b128040-nwAfxMBj2BPF.jpg','SC'),(2338,'Kaijin','Kaijin was a blacksmith of the Dwarven Kingdom, and the brother of Kaidou. After he was exiled from his own country, he became Rimuru Tempest\'s subordinate, and helped build the Monster City \"Tempest\", he acted as a builder, blacksmith, and craftsmen. He also was the former commander of the Dwargon Engineering Corps.\n\n(Source: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:34:50','2020-10-19 11:34:50','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b1299