 ','2020-10-19 11:34:57','2020-10-19 11:34:57','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b129349-lneC6Glj2bps.jpg','MC'),(2372,'Kaval','Kaval is the leader of his adventure\'s party, where he serves as the \'fighter\' role. ~!Alongside Gido, he is also tasked as the secret bodyguard of Lady Elyune under the guise of an adventurer.!~\n\n(Source: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:34:57','2020-10-19 11:34:57','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b129918-Srq5hldfOKBm.jpg','MC'),(2373,'Bester','Bester ( Besut) is a former minister of Dwargon and is currently the lead researcher of Tempest.\n~!After joining Tempest he has become more reliable. He got rid of that sharp personality and mellowed out.!~','2020-10-19 11:34:57','2020-10-19 11:34:57','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b132364-7siTngt0w7xv.jpg','MC'),(2374,'Dord','Dord, the middle brother of Garm and Mild. He is known for his first-rate craftsmanship. Dord focuses more on dyes and high class attire.\n\n(Source: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:34:58','2020-10-19 11:34:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n129917-3UC194PSkLFQ.jpg','SC'),(2375,'Veldora Tempest','\"Storm Dragon\" Veldora Tempest  , \"Boufuu Ryuu\" Verudora Tenpesuto is the youngest of the four strongest dragons (True Dragons). He is connected with Rimuru by an agreement and was known to rampage here and there. He was the one to name Rimuru and Rimuru gave him his last name, since they share the same last name, Rimuru could technically be classifed as Veldora\'s adoptive brother.','2020-10-19 11:34:58','2020-10-19 11:34:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b128034-1FPe5zSuuMAz.jpg','MC'),(2376,'Myrd','Myrd is younger brother of Garm and Dord. Though he was a dwarf of few words, he was an expert at what he does. Having knowledge in construction, and well-versed in the arts, he is a one of a kind genius. Myrd was appointed as the captain of the construction team.\n\n(Source: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:34:58','2020-10-19 11:34:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n129914-30U7I3xGmL3q.jpg','SC'),(2377,'Alice Rondo','One of the children who were incompletely summoned. At 9 years old, Alice is the youngest of the group, and she\'s also a bit of a tomboy.','2020-10-19 11:34:58','2020-10-19 11:34:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b132746-BzAOW92pBsvM.jpg','MC'),(2378,'Garm','Garm, the elder brother of Doldo and Mild. He is a skilled blacksmith. Garm is in charge of everyday clothing and underwear. \n \n(Source: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:34:58','2020-10-19 11:34:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n129923-om5JwjVx2Pw7.jpg','SC'),(2379,'Shizue Izawa','Shizue Izawa was the companion of the previous Hero and a Japanese Summoned One. She is also known as the \"Explosive Monarch\", an A ranked Adventurer of the Freedom Association\'s Headquarters, and the formal homeroom teacher of the Freedom Academy\'s S Class students.\n\nShe was also the mentor of several excellent pupils whom became important figures of society.\n\n(Source: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Fandom)','2020-10-19 11:34:58','2020-10-19 11:34:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b128037-fJYYmpeJjrN6.jpg','MC'),(2380,'Garde-Myourmiles','An influential merchant from the kingdom of Burumund. Myorumairu is both the chairman of the Burumund shopping district and also a loan shark.','2020-10-19 11:34:59','2020-10-19 11:34:59','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b132749-lb37TWQ6iY6A.jpg','SC'),(2381,'Pikary','A Kiralian rocket man.','2020-10-19 11:35:01','2020-10-19 11:35:01','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/13685.jpg','SC'),(2382,'Haruna Sairenji','__Birthday:__ March 6\n__Age__: 15\n__Height:__ 160 cm\n__Weight:__ 50 kg \n__BWH:__ 79-56-82 cm \n\nHaruna Sairenji is the second female protagonist of To Love Ru and one of Rito\'s classmates and the girl of his affections. Haruna has similar feelings for him, having been attracted to his kind, gentle nature since junior high. Despite her growing love for Rito, which she believes to be unrequited, she usually suppresses her feelings and cannot confess to him because of her friendship with Lala who also loves Rito. However, with some encouragement, she tells Lala of her ordeal, to which Lala accepts, claiming Haruna as her rival for Rito\'s heart, while remaining friends. She lives with her older sister Akiho Sairenji in an apartment and has a severe fear of ghosts and the supernatural, the exception being Oshizu Murasame but only to an extent.\n\nWhen frightened, she has a habit of grabbing the nearest thing around her  typically Rito  and swinging him wildly, in an attempt to get rid of whatever frightens her. There is also a running gag to where Rito is about to confess to her, only for something (or someone) to come between it. She lives with her older sister in an apartment.\n\nA highly responsible person, Haruna\'s personality can sway her classmates\' hearts to vote for her as their class representative, even when she did not run to be a candidate. She is affiliated with the tennis club and a southpaw.\n\n(Source: To LOVE-Ru Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:35:01','2020-10-19 11:35:01','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b5512-1wPXDnrqMBsd.png','SC'),(2383,'Mikan Yuuki','Birthday: November 3rd\nHeight: 149 cm \nWeight: 41 kg \n3 sizes: 70 - 52 - 73 cm  \n\nRito\'s independent and reliable 11-year-old sister, Mikan takes care of the housework while their parents are away on business. In contrast to her brother, she is very mature and does not hesitate to tease him, going as far as stating they aren\'t blood related, just for a laugh. Mikan also seems to have a certain lack of respect for Rito because of this (she hardly ever addresses him by his honorific as an older brother), but does answer him \"Onii-chan\" as thanks for trying so hard to take care of her when she develops a fever. Mikan may not show it, but she cares very deeply for Rito and misses his company, and states how they used to play together before Lala entered their lives.  Mikan grows quite attached to Golden Darkness, perhaps due to Darkness seemingly being the same age as her. Mikan is very perceptive and seems to be able to read people\'s emotions, even their reactions, most of which is Rito\'s obvious anxiety around Haruna and Yui\'s more than subtle feelings for him (Mikan even calls him a \"playboy\" for attracting so many girls).   \n\n(Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:35:01','2020-10-19 11:35:01','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b7806-YLwD4rZyclb0.png','MC'),(2384,'Konjiki no Yami','__Birthday:__ December 24\n__Height:__ 153 cm\n__Weight:__ 45 kg \n__BWH:__ 75-52-77 cm  \n__Likes:__ Taiyaki\n__Dislikes:__ Perverts\n\nA dispassionate, withdrawn assassin, Golden Darkness is hired by one of Lala\'s arranged suitors, Lacospo to kill Rito, until she breaks the contract, noting the true nature behind her target. Golden Darkness is currently staying on Earth, roaming around the city streets and Sainan High, with a motivation to continue her duty to assassinate Rito, although she has yet to accomplish this (hinting she only said this as an excuse to stay on Earth, which is then confirmed). Commonly referred as \"Yami-chan\", she spends her time reading books and magazines, while eating taiyaki (it is the only thing she eats on Earth since it is the first food offered by Rito, prior to spending a night at the Yuuki residence for a sukiyaki dinner). By her planet\'s calculations, she is 24 years-old, despite having the appearance of an 11-year-old (albeit a rather mature one), although this is only mentioned in the anime and has a weakness towards anything slimy.\n\nLike Lala, Golden Darkness\' physical abilities are exponentially stronger than a human\'s. She carries a unique ability to turn her body parts into various objects through use of nano machines circulating her body, ranging from swords to dragon heads. Unfortunately, excessive use becomes a hazard to her health. She states she hates \"ecchi\" people, and does not hesitate to assault a person who looks at her in an obscene way, even if it\'s her own fault like when she was using her abilities to increase her bust she attacks Rito when he saw her, mostly out of embarrassment or for many occasions standing at the top of something such as stairs where her panties could be seen by accident. She has also stated, that she doesn\'t understand if she can feel love and all its wonders, though she slowly becomes closer to Rito once seeing that he is a good person.\n\n~!In Chapter 149, it is revealed that her creator is named Doctor Tearju (later revealed as Tearju Lunatique) and her given name is Eve, revealed in Darkness Chapter 14. When she was under Tearju\'s care, she was bright and cheerful, until Tearju was forced to escape from the organization that created Eve. This left her under the care of the evil scientists who raised her to be a cold assassin.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:01','2020-10-19 11:35:01','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b5513-wcyEEjTlZtOB.png','MC'),(2385,'Shizu Murasame','Height: 159 cm Weight: 49 kg 3-sizes: 82-56-81 cm  The ghost of a girl who died in the old abandoned school building 400 years ago, Shizu is sincere, kind, and very curious about the modern world, but has a severe fear of dogs, likened to Haruna\'s level of fear to the supernatural. She is usually addressed as \"Oshizu\" (?); the O (?) is an honorific used to refer to women. When frightened, she can emit blasts of mental stress, blowing apart various objects and surroundings, but is also capable of manipulating others through sheer willpower. A related gag is the blasts of stress frequently rip apart clothing, resulting in Rito being in an awkward situation with one of the female cast. Since her meeting with Rito and the others, she begins exploring the world outside the old school building. Oshizu is aware of Haruna\'s crush on Rito by her ability to sense feelings while possessing another person and becomes very supportive towards cheering Haruna into confessing her feelings to him.  Oshizu \"returns\" to the living, after Ryouko creates a prosthetic body for her to inhabit, built with biological qualities (looking and feeling like an actual, human body). However, she occasionally \"disconnects\" during brief moments of excitement, her spirit leaving her prosthetic body. She currently works as a nurse for Ryouko, while Ryouko maintains Oshizu\'s physical body. In the first anime, Oshizu is not given a new body and her presence is limited, while she has her body as she does in the manga for the OVA releases and the new anime.  (Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:35:01','2020-10-19 11:35:01','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b14388-HNc1lZenz3rz.png','SC'),(2386,'Ryouko Mikado','Height: 171 cm Weight: 59 kg 3-sizes: 94-58-91 cm  The school doctor who also happens to be alien (she has pointed ears). She dresses rather provocatively even when on the job and helps out aliens on Earth in various manners, usually those dealing with medical care.','2020-10-19 11:35:02','2020-10-19 11:35:02','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/7808.jpg','MC'),(2387,'Taizou Motemitsu','A member of the baseball team.  He always acts suave, yet he is constantly rejected by women.','2020-10-19 11:35:02','2020-10-19 11:35:02','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/7754.jpg','SC'),(2388,'Kenichi Saruyama','Perverted male best friend of Rito. Later on falls in love with the female version of Rito called Riko.','2020-10-19 11:35:02','2020-10-19 11:35:02','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/7809.jpg','MC'),(2389,'Lacospo','One of Lala\'s arranged suitors, (his appearance reminiscent of Emperor Pilaf of the original Dragonball, perhaps a homage).  (Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:35:03','2020-10-19 11:35:03','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/71391.jpg','SC'),(2390,'Kyouko Kirisaki','Height: 162.5 cm Weight: 49 kg 3-sizes: 86/56/86 cm  A half-Earthling half-alien girl, Kyouko is a famous idol who the ability to create and throw fire at will and becomes a friend to Run when Run portrays an antagonist on her show. She is best known for her role as Magical Kyouko, a fictional magical girl character who stars in her own television serial Lala loves watching, often forcing Rito to watch it with her. She reappears again as Run askes Rito to be her date, however Kyouko is able to tell they aren\'t dating though wishes her luck on getting him. Ever since their first meeting on her show Run and her have done many projects together, one of which is debuting many songs together.  When Rito and his friends are subsequently given invitations to an RPG world Lala had partially created, an image of Kyouko is programmed into the game. However, Kyouko\'s programming within the game is modified by Nana and Momo, turning her into the \"Demon King\", tasked to seek out Rito and offer him a way to send him and his friends home if he left Lala and promises to be her boyfriend. Adding to Rito\'s anxiety, Demon King Kyouko threatens to destroy Rito and his friends if he does not state his feelings for Lala. In comedic fashion, the otherwise unbeatable Kyouko is destroyed by a watering can only Rito can use.  Like some To Love-Ru characters, Kyouko is a homage to Kyouko Kirisaki of Black Cat. Both characters also share the same voice actress in their respective drama CD/animated counterparts, even addressing herself as her Black Cat incarnation, along with fire manipulation. ','2020-10-19 11:35:03','2020-10-19 11:35:03','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b24803-FQjyfyAUYqX4.png','MC'),(2391,'Zastin','Lala\'s personal bodyguard and the best swordsman of the planet Deviluke. He is currently Assistant Chief to Rito\'s father who is a manga writer due to an incident caused by Lala. Despite his skill with a sword, he has a horrible sense of direction, resulting in him being constantly lost (another running gag in the series).  \n\nIn <i>To LOVE-Ru Darkness</i>, he now works as a mangaka.\n\n(Source Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:35:03','2020-10-19 11:35:03','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/5515.jpg','SC'),(2392,'Risa Momioka','Height: 167 cm Weight: 54.5 kg 3-sizes: 83-60-85 cm  Mischievous best friend of Haruna. Likes to play with Haruna and Mio. ','2020-10-19 11:35:03','2020-10-19 11:35:03','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b7810-b7MUxigjiYZA.png','SC'),(2393,'Lala Satalin Deviluke',' __Birthday:__ July 7\n__Age:__ 16\n__Height:__ 165 cm\n__Weight:__ 50.5 kg\n__BWH:__ 89-57-87 cm\n__Zodiac sign:__ Cancer\n\nPrincess of Deviluke. Ran away from home so she doesn\'t have to get married. Uses many self-made inventions. At first she was pretending to love Rito to keep from getting married, but eventually she fell in love with him. She has physical abilities far beyond that of a human and also has a distinctive tail coming from her back (which is very sensitive).\n\nBeing an alien, Lala has far more strength, power and speed than the average human. Her physical strength (without any inventions or powers) surpasses any human on Earth, and maybe even some aliens in the solar system. She has also shown slight durability even with her own tongue, like when she ate one of Run\'s really spiced sandwiches and it didn\'t even phase her.\n\nShe can fire laser beams from her tail. However, her tail is both her weapon and her weakness. On Planet Deviluke, females\' tails are far more sensitive than males\'. When someone touches Lala\'s tail, she becomes weak and seems to lose her strength, though she can shake anyone off of her tail with her astonishing strength.\n\nPerhaps Lala\'s most distinguishing ability is being an extraodinary inventor. She is considered a genius and has made many inventions. However, Lala very much has the personality of both a perky child and an absent-minded scientist, resulting in all of her inventions being very toy-like, troublesome, and serving no important purpose besides fun, mischief, and unintentional fanservice. A running gag in the plot is that her inventions usually do not work as well as Lala and the others had hoped, often resulting into a perverted accident.\n\n(Source: To LOVE-Ru Wika)','2020-10-19 11:35:03','2020-10-19 11:35:03','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b5511-fz4zDPM0gBSQ.png','MC');
INSERT INTO `characters` VALUES (2394,'Ren Elsie Jewelria','Ren Elise Jewelria is an childhood friend of Lala and the boy version of Run Elise Jewelria. As Ren and Run are royalty from planet Memorze, they can change gender in mind and body upon triggering a specific stimulus. In their case, a sneeze. Ren likes Lala, while Run likes Rito. Ren hates Rito because Lala likes him, while Run hates Lala because Rito likes her. ','2020-10-19 11:35:03','2020-10-19 11:35:03','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/74075.jpg','SC'),(2395,'Rin Kujou','Height: 167.5 cm Weight: 54 kg 3-sizes: 86 - 61 - 86 cm  Saki\'s loyal and assisting friends, Rin is skilled in the kendo arts and has been a loyal bodyguard of Saki for years, as her family has always served the Tenjouin in this position. The bespectacled Aya is weak-willed and became associated with Saki after she and Rin protected her from bullies when they were children.   (Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:35:04','2020-10-19 11:35:04','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/21694.jpg','MC'),(2396,'Akiho Sairenji','Haruna\'s older sister, she shares her apartment with Haruna. Extremely popular with the guys (having received confessions from two men at the same time), Akiho continuously turns them down, as her sister states she is not looking for love at the moment. However, she is currently dating Yuu Kotegawa.   (Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:35:04','2020-10-19 11:35:04','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/24414.jpg','SC'),(2397,'Run Elsie Jewelria','__Height:__ 158 cm\n__Weight:__ 49 kg\n__BWH:__ 83-56-83 cm\n\nA childhood friend of Lala, infamously known for wearing girl clothing during his play dates with Lala. At first he arrives on Earth to win back Lala, but soon becomes jealous due to her relationship with Rito. As Ren is from Planet Memorze, he can change gender in both mind and body upon sneezing; as a girl she goes by the name Run. Run likes Rito, while Ren is in competition (albeit rather one sided) with Rito for Lala\'s hand in marriage.\n\n~!In <i>To LOVE-Ru Darkness</i>, Run and Ren are finally separated from each other. It\'s also revealed that Memorzians is separating while reaching adulthood.!~\n\n(Source: Wikipedia) ','2020-10-19 11:35:04','2020-10-19 11:35:04','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b5516-QhH9yj22Mzj3.png','SC'),(2398,'Principal','The unnamed principal of Sainan High is well-known throughout campus as a pervert.  He will impulsively enroll girls into the school body, so as to ogle and grope them without hindrance, though this is not restricted to Sainan High, but also occurs in public, as well.','2020-10-19 11:35:04','2020-10-19 11:35:04','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/18835.jpg','MC'),(2399,'Saki Tenjouin','Height: 165 cm Weight: 50 kg 3-sizes: 84 - 56 - 86 cm  The arrogant queen bee of the school, she consistently tries to one-up Lala only to get herself further embarrassed. Eventually she gains a crush on Zastin only to be horrified at the thought that he is in service to Lala, this however has made her very determined to win his heart at any cost.  ','2020-10-19 11:35:04','2020-10-19 11:35:04','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/10395.jpg','MC'),(2400,'Honekawa','The homeroom teacher of Rito\'s class.','2020-10-19 11:35:04','2020-10-19 11:35:04','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/37919.jpg','MC'),(2401,'Yui Kotegawa','__Age:__ 16\n__Birthday:__ May 3 \n__Height:__ 162 cm \n__Weight:__ 51 kg \n__BWH:__ 88-59-87 cm\n\nYui is a girl in Rito\'s class who seems a good deal more conservative than the others (except in the anime, where she\'s downright being portrayed as a school nazi, ruling the hallways with an iron fist), which is partially caused by her prettyboy brother and his habit of going out with different girls on a regular basis. She quickly comes at odds with Lala and her free-spirited personality, which she sees as a hindrance towards making the school a more peaceful and better place.\n\n~!She admits to herself that she is in love with Rito in <i>To LOVE-Ru Darkness</i>.!~ \n\n ~!Throughout the series, Yui\'s love intrest has developed. Originally thinking he was just a \"Shameless,\" boy, she realized how she was wrong after seeing Rito\'s kindness around town. Later at a group picnic, Yui told Rito that she state that \"I won\'t let you do shameless things with anyone else but me!!\" However this was because she was under the influence of pollen that caused all the girl\'s to fall in love with Rito. Yui also made chocolate for Valentines Day, even though she claimed to him it was just \"Giri (Obligatory) Chocolate,\" but really it was only for him.\n\nIn <i>To LOVE-Ru Darkness</i>, while Momo is trying to further her Harem Plan, in which Rito will marry all of the women who love him, she influences the weather when Rito and Yui are walking home so that they go to Rito\'s house for shelter. While there Yui starts to confess to Rito, stating how it is normal for boys to do \"shameless things,\" and nearly comes close to kissing him, but she backed out. Yui announced her love for Rito, albeit only to herself, she finally came to terms with it.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:05','2020-10-19 11:35:05','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b9530-MY4D9opZHhKh.png','SC'),(2402,'Mio Sawada','Height: 155 cm Weight: 45 kg 3-sizes: 74 - 56 - 76 cm  Mischievous best friend of Haruna. Teams up with Risa to grope breasts, especially Haruna and Lala\'s.','2020-10-19 11:35:05','2020-10-19 11:35:05','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/10396.jpg','SC'),(2403,'Rito Yuuki',' __Birthday:__ October 16\n__Age:__ 16 \n__Height:__ 164.5 cm\n__Weight:__ 62 kg\n\nRito Yuuki is the main male protagonist of To Love-Ru. He is a normal brown haired 16 year old student of Sainan High, and he has a big crush on Haruna Sairenji. He attempted numerous times to confess to her but has met with failure each time. Rito used to be on the soccer team in junior high and was quite good, but quit because he was constantly helping his father with his mangaka duties, thus did not want to leave his little sister Mikan Yuuki alone in the house. Mikan comments he is very good at the most \"useless little things\", like crane and festival games (e.g. hoops, catching fish, squirt guns). Along with the numerous useless little things Rito is good at, he is also an accomplished florist, gardener, and horticulturalist.\n\nRito\'s nature is borderline clumsy, where he always ends up ogling or groping the many girls in the series (though mostly unintentionally). It is only by accident that he encounters and despite his enduring feelings for Haruna, Rito shows signs of developing deeper affection towards Lala a troublesome character that at first pretends to show affectionate feelings for Rito Yuki through the beggining of the story. As the story progresses he starts to show affection for Lala but is unsure if what he feels is actually love. This is shown again when he couldn\'t help but think about Lala even though he was with a naked Haruna. It is recently revealed that he is in love with Lala, but he is also in love with Haruna. At the end of the series, he confesses to Lala, but tells her he also loves Haruna, yet she is happy on both parts. He is confused as polygamy is illegal in Japan where Lala replied that once he is king of the universe the laws of earth no longer apply and forces him to go tell Haruna (strapping a jet pack to his back). Right before he was about to tell her, she moves out of the way, just like when he confessed to her very early in the series, leading him to state \"I love you\" to all of the female cast with the exception of Momo, Mikan, Golden Darkness, and Haruna herself. The ending implies that his \"love\" troubles will continue on into the future.\n\n~! __Riko\'s sizes:__\n __Height:__ 163 cm \n__Weight:__ 52.5 kg \n__BWH:__ 85-55.5-84 cm \n\nRiko is Rito\'s female alter-ego, she is a beautiful girl (with a physical appearance resembling a tomboy) who gets much attention from men, such as Taizou Motemitsu, the principal and even Kenichi Saruyama, Rito\'s best friend. Later, Saruyama falls in love with \"Riko-chan\" and asks Lala to invite her for a date; out of pity, she forcefully changes Rito into \"Riko\" so Saruyama can go on a date with Riko. After that Riko only appears for short amount of times at rare occasions.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:06','2020-10-19 11:35:06','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/5510.jpg','MC'),(2404,'Peke','A talking robot made by Lala as a clothing robot. He can change his shape into clothes pre-set by Lala. He can also copy any kind of clothing after seeing them. He needs to recharge every night or else he will lose power and Lala will end up being naked. ','2020-10-19 11:35:07','2020-10-19 11:35:07','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/7807.jpg','MC'),(2405,'Aya Fujisaki','__Height:__ 157 cm\n__Weight:__ 47 kg\n__BWH:__ 81-54-81 cm\n\nThe bespectacled Aya is weak-willed and became associated with Saki after she and Rin protected her from bullies when they were kids.','2020-10-19 11:35:07','2020-10-19 11:35:07','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/24804.jpg','SC'),(2406,'Mea Kurosaki','__Birthday:__ November 1\n__Height:__ 153 cm\n__Weight:__ 44 kg\n__BWH:__ 75-52-77 cm\n\nMea Kurosaki is a character from To-Love-Ru Darkness. She is sent to Earth to bring back the \"old\" Golden Darkness. It is revealed that she is Yami\'s younger sister as she was created by the same organization as her. At first she is found alone starring out the window until she meets Nana and becomes friends with her. She now views others as friends. It appears (in chapter 7) that she has sexual feelings towards Rito.\n\nShe is described by Yami as a \"second generation\" transforming weapon, making her abilities more advanced than her 