 Lala\'s arranged suitors, Lacospo to kill Rito, until she breaks the contract, noting the true nature behind her target. Golden Darkness is currently staying on Earth, roaming around the city streets and Sainan High, with a motivation to continue her duty to assassinate Rito, although she has yet to accomplish this (hinting she only said this as an excuse to stay on Earth, which is then confirmed). Commonly referred as \"Yami-chan\", she spends her time reading books and magazines, while eating taiyaki (it is the only thing she eats on Earth since it is the first food offered by Rito, prior to spending a night at the Yuuki residence for a sukiyaki dinner). By her planet\'s calculations, she is 24 years-old, despite having the appearance of an 11-year-old (albeit a rather mature one), although this is only mentioned in the anime and has a weakness towards anything slimy.\n\nLike Lala, Golden Darkness\' physical abilities are exponentially stronger than a human\'s. She carries a unique ability to turn her body parts into various objects through use of nano machines circulating her body, ranging from swords to dragon heads. Unfortunately, excessive use becomes a hazard to her health. She states she hates \"ecchi\" people, and does not hesitate to assault a person who looks at her in an obscene way, even if it\'s her own fault like when she was using her abilities to increase her bust she attacks Rito when he saw her, mostly out of embarrassment or for many occasions standing at the top of something such as stairs where her panties could be seen by accident. She has also stated, that she doesn\'t understand if she can feel love and all its wonders, though she slowly becomes closer to Rito once seeing that he is a good person.\n\n~!In Chapter 149, it is revealed that her creator is named Doctor Tearju (later revealed as Tearju Lunatique) and her given name is Eve, revealed in Darkness Chapter 14. When she was under Tearju\'s care, she was bright and cheerful, until Tearju was forced to escape from the organization that created Eve. This left her under the care of the evil scientists who raised her to be a cold assassin.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:09','2020-10-19 11:35:09','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b5513-wcyEEjTlZtOB.png','SC'),(2408,'Nemesis','Nemesis is a sadistic, demanding girl who is responsible in giving orders to Mea. She uses Mea as her spy to look after Yami\'s changes and recent life. In addition, Nemesis is the one behind the plans to make Yami return to her emotionless-assassin\'s life again. Claiming that she knows that one day, Yami will return to her real path naturally, she decided to live in the human world and tries to be friends with everyone; in refusal of Momo and Rito. Like the other girls, she also seems to have sexual feelings towards Rito and plans to train him as her \'pet\'.  (Source: To LOVE-Ru Wikia)','2020-10-19 11:35:09','2020-10-19 11:35:09','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b41370-e1LgczRRdiCZ.png','SC'),(2409,'Ren Elsie Jewelria','Ren Elise Jewelria is an childhood friend of Lala and the boy version of Run Elise Jewelria. As Ren and Run are royalty from planet Memorze, they can change gender in mind and body upon triggering a specific stimulus. In their case, a sneeze. Ren likes Lala, while Run likes Rito. Ren hates Rito because Lala likes him, while Run hates Lala because Rito likes her. ','2020-10-19 11:35:10','2020-10-19 11:35:10','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/74075.jpg','MC'),(2410,'Risa Momioka','Height: 167 cm Weight: 54.5 kg 3-sizes: 83-60-85 cm  Mischievous best friend of Haruna. Likes to play with Haruna and Mio. ','2020-10-19 11:35:10','2020-10-19 11:35:10','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b7810-b7MUxigjiYZA.png','SC'),(2411,'Nana Astar Deviluke','Age: 14 Height: 150 cm Weight: 43 kg 3-sizes: 69 - 53 - 76 cm  One of Lala\'s younger sisters, she is also the elder twin sister of Momo. Nana only appear