),(2490,'Kazuya Kagami','Kazuya Kagami is the son of Kanaka and Kazuaki Kagami and younger brother of Kasumi. Partnering with Kiriha, the tsukumogami of his mother\'s kimono obi, he works as Kamioka\'s exorcist. His sister refers to him under the petname Yakkun.','2020-10-19 11:35:38','2020-10-19 11:35:38','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b126356-B43iy8UOEPUG.png','MC'),(2491,'Kanaka Kagami','','2020-10-19 11:35:38','2020-10-19 11:35:38','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128859-begd6sEB4sRA.png','MC'),(2492,'Chisato Chikaishi','Chisato Chikaishi is a childhood friend and classmate of Kazuya Kagami.','2020-10-19 11:35:39','2020-10-19 11:35:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b128858-Bos9Ht2GoluZ.png','MC'),(2493,'Kasumi Kagami','','2020-10-19 11:35:39','2020-10-19 11:35:39','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128860-b38XbQTxqTrW.png','MC'),(2494,'Shirou Shiramine','Perverted classmate of Kagami Kazuya.','2020-10-19 11:35:40','2020-10-19 11:35:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184214-Ceh7aCku43Qc.jpg','SC'),(2495,'Osamu Osanai','Studious friend of Kagami Kazuya.','2020-10-19 11:35:40','2020-10-19 11:35:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184215-KWVBGFtBa96j.jpg','MC'),(2496,'Kukuri','Kukuri-Hime-no-Kami, also known as Kukuri for short, is the resident God of the Land of the Hakusan Shrine. She guards over the Kamioka region and disperses the curse, assisting Kazuya in his job as an exorcist.','2020-10-19 11:35:40','2020-10-19 11:35:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b128857-AvfPROsTT9Ig.png','MC'),(2497,'Kotetsu','','2020-10-19 11:35:40','2020-10-19 11:35:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128863-4PrYBaTKATOM.png','SC'),(2498,'Hiroshi Ookado','','2020-10-19 11:35:40','2020-10-19 11:35:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b188388-y7mO8UUWlKR8.png','SC'),(2499,'Kokuyou','','2020-10-19 11:35:40','2020-10-19 11:35:40','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n128866-WjL9geTIOn4c.png','MC'),(2500,'Bjorn','Bjorn is [Askeladd](https://anilist.co/character/13020)\'s second in command, a burly man who fights for the love of combat. He is a berserker, able to enter powerful rages through the consumption of certain mushrooms.','2020-10-19 11:35:42','2020-10-19 11:35:42','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b19485-GqL2A0NKp3Tf.png','MC'),(2501,'Floki','A Jomsviking commander whom contracted [Askeladd](https://anilist.co/character/13020) to assassinate [Thors](https://anilist.co/character/13021), Floki\'s former comrade.\n','2020-10-19 11:35:43','2020-10-19 11:35:43','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/82537.jpg','SC'),(2502,'Thorkell','Thorkell is a Jomsviking general and brother of the Jomsviking Chief. A giant man who loves combat, Thorkell defected from the Danish army to become a mercenary for the English, believing that fighting his fellow Vikings will give him a better challenge. This same love of war leads him to support Prince [Canute](https://anilist.co/character/17438)\'s bid for kingship of the Danes. Before [Thors](https://anilist.co/character/13021)\' defection he works with and highly respects the man, and bears a fondness for his son [Thorfinn](https://anilist.co/character/10138) in the main plot. He duels twice with Thorfinn and dominates each time, though he loses two fingers in the first duel and an eye in the second. In battle, Thorkell typically wields a pair of axes as his primary weapons, but his greatest asset is probably his vast physical strength. During a skirmish with [Askeladd](https://anilist.co/character/13020)\'s band, he hurled a spear with such force that it skewered three men at once, despite having been thrown from several hundred feet away. Thorkell\'s character is based on Thorkell the Tall, a historical Jomsviking lord who is a mentor to Canute in the Flateyjarbk.   ~!Joined Canute as his servant after seeing him change in front of Askeladd and Thorfinn.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:43','2020-10-19 11:35:43','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b17440-XvYe5JY862ZT.png','MC'),(2503,'Atli','He is [Torgrim](https://anilist.co/character/141591)\'s younger brother.','2020-10-19 11:35:43','2020-10-19 11:35:43','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b141592-U2GLxZx8Nvto.png','SC'),(2504,'Ear','A member of [Askeladd](https://anilist.co/character/13020)\'s band whose remarkable hearing allows him estimate distance and marching speed of enemy troops just by pressing his ear to the ground. He needs complete silence to work, and snow dampens sound enough to severely limit this ability.','2020-10-19 11:35:43','2020-10-19 11:35:43','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b141593-iO0s9fTOHtmw.jpg','SC'),(2505,'Helga','She is the mother of [Thorfinn](https://anilist.co/character/10138) and [Ylva](https://anilist.co/character/27876), and the wife of [Thors](https://anilist.co/character/13021). ~!She\'s the daughter of the Jomsviking Chief.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:43','2020-10-19 11:35:43','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b141589-z9PsqosVAEpr.jpg','SC'),(2506,'Thors Snorresson','Height: 180cm (5\'11\")\n\nThors is the father of [Thorfinn](https://anilist.co/character/10138), a Jomsviking general whose phenomenal combat prowess earns him the epithet &quot;The Troll of Jom&quot;. Thors grows weary of battle after the birth of his children, fakes his own death, and retires to become a pacifist farmer. The Jomsvikings later discover that Thors is alive and force him to return to the battlefield. ~!Before he can arrive at the theater of war he is betrayed by a former comrade, [Floki](https://anilist.co/character/82537), who hires [Askeladd](https://anilist.co/character/13020) to assassinate him.!~ Thors is largely considered the greatest fighter to appear in the series, having defeated the likes of Askeladd and [Thorkell](https://anilist.co/character/17440) in single combat. Such was his strength that Floki was unwilling to engage him directly, even with an entire squadron of Jomsviking warriors. Unlike his son, Thors has no explicit or implied historical basis.','2020-10-19 11:35:43','2020-10-19 11:35:43','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b13021-lYBeamtBFvya.png','MC'),(2507,'Ragnar','He is the main adviser for Prince [Canute](https://anilist.co/character/17438), ~!all the way through to his death, Ragnar guarded, protected and talked for Canute!~. Ragnar is bald apart from very long, black, curly hair on the sides of his head. He has very thick black eyebrows that lie close to his deepset eyes. His wrinkles are also very deep, especially in his cheeks, just above his thick beard. He consciously keeps his face under control, even during the moment of death. However, when he gets angry, his entire frame shakes and he curls his fists up into balls.\n\n(Source: Vinland Saga Wiki)','2020-10-19 11:35:43','2020-10-19 11:35:43','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b82533-EN57FGoTIHn3.png','SC'),(2508,'Sweyn Forkbeard','','2020-10-19 11:35:44','2020-10-19 11:35:44','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b27957-1eAJeuybBavR.png','MC'),(2509,'Leif Erikson','An explorer who joins [Thorfinn](https://anilist.co/character/10138) in his quest to find paradise.','2020-10-19 11:35:44','2020-10-19 11:35:44','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b19486-XRzBNqoLb5Le.png','SC'),(2510,'Willibald','A 23-year-old Friar who travels with and mentors Prince [Canute](https://anilist.co/character/17438). He enjoys alcohol and is searching for true love.','2020-10-19 11:35:44','2020-10-19 11:35:44','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b20704-N5pntGOae3F4.jpg','SC'),(2511,'Halfdan','Halfdan is a wealthy and powerful landowner and moneylender known for his ruthlessness, earning the nickname \"Iron Chain\" for his skilled use of one as a weapon and symbol of his philosophy of chaining others.','2020-10-19 11:35:44','2020-10-19 11:35:44','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b140356-R5fxgrMKPOng.jpg','MC'),(2512,'Ylva','She is [Thorfinn](https://anilist.co/character/10138)\'s older sister. After Thorfinn has set on a journey to avenge his father, [Thors](https://anilist.co/character/13021), she takes care of household and [her mother](https://anilist.co/character/141589).','2020-10-19 11:35:45','2020-10-19 11:35:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b27876-YKfoiJg6kGee.jpg','MC'),(2513,'Hordaland ','','2020-10-19 11:35:45','2020-10-19 11:35:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b147777-ZPAMF8oz9Rmv.jpg','MC'),(2514,'Askeladd','Askeladd is the commander of a small but powerful Viking band, which owed its success to Askeladd\'s exceptional intelligence. Ten years before the main Vinland Saga storyline, Askeladd accepted a contract to assassinate [Thors](https://anilist.co/character/13021), father of [Thorfinn](https://anilist.co/character/10138). During the Viking invasion and war in England, he manipulated Thorfinn\'s desire for revenge against him as a way of keeping the gifted young fighter in his service. Askeladd is one of the most skilled fighters in the series, and is particularly adept at predicting his opponents\' moves in combat. Askeladd shares the name of Askeladden, a Norwegian folk character known for his cleverness.\n\n~!He is half-Danish and half-Welsh, being the son of a Welsh princess captured by a Viking raider. He believes in the legend of Avalon, which inspired him to support Prince [Canute](https://anilist.co/character/17438)\'s bid for kingship of the Danes and ultimately sacrifices himself assassinating King [Sweyn](https://anilist.co/character/27957) in order to install Canute as the Danish King and to ensure the safety of Wales from Denmark.!~\n\nVoiced by [Chiaki Kobayashi](https://anilist.co/staff/133507) during his adolescence phase and by [Maki Kawase](https://anilist.co/staff/127542) during his childhood phase in the anime.','2020-10-19 11:35:45','2020-10-19 11:35:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b13020-IH6JgWkNYItV.png','SC'),(2515,'Asgeir','','2020-10-19 11:35:45','2020-10-19 11:35:45','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b141590-4NuKDvd5B5ht.png','SC'),(2516,'Canute','Canute is a 17-year-old prince of the Danes. He is initially portrayed as timid and womanly, with a bishounen appearance and inability to function without his retainer [Ragnar](https://anilist.co/character/82533). These traits, along with his strong Christianity, earn him the mockery of the Vikings with whom he works. ~!After Ragnar\'s death, however, he has a sharp reversal of personality, becomes strong and kingly, and develops an ambition to create utopia on earth before God\'s return. Towards this end, he plots to overthrow his father [Sweyn Forkbeard](https://anilist.co/character/27957) and take the crown of the Danes. Canute is based on the historical King Canute the Great, the most prominent Danish ruler of England.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:46','2020-10-19 11:35:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b17438-7fxiIAHd6Omj.jpg','SC'),(2517,'Ake',' a member of Askeladd\'s band','2020-10-19 11:35:46','2020-10-19 11:35:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b156508-r7u8QLyKbr7B.jpg','SC'),(2518,'Thorfinn Karlsefni','Thorfinn is a courageous young man armed with two twin blades he inherited from his deceased [father](https://anilist.co/character/13021). He\'s traveling with [Askeladd](https://anilist.co/character/13020), who is the leader of a ruthless group of mercenaries who take jobs from whoever they think can offer them a reasonable reward. Besides, Askeladd is the man who killed Thorfinn\'s father, Thors, and the only reason Thorfinn is traveling with Askeladd is so he can defeat him in a duel and win back his father\'s pride. Thorfinn only wants to win his father\'s pride with a fair duel. Askeladd only agrees to these duels when Thorfinn completes a certain task (like bringing him the head of the opposing armies general on the battlefield).  He does not fight for the love of battle, but is still prone to losing his composure when in combat. This hotheadedness often costs him battles against more experienced opponents.\n\n~!After Askeladd is killed, Thorfinn entered a rage and tried to kill [Canute](https://anilist.co/character/17438), which resulted in him being sold into slavery and bought by a farmer.!~\n\nVoiced by [Shizuka Ishigami](https://anilist.co/staff/118738) during his childhood in the anime.','2020-10-19 11:35:46','2020-10-19 11:35:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b10138-xfsBtXLrHjPF.jpg','MC'),(2519,'Gratianus','is a Welsh warrior serving as a captain of Morgannwg\'s military.','2020-10-19 11:35:46','2020-10-19 11:35:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b156515-2CuUwCXo0XVG.jpg','MC'),(2520,'Torgrim','He is [Atli](https://anilist.co/character/141592)\'s older brother.','2020-10-19 11:35:46','2020-10-19 11:35:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b141591-UMaBb2ngD21s.png','SC'),(2521,'Tore','is a member of Askeladd\'s band.','2020-10-19 11:35:46','2020-10-19 11:35:46','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b156514-Bz6bnIhPCOft.jpg','MC'),(2522,'Asser','is a Welsh envoy','2020-10-19 11:35:47','2020-10-19 11:35:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b156503-mSIcfRrmQmbp.jpg','SC'),(2523,'Anne','','2020-10-19 11:35:47','2020-10-19 11:35:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b149584-FxdawVQg19at.png','SC'),(2524,'Ari','~!He is the husband of [Ylva](https://anilist.co/character/27876).!~','2020-10-19 11:35:47','2020-10-19 11:35:47','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b140357-kZrxMbSYiFrb.png','MC'),(2525,'Violet Evergarden','Violet Evergarden is the titular protagonist of the Violet Evergarden series. She is an orphaned former child soldier who was enlisted in the Leidenschaftlich army and fought in the war, where she was treated as nothing more than a weapon because of her extraordinary fighting capabilities. After the war, Violet became an Auto Memories Doll at the CH Postal Company, seeking to understand the meaning of the words \"I love you,\" which was told by the person she holds dearest, Gilbert, during the War\'s final leg.','2020-10-19 11:35:50','2020-10-19 11:35:50','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b90169-q5lmES4WWGuV.png','SC'),(2526,'Dietfried Bougainvillea','Dietfried Bougainvillea is a naval captain in the navy and [Gilbert](https://anilist.co/character/124790/)\'s older brother. He was the one who found [Violet](https://anilist.co/character/90169/) and made her into Gilbert\'s \"weapon\" on his promotion to a major in the army.\n\n(Source: Violet Evergarden wiki)','2020-10-19 11:35:50','2020-10-19 11:35:50','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b124789-DLp0QEJZeiQ8.png','MC'),(2527,'Cattleya Baudelaire','Cattleya Baudelaire is a character in the Violet Evergarden series. Being a figurehead Auto Memories Doll who works for the CH Postal Company, Cattleya never stops being requested and often takes on clients with love troubles. She works alongside Violet and has been close with Hodgins since before the company was established, joining as one of its initial employees.','2020-10-19 11:35:51','2020-10-19 11:35:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124787-ODinkzaIhmOh.png','MC'),(2528,'Gilbert Bougainvillea','Gilbert Bougainvillea is a character in the Violet Evergarden series. He is a major in the Leidenschaftlich army who values Violet more than anything, seeing her as a human being rather than a tool.\n\n~!Violet was \"given\" to Gilbert as a gift to commemorate his promotion, having being promoted to a major in light of his wartime achievements and expectations from his bloodline. Dietfried, not wanting to take care of Violet, pushed this task to his younger brother. Gilbert then decided to enlist her on a militant unit that he had been appointed to take overall command of in his promotion to major. He later received permission to conduct private experiments at the training grounds as to whether Violet could be officially classified as a \"weapon.\"!~','2020-10-19 11:35:51','2020-10-19 11:35:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124790-usp7asMBiXtX.jpg','MC'),(2529,'Iris Cannary','Iris Cannary is a character in the Violet Evergarden series. A rookie Auto Memories Doll with an unyielding spirit who works at CH Postal Company, Iris admires young working women and is enthusiastic about quickly making a name for herself in the industry.\n\n~!As a child, she became friends with a boy named Emonn Snow and the two were very close. Iris was in love with him, and she had also supposedly convinced herself that her feelings were reciprocated. Because of that, she confessed to him before they graduated school, but he rejected her confession. The emotional pain caused by Emonn\'s rejection was what caused her to leave her hometown to become an Auto Memories Doll.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:51','2020-10-19 11:35:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124793-dLsKOcQbMu85.png','SC'),(2530,'Erica Brown','Erica Brown is a character in the Violet Evergarden series. She is an Auto Memories Doll who has been working at the CH Postal Company for a while. She is not good at communicating and isn\'t confident in her work.\n\n~!Erica is an anime-original character.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:51','2020-10-19 11:35:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124792-uEurZmHwRxXh.png','MC'),(2531,'Benedict Blue','Benedict Blue (, Benedikuto Bur?) is a character in the Violet Evergarden series. He is a postman working at the CH Postal Company. He has known Hodgins since before the company\'s establishment and has had a brusque attitude towards him since he started working there.','2020-10-19 11:35:51','2020-10-19 11:35:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124788-4yiwdREZoLUs.jpg','MC'),(2532,'Lilian','','2020-10-19 11:35:51','2020-10-19 11:35:51','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b124801-zyntCs9PRuFU.jpg','MC'),(2533,'Bridget','','2020-10-19 11:35:52','2020-10-19 11:35:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b124791-UZv7eQrf3b2J.jpg','SC'),(2534,'Guest Man','Appears in anime episode 2.','2020-10-19 11:35:52','2020-10-19 11:35:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg','SC'),(2535,'Claudia Hodgins','Claudia is a former army commander. He founded the CH postal company and serves as president.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:35:52','2020-10-19 11:35:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124799-uLq3gAjXOQ6G.jpg','SC'),(2536,'Tiffany Evergarden','An old woman who wants to take in Violet after being contacted by Gilbert. She has lost her son during the war.','2020-10-19 11:35:52','2020-10-19 11:35:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124795-TVTdrCVsDONn.jpg','SC'),(2537,'Spencer Marlborough','','2020-10-19 11:35:52','2020-10-19 11:35:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124805-EouyBUScvHdi.png','SC'),(2538,'Oliver','','2020-10-19 11:35:52','2020-10-19 11:35:52','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b124808-zzb8RhH6z3LX.jpg','SC'),(2539,'Iberis Conoway','','2020-10-19 11:35:53','2020-10-19 11:35:53','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124794-nNNzoCGufkAF.png','MC'),(2540,'Nerine','','2020-10-19 11:35:54','2020-10-19 11:35:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b124809-mLwqAQH1KRz8.jpg','MC'),(2541,'Iris\' Niece','','2020-10-19 11:35:54','2020-10-19 11:35:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b124803-9qK35gh1KwkO.jpg','MC'),(2542,'Toby Selwyn','','2020-10-19 11:35:54','2020-10-19 11:35:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b161638-bOsXdyPsdiAq.png','SC'),(2543,'Charlotte Abelfreyja Drossel','She is the princess of Drossel, and the narrator for the 5th episode of Violet Evergarden.','2020-10-19 11:35:54','2020-10-19 11:35:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b142149-kS9eRdPsWyS0.png','MC'),(2544,'Luculia Marlborough','','2020-10-19 11:35:54','2020-10-19 11:35:54','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124810-TaIsx6FgMEOE.png','SC'),(2545,'Roland','','2020-10-19 11:35:55','2020-10-19 11:35:55','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124807-cTrQjEhuQC5e.jpg','MC'),(2546,'Leon Stephanotis','','2020-10-19 11:35:55','2020-10-19 11:35:55','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n129999-597v3afHYcH3.jpg','MC'),(2547,'Bluebell Unoa','','2020-10-19 11:35:56','2020-10-19 11:35:56','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/124806-s4r4rTM7JTwN.png','MC'),(2548,'Isabella','Isabella is the mama of the Grace Field House.\n\n~!She serves as the main antagonist of The Promised Neverland in the first arc and runs one of the Grace Field House orphanages, specifically known as Plant 3.!~\n\n~!She is later to be revealed as the biological mother of Ray.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:57','2020-10-19 11:35:57','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b121701-AU6DioIiWbmB.jpg','MC'),(2549,'Krone','Sister Krone runs the Grace Field House orphanage with Madam Isabella.\n\nSPOILER\n~! She would eventually attempt to usurp the position of \"Mama,\" an act which would lead to her death at the hands of Isabella, Grandma and the Demons !~','2020-10-19 11:35:57','2020-10-19 11:35:57','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b121702-AtJJQaf7HcVI.jpg','SC'),(2550,'Norman','Age: 11\nBirthday: March 21, 2034\nHeight: 145 cm\nFarm Identifier: 22194\n\nNorman seems to be logical, well-meaning, and devoted, with a slightly naive side. He can easily plan his actions in advance and he anticipates on other\'s actions. He is one of the top 3 ranking orphans, along with Emma and Ray.\n\nHe loves Emma. He is helpful and loyal towards her and will try to do what it takes to make sure she and the other kids ~!get to safety and away from the demons.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:58','2020-10-19 11:35:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b121700-0QhyLdihQxrT.jpg','MC'),(2551,'Nat','Nat is a child of average height with red hair kept in a bowl cut and brown eyes. He has a tall nose line (which he took pride of) and has his number \"30294\" on the left side of his neck. He wears standard orphanage uniform.','2020-10-19 11:35:58','2020-10-19 11:35:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b129805-cpxzl5lIYi2t.jpg','SC'),(2552,'Phil','__Age:__ 4\n__Farm Identifier:__ 34394 (Grace Field House)\n__D.O.B:__ 2041\n__Height:__ 100 cm\n\nPhil is very active and can always be seen running around. \n~~!He is also shown to be very mature and intelligent for his age, even suspecting something was wrong when Emma and the other older orphans were trying to find out ways to escape.!~~','2020-10-19 11:35:58','2020-10-19 11:35:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b126475-zPTsgEBqDdzW.jpg','SC'),(2553,'Ray','__Age:__ 11 (in the beginning of the story), 13 (after time skip), 15 (end of story)\n__Birthday:__ January 15, 2034\n__Height:__ 150 cm\n__Farm Identifier:__ 81194\n\n~!In the manga, it is revealed that January 15th is not Ray\'s real birthday, but more information is not given.!~\nAs one of the three perfect students at the orphanage Ray is very logical, smart, cunning, extremely patient and is usually shown to read books by himself. Although he is extremely book smart he says that he never liked to study. According to data obtained by sister Krone, his weakness is that he gives up easily.\n~!Ray betrays Norman and Emma and reveals crucial information about their plans to Mama. It turns out, though, that he was actually always on Norman and Emma\'s side and wanted to protect them at any cost. We later find out that Ray knew about what was truly happening in the orphanage since he was a baby. Ray is Isabella\'s biological child.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:58','2020-10-19 11:35:58','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b121724-SJTdODjeO7e6.jpg','SC'),(2554,'Don','__Age:__ 10\n__Farm Identifier:__ 16194\n__D.O.B:__ 2035\n__Height:__ 1,55 cm\n\nDon has dark skin and a tall and slender appearance. He has short, messy black hair with an undercut and brown eyes. He wears the standard white uniform.\n<br></br>\nLike Emma, Don cares deeply about his siblings. Don is portrayed as a cheerful and slightly careless boy, however, he too is fairly intelligent, coming around 5th place in the everyday test, after Gilda. He also has talents in pick pocketing. His physical ability is also fairly strong.\n<br></br>\n~!He swore he would rescue Conny and the rest of the orphans when he was told they were sold off. When he found out this was a lie, and Conny no longer lived, he uses violence against Ray and Norman for hiding the harsh reality, and expressed his sorrows and anger for not being able to do anything about it. !~','2020-10-19 11:35:59','2020-10-19 11:35:59','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b126454-lqHzjU6lfi6k.jpg','MC'),(2555,'Lannion','Lannion is 7-years-old boy with an ID number of 54294 living at Grace Field House. \n<br></br>\n~!He escaped the house with the rest of his siblings.!~','2020-10-19 11:35:59','2020-10-19 11:35:59','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b129783-6KAMdcOzkmCv.jpg','MC'),(2556,'Gilda','__Age:__ 10\n__Farm Identifier:__ 65194\n__D.O.B:__ 2035\n__Height:__ 138 cm\n\nGilda has short olive drab hair kept in a Chinese bob hairstyle and wears circular-lensed glasses. Gilda is an intuitive young girl. She also has a caring personality. She seems to be an introvert, however she also has her moments of bravery. She can also be quite threatening.','2020-10-19 11:35:59','2020-10-19 11:35:59','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b126455-m3tV91yqOwl6.jpg','SC'),(2557,'Grandmother','Grandmother is a high ranking human.','2020-10-19 11:35:59','2020-10-19 11:35:59','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b136463-iH8PI8qDMeDN.jpg','SC'),(2558,'Thoma','Thoma is a 7-years-old boy with an ID number of 55294 living at Grace Field House. \n\n~!He escaped the house with the rest of his siblings.!~','2020-10-19 11:36:00','2020-10-19 11:36:00','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b129784-FbXsryoxKR2b.jpg','SC'),(2559,'Anna','__Age:__ 9\n__Farm Identifier:__ 48194 (Grace Field House)\n__D.O.B:__ 2036\n__Height:__ 1,35 cm\n<br></br>\nJust like every other orphans of Grace Field, she wears the standard Grace Field Orphanage uniform. Anna is a petite girl with blonde hair tied into twin braids. She now has shorter hair which are tied into short pigtails.','2020-10-19 11:36:00','2020-10-19 11:36:00','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/n126504-xHMVYY9uEfkh.png','SC'),(2560,'Conny','She was a little girl with blonde hair and eyes blue. Her hair was tied into two pigtails on the back. She wore the standard clothes from the Grace Field House. She is 6 years old. Height is 115 cm. Her identification number is 48294. She is nice and lovely towards Emma, Don and the other orphans. She always carried her stuffed rabbit Little Bernie around with her. Her intellect level seemed to be average for her age.\n~!She was one at the orphans at the Grace Field House where she lived her life comfortably with all of her siblings around her. Until the day when Isabella told her and the kids that a house with nice parents had been found for her. When she was sent out from the house, Emma and Norman found out that she was being harvested by some kind of Demons. They saw a flower sticking out of her chest, killing her instantly. Emma and Norman called the flower a Demon Flower. Her shipping date is 12th year 2045.!~\n<br></br>(Source: Wikipedia)','2020-10-19 11:36:04','2020-10-19 11:36:04','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b129785-rbe2QtLiRrZW.jpg','MC'),(2561,'Emma','__Age:__ 11 (at the beginning of the story), 13 (post timeskip), 15 (by end of series)\n__Birthday:__ August 22, 2034\n__Height:__ 145 cm\n__Farm Identifier:__ 63194\n\nEmma acts as an older sister to the other children and loves her family very intensely. She is sweet, heroic, caring, and has a big heart. She can also be naive and reckless, and doesn\'t hesitate to put herself at risk to ensure the safety of the group. The other kids describe her as having monster reflexes and an astounding ability to learn, which enables her to think fast in difficult situations and makes her a very good strategist. She could be considered a beacon of hope for the rest of the children.','2020-10-19 11:36:05','2020-10-19 11:36:05','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b121725-LQciVJOjnMVh.png','MC');
