kmon thieves who are apart of an evil organization called \"Team Rocket\". But everytime Team Rocket try to do their evil deeds, they fail thanks to Satoshi and his Pokmon.<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)','2020-10-04 02:41:52','2020-10-06 03:11:53',NULL),(91,'Pokmon Journeys: The Series','Pocket Monsters (2019)',2,NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2AZd74zPCMw','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx112153-LK1lpFz3vlvl.png','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112153-01RDuvgGTXjp.jpg',1,33126,'2019-11-17',NULL,0,'Series','Pokmon Trainer Satoshi has a new plan: see the world! But first, he and his partner Pikachu are headed to the opening of the Sakuragi Institute, a research facility dedicated to uncovering the mysteries of Pokmon in every region. Satoshi meets Goh, another boy with boundless curiosity about Pokmon, and both are overjoyed when Professor Sakuragi asks them to become official research fellows. With Satoshi as determined as ever to become a Pokmon Master, and Goh aiming to catch one of every Pokmon (including the Mythical Mew), our heroes are in for adventure and excitement as they explore the wide world of Pokmon!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Pokmon TV)','2020-10-04 02:41:56','2020-10-06 03:11:53',NULL),(92,'Pokemon Mystery Dungeon: Team Go-Getters Out of the Gate!','Pokemon Fushigi no Dungeon: Shutsudou Pokemon Kyuujotai Ganbaruzu!',2,NULL,'','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx2842-CkYZSdbEAj0z.png','',1,12180,'2006-09-08',NULL,0,'','A human wakes up one day to discover that he has become a Squirtle in a world filled with natural disasters, where he meets Charmander and Chikorita of Team Go-Getters, a Pokemon rescue team. Squirtle joins Team Go-Getters for the task of saving Pichu\'s Brother Pikachu from Skarmory, however Gengar and his Team Meanies decide to interfere.<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)','2020-10-04 02:42:00','2020-10-06 03:11:53',NULL),(93,'Pokmon Origins','Pocket Monsters: The Origin',2,NULL,'','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20159-Q4VpDs7q2j3O.png','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20159-hlRzN7QIuZhT.jpg',1,168130,'2013-10-02',NULL,0,'','One day, Red, a boy filled with dreams of going on a Pokmon journey, is called to Professor Okido\'s lab. There, he and his rival Green are given a Pokdex in order to collect data on all of the Pokmon in the region. As Red works his way to become champion with his Charmander, he meets many people on his journey, including Old Man Fuji, a man who runs the home for abandoned Pokmon, and Reina, a girl who works there. As danger in Red\'s journey begins to peak, he and his partner Pokmon experience a transformation like never before...\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)','2020-10-04 02:42:02','2020-10-06 03:11:53',NULL),(94,'Prison School','Kangoku Gakuen',0,NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HSvlOPMLQFQ','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20807-8nFoO0AUdGsy.jpg','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20807-IHYC4Qby3dkT.jpg',1,95109,'2016-03-04',NULL,0,'Series','Hachimitsu Private Academy was a revered and elite all-girls\' boarding school on the outskirts of Tokyo...once upon a time. But with the new school year comes a revision to school policy: Boys are to be admitted into the student body for the first time ever. But on his first day at Hachimitsu, Kiyoshi Fujino discovers that he\'s one of only five boys enrolled at the school. Their numbers overwhelmed by the thousand girls in the student body, is it heaven or hell that awaits these five (un)fortunates?!.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: ANN)','2020-10-04 02:42:06','2020-10-04 02:42:06',NULL),(95,'PSYCHO-PASS','PSYCHO-PASS',0,NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DgDBzAHg4wU','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx13601-tgjUlf4eQOyx.jpg','https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/1